2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Day%206%20Of%20Tunnel%20Collapse%3A%20Trapped%20Workers%20Face%20Risk%20Of%20Trauma%2C%20Hypothermia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERescue%20teams%20in%20Uttarakhand's%20Uttarkashi%20are%20battling%20against%20time%20to%20evacuate%2040%20construction%20workers%20who%20have%20been%20trapped%20under%20debris%20for%20over%20120%20hours%20following%20a%20tunnel%20collapse.%20The%20workers'%20prolonged%20confinement%20within%20the%20tunnel%20is%20raising%20serious%20concerns%20about%20their%20health%20and%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2012%2C%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20under-construction%20Silkyara%20Tunnel%20collapsed%2C%20trapping%2040%20construction%20workers%20within%20the%20debris.%20Elite%20rescue%20teams%20from%20Thailand%20and%20Norway%2C%20including%20the%20one%20that%20successfully%20rescued%20the%20trapped%20children%20from%20a%20cave%20in%20Thailand%20in%202018%2C%20have%20joined%20forces%20to%20aid%20in%20the%20ongoing%20rescue%20operation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERescuers%20have%20drilled%20up%20to%2024%20metres%20into%20the%20debris%20and%20have%20fitted%20four%20pipes%20to%20supply%20food%20and%20oxygen%20to%20the%20trapped%20workers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Ff6g15o38_uttarakhand-tunnel-collapse-drilling-machine_625x300_17_November_23.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoctors%20have%20emphasised%20the%20need%20for%20comprehensive%20rehabilitation%20for%20the%20trapped%20workers%2C%20fearing%20that%20the%20prolonged%20confinement%20may%20necessitate%20both%20mental%20and%20physical%20recovery%20processes.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20traumatic%20event%20and%20their%20current%20mindset%20would%20be%20very%20apprehensive%2C%20filled%20with%20uncertainty%20about%20their%20future%20and%20their%20survival.%20They%20could%20be%20feeling%20fearful%2C%20helpless%2C%20traumatized%20and%20frozen%20in%20time.%20They%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20really%20process%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Archana%20Sharma%2C%20consultant%20clinical%20psychologist%20at%20Sri%20Balaji%20Action%20Medical%20Institute%2C%20Delhi%2C%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trapped%20workers%20may%20also%20experience%20panic%20attacks%20due%20to%20the%20prolonged%20confinement%20in%20an%20enclosed%20space%2C%20said%20Dr%20Ajay%20Agarwal%2C%20Director%20of%20Internal%20Medicine%20at%20Fortis%20Hospital%2C%20Noida.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFurther%2C%20the%20ambient%20conditions%20such%20as%20oxygen%20and%20carbon%20dioxide%20levels%20too%20could%20impact%20their%20physical%20health%20and%20prolonged%20exposure%20to%20cold%20underground%20temperatures%20could%20possibly%20cause%20hypothermia%20and%20make%20them%20fall%20unconscious%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Agarwal%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoctors%20warned%20that%20construction%20sites%20often%20present%20a%20multitude%20of%20hazards%2C%20with%20falling%20debris%20being%20a%20major%20concern.%20The%20impact%20from%20falling%20objects%20can%20cause%20severe%20injuries%2C%20including%20fractures%20and%20open%20wounds.%20These%20injuries%20can%20be%20further%20complicated%20by%20the%20unsanitary%20conditions%2C%20increasing%20the%20risk%20of%20infection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20all%20the%20workers%20are%20collectively%20breathing%20in%20a%20closed%20space%2C%20carbon%20dioxide%20levels%20can%20heighten%2C%20exacerbating%20breathing%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20Ajay%20Kaul%2C%20chairman%2C%20Cardiac%20Sciences%2C%20Fortis%20Hospital%2C%20Noida.%20%26quot%3BLack%20of%20oxygen%20inside%20the%20tunnel%20can%20lead%20to%20asphyxia%20(suffocation)%20and%20that's%20a%20serious%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deployment%20of%20an%20'American%20auger'%20machine%2C%20airlifted%20from%20New%20Delhi%2C%20signaled%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20the%20rescue%20efforts.%20This%20specialised%20equipment%2C%20known%20for%20its%20efficiency%20and%20power%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20cut%20through%2070%20metres%20of%20rock%2C%20much%20of%20which%20came%20down%20from%20the%20roof%20during%20the%20rescue%20efforts%2C%20in%20an%20estimated%2012%20to%2015%20hours.%20The%20machine%20operates%20at%20a%20%26quot%3Btheoretical%20speed%26quot%3B%20of%205%20metres%20an%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20machine%20arrived%20in%20disassembled%20at%20the%20Chinyalisaur%20airport%2C%20located%20over%2030%20kilometres%20from%20the%20collapsed%20tunnel%20on%20the%20Char%20Dham%20pilgrimage%20route.%20The%20plan%20is%20to%20utilise%20this%20specialized%20machine%20to%20excavate%20a%20passage%20through%20the%20debris%20of%20the%20collapsed%20tunnel%20section%2C%20thereby%20creating%20a%20pathway%20to%20reach%20the%20trapped%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20under-construction%20tunnel%20is%20part%20of%20the%20ambitious%20Char%20Dham%20project%2C%20a%20national%20infrastructure%20initiative%20to%20enhance%20connectivity%20to%20the%20Hindu%20pilgrimage%20sites%20of%20Badrinath%2C%20Kedarnath%2C%20Gangotri%2C%20and%20Yamunotri.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700187540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fhlr455e8_uttarakhand-tunnel-collapse-_625x300_17_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-collapse-day-6-of-tunnel-collapse-trapped-workers-face-risk-of-trauma-hypothermia-4581144%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rescue%20teams%20in%20Uttarakhand's%20Uttarkashi%20are%20battling%20against%20time%20to%20evacuate%2040%20construction%20workers%20who%20have%20been%20trapped%20under%20debris%20for%20over%20120%20hours%20following%20a%20tunnel%20collapse.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https