n%20this%20round%20of%20elections.%20Not%20only%20is%20the%20state%20BJP%20in%20a%20disarray%2C%20there%20is%20massive%20support%20for%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20who%20set%20the%20state%20on%20the%20path%20of%20progress%2C%20the%20party%20claims.%20The%20Congress%20is%20aiming%20to%20win%2075%20of%20the%20state's%2090%20seats.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBut%20of%20the%20two%20states%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20with%20230%20seats%20is%20generating%20bigger%20interest%20given%20the%20twist%20in%20the%20backstory%20of%20this%20election.%20The%20collapse%20of%20the%20Congress%20government%20led%20by%20Kamal%20Nath%20in%202020%20following%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20and%20his%2022%20loyalists'%20walkover%2C%20placed%20the%20BJP%20back%20in%20power%20again.%C2%A0%20Now%20each%20party%20is%20out%20to%20prove%20they%20have%20been%20the%20people's%20choice.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Congress%20claims%20the%20BJP's%20return%20to%20power%20has%20pushed%20anti-incumbency%20to%20never-before%20heights.%20The%20state%20has%20been%20under%20BJP%20rule%20since%20August%202004%2C%20when%20Uma%20Bharati%20became%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20Then%20after%20a%20brief%20stint%20by%20Babulal%20Gaur%2C%20Shivraj%20Chouhan%20was%20named%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20in%20November%202005.%C2%A0%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESoft%20spoken%20Mr%20Chouhan%2C%20dubbed%20%26quot%3Bmama%26quot%3B%20--%20maternal%20uncle%20--%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20state's%20most%20popular%20Chief%20Ministers.%20The%20BJP%2C%20though%2C%20has%20not%20projected%20him%20as%20the%20Chief%20Ministerial%20candidate%20this%20time%2C%20and%20campaigned%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20party%20has%20also%20fielded%20an%20unprecedented%20seven%20MPs%2C%20including%20Union%20ministers%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%2C%20Pralhad%20Patel%20and%20Faggan%20Singh%20Kulaste.%20Though%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20is%20not%20contesting%2C%20the%20performance%20of%20his%20loyalists%20will%20have%20a%20crucial%20effect%20in%20the%20power%20balance%20with%20the%20party's%20old%20guard.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMany%20feel%20this%20signals%20the%20Central%20leadership's%20readiness%20to%20go%20for%20a%20new%20face%20for%20the%20top%20job.%20Others%20claim%20the%20party%20will%20have%20trouble%20replacing%20Mr%20Chouhan%2C%20one%20of%20the%20state's%20tallest%20OBC%20leaders%20who%20also%20has%20a%20mass%20following.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20focused%20particularly%20on%20the%20Gwalior-Chambal%20and%20Mahakoshal%20regions%20--%20where%20it%20fared%20badly%20in%20the%202018%20elections.%20The%20area%20accounts%20for%2072%20of%20the%20state's%20230%20assembly%20seats.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20second%20phase%20of%20election%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20has%20a%20line-up%20of%20heavyweights%20--%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%2C%20his%20deputy%20TS%20Singh%20Deo%2C%20eight%20state%20ministers%20and%20four%20members%20of%20Parliament.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20traditional%20binary%20contest%20in%20the%20state%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20has%20become%20a%20multi-cornered%20tussle%20with%20the%20entry%20of%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party.%20Mayawati's%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20in%20the%20race.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECounting%20of%20votes%20for%20both%20states%20will%20take%20place%20on%20December%203%2C%20along%20with%20votes%20for%20Telangana%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Mizoram%2C%20where%20elections%20are%20taking%20place%20in%20this%20round.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700187300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F57442v6c_mp-polls-1200_625x300_16_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbattleground-madhya-pradesh-chhattisgarh-10-points-4580848%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhatti