F65544f2a36d588dc55d088ff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bathroom.%3Cp%3EAnna-Carina%20Tetzner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3ECapturing%20the%20moments%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMidway%20through%20the%20project%2C%20the%20couple%20started%20documenting%20their%20progress%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40slowlifeinbali%2Fvideos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20beginning%2C%20we%20weren't%20filming%20anything%20because%20we%20just%20didn't%20have%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Tetzner%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20as%20time%20went%20on%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20little%20bit%20sad%20that%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20the%20memories%2C%20so%20I%20thought%2C%20let%20me%20just%20see%20if%20I%20can%20put%20something%20very%20basic%20together%20that%20we%20could%20look%20back%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20videos%20on%20the%20couple's%20channel%20are%20both%20cinematic%20and%20raw%2C%20with%20stunning%20drone%20footage%20spliced%20together%20with%20scenes%20of%20the%20couple%20discussing%20their%20plans%20for%20the%20day%20and%20time-lapses%20of%20things%20getting%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDo%20your%20research%20first%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20living%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65544bf636d588dc55d088c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22563%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20cabinet%20in%20the%20couple's%20living%20room.%3Cp%3EAnna-Carina%20Tetzner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20piece%20of%20advice%20for%20others%20who%20want%20to%20build%20a%20home%20in%20Bali%3F%20Get%20at%20least%20three%20quotes%2C%20Tetzner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20important%20to%20live%20in%20Bali%20for%20a%20while%20and%20learn%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20the%20language%20before%20making%20such%20a%20huge%20li