-death-penalty-for-his-empire-experts-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20be%20put%20in%20receivership%20and%20its%20assets%20%26quot%3Bdissolved%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20sold.%20The%20order%20has%20been%20appealed%20and%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20fully%20explained%20or%20even%20partially%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Flemmons%2C%20a%20former%20fraud%20enforcer%20for%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commision%2C%20testified%20that%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20%26quot%3Bmethodologies%26quot%3B%20can%20be%20used%20in%20coming%20up%20with%20the%20estimated%20property%20and%20asset%20values.%20These%20methodologies%20can%20come%20up%20with%20net-worth%20values%20that%20differ%20from%20each%20other%20by%20%26quot%3Borders%20of%20magnitude%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Flemmons%20conceded%20on%20the%20stand%20that%20a%20decade's%20worth%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-gets-beat-up-by-his-own-fraud-trial-expert-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump's%20annual%20net-worth%20statements%20contained%20%26quot%3Bglaring%26quot%3B%20problems.%20%3C%2Fa%3EBut%20he%20said%20that%20Trump's%20accountants%20had%20the%20ultimate%20responsibility%20for%20what's%20in%20the%20statements%2C%20an%20assertion%20that%20the%20AG's%20office%20and%20the%20judge%20have%20differed%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20he%20was%20asked%20by%20Wallace%2C%20the%20attorney%20for%20the%20AG%2C%20about%20that%20%26quot%3Borders%20of%20magnitude%26quot%3B%20remark.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20are%20you%20able%20to%20have%20values%20that%20differ%20by%20an%20order%20of%20magnitude%26quot%3B%20that%20both%20reflect%20a%20property's%20current%20value%2C%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEstimated%20current%20value%20is%20not%20an%20exact%20science%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETestimony%20in%20Trump's%20defense%20case%20continues%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ER