elfare%20initiatives%20for%20the%20economically%20weaker%20sections%20of%20the%20society%20and%20it%20would%20cost%20a%20poor%20state%20like%20Bihar%20several%20crores%20of%20rupees.%20We%20will%20have%20to%20spend%20it%20in%20over%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20demand%20for%20special%20status%20to%20Bihar%20is%20fulfilled%2C%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20provide%20all%20benefits%20to%20the%20people%20concerned%20within%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years.%20Therefore%2C%20Bihar%20needs%20the%20status%20immediately%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20chief%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20two%20bills%20related%20to%20reservation%20of%20vacancies%20which%20were%20passed%20unanimously%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20and%20council%20during%20the%20recently%20concluded%20winter%20session%20were%20sent%20to%20Governor%20Rajendra%20Arlekar%20for%20his%20assent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20hopeful%20that%20the%20governor%20will%20soon%20sign%20both%20bills.%20Immediately%20after%20that%2C%20we%20will%20implement%20it%20for%20the%20upliftment%20of%20socially%2C%20educationally%20and%20economically%20backward%20sections%20of%20the%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Kumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20bills%20raised%20the%20quota%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%20from%2016%20to%2020%20per%20cent%2C%20scheduled%20tribes%20from%201%20to%202%20per%20cent%2C%20extremely%20backward%20castes%20(EBCs)%20from%2018%20to%2025%20per%20cent%20and%20other%20backward%20classes%20(OBCs)%20from%2015%20to%2018%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700160720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F94mspj98_nitish-kumar-pti-_625x300_03_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-launch-movement-if-bihar-not-giv