%2Fbusiness-67436369.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rs%20820%20Crore%20Erroneously%20Credited%20To%20Account%20Holders%20Of%20This%20Bank%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20much%20as%20Rs%20820%20crore%20were%20credited%20to%20account%20holders%20of%20UCO%20Bank%20in%20what%20the%20lender%20described%20as%20an%20erroneous%20transfer%20and%20has%20initiated%20a%20process%20to%20reverse%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20has%20recovered%20Rs%20649%20crore%20or%2079%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20amount%20erroneously%20credited%20to%20some%20accounts%20of%20the%20bank%20via%20Immediate%20Payment%20Service%20(IMPS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20taking%20various%20proactive%20steps%2C%20the%20bank%20blocked%20the%20recipients'%20accounts%20and%20has%20been%20able%20to%20recover%20Rs%20649%20crore%20out%20of%20Rs%20820%20crore%20which%20is%20about%2079%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20amount%2C%20UCO%20Bank%20said%20in%20a%20regulatory%20filing%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state-owned%20bank%20is%20yet%20to%20clarify%20whether%20this%20technical%20glitch%20was%20due%20to%20human%20error%20or%20a%20hacking%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20IMPS%20platform%20is%20operated%20by%20National%20Payments%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(NPCI).%20IMPS%20is%20a%20real-time%20interbank%20electronic%20funds%20transfer%20system%20that%20happens%20straight%20without%20intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20has%20initiated%20requisite%20actions%20to%20recover%20the%20balance%20amount%20of%20Rs%20171%20crore%2C%20it%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20matter%20has%20also%20been%20reported%20to%20the%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20for%20necessary%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20period%20from%20November%2010-13%2C%20the%20bank%20had%20observed%2C%20due%20to%20technical%20issue%20in%20IMPS%2C%20certain%20transaction(s)%20initiated%20by%20holders%20of%20other%20banks%20have%20resulted%20in%20credit%20to%20the%20account%20holders%20