e%20promotion%20process%2C%20which%20means%20it%20is%20their%20responsibility%20to%20support%20your%20growth%20through%20regular%20conversations%20and%20stretch%20assignments%2C%20and%20to%20complete%20all%20required%20inputs%20for%20a%20promotion.%20If%20your%20role%20is%20expected%20to%20work%20from%20the%20office%203%2B%20days%20a%20week%20and%20you%20are%20not%20in%20compliance%2C%20your%20manager%20will%20be%20made%20aware%20and%20VP%20approval%20will%20be%20required%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20internal%20memo%20stated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20after%20the%20e-commerce%20company%20implemented%20a%20policy%20in%20February%20this%20year%20requiring%20workers%20to%20report%20to%20work%20three%20days%20a%20week%20starting%20in%20May.%20The%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20altered%20the%20workplace%2C%20with%20companies%20sending%20employees%20home%20to%20work%20remotely.%20Even%20as%20lockdowns%20eased%20around%20the%20world%2C%20a%20large%20population%20of%20employees%20remained%20remote%20or%20in%20a%20hybrid%20environment.%20In%20a%20message%20that%20was%20posted%20on%20Amazon's%20blog%2C%20CEO%20Andy%20Jassy%20wrote%20the%20decision%20was%20taken%20at%20a%20meeting%20and%20that%20the%20move%20would%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20learn%20and%20collaborate.%20The%20company%20added%20there%20would%20be%20some%20exceptions%20to%20the%20rule%20-%20customer%20support%20roles%20and%20salespeople%20would%20have%20the%20option%20of%20working%20remotely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20staff%20members%20resisted%20the%20policy%20and%20around%2030%2C000%20employees%20petitioned%20Amazon%20to%20do%20away%20with%20its%20office%20rules%20in%20March%202023.%20At%20a%20protest%20at%20the%20company's%20Seattle%20headquarters%20in%20May%2C%20hundreds%20of%20Amazon%20employees%20voiced%20their%20opposition%20to%20the%20new%20policy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20in%20August%2C%20the%20CEO%20told%20staff%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20past%20the%20time%20to%20disagree%20and%20commit.%20If%20you%20can't%20disagree%20and%20commit%2C%20it's%20probably%20not%20going%20to%20work%20out%20for%20you%20at%20Amazon%20because%20we%20are%20going%20back%20to%20the%20office%20at%20least%20three%20days%20a%20week.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Amazon.com%20cut%20around%20180%20jobs%20in%20its%20games%20division%2C%20at%20least%20the%20second%20round%20of%20layoffs%20in%20under%20a%20week%20by%20the%20online%20retailer%20and%20digital%20streaming%20provider%20in%20a%20broader%20restructuring%2C%20an%20email%20viewed%20on%20Monday%20by%20Reuters%20showed.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20our%20initial%20restructuring%20in%20April%2C%20it%20became%20clear%20that%20we%20needed%20to%20focus%20our%20resources%20even%20more%20on%20the%20areas%20that%20are%20growing%20with%20the%20highest%20potential%20to%20drive%20our%20business%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Christoph%20Hartmann%2C%20Vice%20President%20of%20Amazon%20Games.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700153940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-09%2Fcblvdi5c_amazon-logo-reuters_625x300_25_September_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Famazon-to-block-employee-promotions-who-dont-return-to-office-report-4580658%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20company%20told%20managers%20that%20a%20higher%20office-to-home%20ratio%20is%20a%20must%20for%20employees%20who%20wish%20to%20advance%20in%20their%20careers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Famazon-to-block-employee-promotions-who-dont-return-to-office-report-4580658%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Famazon-to-block-employee-promotions-who-dont-return-to-office-report-4580658%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Famazon-to-block-employee-promotions-who-dont-return-to-office-report-4580658%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%