uccess-than-what-he-has-achieved-says-he-has-immense-respect-for-the-jawan-star%2Farticleshow%2F105269452.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Myanmar%3A%20After%20Refugees%20Flooded%20Into%20Mizoram%2C%20New%20Delhi%20Says%20It%20Was%20%E2%80%98Deeply%20Concerned%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14134513%2FScreenshot-2023-11-14-at-1.30.51.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20With%20hundreds%20of%20Myanmarese%20having%20crossed%20the%20border%20to%20seek%20refuge%20after%20heavy%20fighting%20between%20rebels%20and%20the%20junta%2C%20India%20on%20Thursday%20(November%2016)%20said%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20concerned%E2%80%9D%20and%20wanted%20a%20cessation%20in%20the%20violence%20through%20%E2%80%9Cconstructive%20dialogue%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20last%20month%2C%20the%20Myanmar%20military%20has%20faced%20a%20major%20coordinated%20offensive%20from%20an%20alliance%20of%20three%20ethnic%20armed%20forces.%20This%20had%20led%20to%20the%20rebels%20capturing%20several%20towns%20and%20security%20outposts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20days%2C%20intense%20fighting%20has%20taken%20place%20near%20the%20border%20with%20India%2C%20with%20some%20reports%20stating%20that%20more%20than%205%2C000%20refugees%20have%20escaped%20across%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20on%20Thursday%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20fighting%20has%20led%20to%20an%20exodus%20of%20civilians%20across%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20result%20of%20fighting%20between%20Rikhawadar%20area%20opposite%20Zokhawthar%20area%20in%20%5Bthe%5D%20India-Myanmar%20border%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20in%20the%20Chin%20state%20of%20Myanmar%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20movement%20of%20Myanmar%20nationals%20to%20the%20Indian%20side%2C%E2%80%9D%20MEA%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20said%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20asserted%20that%20India%20was%20worried%20about%20the%20fighting%20and%20would%20like%20an%20end%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20deeply%20concerned%20with%20such%20incidents%20close%20to%20our%20border.%20Our%20position%20on%20the%20ongoing%20situation%20in%20Myanmar%20is%20very%20clear.%20We%20want%20cessation%20of%20the%20violence%20and%20resolution%20of%20the%20situation%20through%20constructive%20dialogue%2C%E2%80%9D%20stated%20Bagchi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20authorities%20in%20the%20Indian%20states%20%E2%80%9Chave%20been%20handling%20the%20situation%20appropriately%20on%20humanitarian%20grounds%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20reiterated%20that%20India%20has%20called%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Creturn%20of%20peace%2C%20stability%2C%20and%20democracy%20in%20Myanmar%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20Myanmar%20citizens%20had%20taken%20refuge%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20current%20conflict%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20did%20not%2C%20however%2C%20specifically%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20Myanmar%20soldiers%20entering%20Mizoram%20after%20their%20military%20camp%20was%20taken%20over%20by%20rebels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20news%20agencies%2C%20over%2070%20Myanmar%20soldiers%20had%20fled%20into%20India%20with%20their%20arms%2C%20who%20were%20then%20handed%20over%20by%20local%20police%20to%20Indian%20defence%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBagchi%20also%20stated%20that%20India%20was%20facilitating%20the%20return%20of%20those%20who%20wish%20to%20go%20back%20to%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fafter-battle-with-junta-myanmar-rebels-take-control-border-point-with-india-2023-11-15%2F%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20most%20of%20the%205%2C000%20refugees%20have%20returned%20home%20as%20the%20fighting%20had%20calmed%20down.%20The%20Chin%20rebel%20forces%20have%20reportedly%20taken%20control%20of%20the%20Zokhawthar%20border%20crossing%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fighting%20is%20being%20described%20as%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20faced%20by%20the%20junta%2C%20which%20overthrew%20the%20democratic%20government%20in%20Myanmar%20in%20February%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20junta%20spokesperson%20Zaw%20Min%20Tun%20said%20that%20the%20military%20was%20contending%20with%20%E2%80%9Cheavy%20assaults%20from%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20armed%20rebel%20soldiers%E2%80%9D%20in%20Shan%20state%20in%20the%20northeast%2C%20Kayah%20state%20in%20the%20east%20and%20Rakhine%20state%20in%20the%20west.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700151854000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14134513%2FScreenshot-2023-11-14-at-1.30.51.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnew-delhi-says-deeply-concerned-after-myanmar-refugees-flooded-into-mizoram%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22External%20affairs%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20did%20not%20specifically%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20Myanmar%20soldiers%20entering%20Mizoram%20after%20their%20military%20camp%20was%20taken%20over%20by%20rebels.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnew-delhi-says-deeply-concerned-after-myanmar-refugees-flooded-into-mizoram%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pics%20of%20Anushka%20from%20World%20Cup%20semifinal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700151616000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105269170%2Cimgsize-53552.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Fcandid-moments-of-anushka-sharma-from-the-india-vs-new-zealand-world-cup-semifinal%2Fphotostory%2F105269170.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22