-towards-grindavik-homes-13009683%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20Army%20Says%20Footage%20Linked%20To%20Hostages%20Found%20At%20Gaza%20Hospital%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20forces%20were%20searching%20building%20to%20building%20at%20Gaza's%20main%20hospital%20Thursday%20as%20Hamas%20said%20the%20military%20had%20%26quot%3Bdestroyed%26quot%3B%20parts%20of%20the%20compound%20where%20deep%20concern%20has%20mounted%20for%20the%20up%20to%20thousands%20of%20Palestinians%20trapped%20inside.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoldiers%20raided%20the%20Al-Shifa%20a%20day%20ago%20in%20the%20hunt%20for%20a%20command%20centre%20they%20say%20the%20militants%20built%20below%20the%20complex%2C%20a%20charge%20denied%20by%20Hamas%20and%20leaders%20of%20the%20hospital%20that%20has%20become%20a%20focal%20point%20of%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20said%20it%20found%20rifles%2C%20ammunition%20and%20explosives%20at%20the%20Gaza%20City%20complex%2C%20as%20well%20as%20computers%20and%20equipment%20containing%20%26quot%3Binformation%20and%20footage%20pertaining%20to%20the%20hostages%26quot%3B%20taken%20in%20Hamas's%20shock%20October%207%20attack%20on%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20soldiers%20are%20proceeding%20one%20building%20at%20a%20time%2C%20searching%20each%20floor%2C%20all%20while%20hundreds%20of%20patients%20and%20medical%20staff%20remain%20in%20the%20complex%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Israeli%20army%20official%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshraf%20Al-Qudra%2C%20spokesman%20for%20the%20health%20ministry%20in%20Hamas-run%20Gaza%2C%20told%20AFP%20Israeli%20troops%20%26quot%3Bdestroyed%20the%20radiology%20service%2C%20and%20bombed%20the%20burns%20and%20dialysis%20departments%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThousands%20of%20women%2C%20children%2C%20sick%20and%20wounded%20are%20in%20danger%20of%20death%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Israel%20first%20sent%20troops%20into%20the%20hospital%20complex%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20UN%20agencies%20estimated%20that%202%2C300%20patients%2C%20staff%20and%20displaced%20civilians%20were%20sheltering%20at%20Al-Shifa%20without%20enough%20food%2C%20water%20and%20fuel%20for%20generators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20vowed%20to%20eradicate%20Hamas%20in%20retaliation%20for%20the%20attacks%20of%20October%207%2C%20which%20killed%201%2C200%20people%2C%20most%20of%20them%20civilians%2C%20and%20saw%20about%20240%20people%20hostage%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20officials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20says%2051%20of%20its%20troops%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Gaza%20since%20fighting%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20the%20Hamas%20government%20media%20office%20saying%20the%20death%20count%20from%20the%20offensive%20has%20now%20topped%2011%2C500%2C%20including%20thousands%20of%20children%2C%20calls%20for%20a%20truce%20are%20mounting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaza's%2036%20hospitals%20have%20been%20caught%20in%20the%20war%2C%20with%20more%20than%20half%20rendered%20non-functioning%20by%20shortages%2C%20combat%20and%20damage%2C%20the%20UN%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Red%20Crescent%20said%20a%20%26quot%3Bviolent%20attack%26quot%3B%20was%20underway%20on%20Gaza's%20Al-Ahli%20hospital%2C%20which%20was%20hit%20by%20a%20deadly%20strike%20on%20October%2017.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20blamed%20the%20blast%20on%20Israel%2C%20while%20Israel%20said%20a%20misfired%20Islamic%20Jihad%20group%20rocket%20was%20responsible%2C%20a%20position%20supported%20by%20US%20and%20some%20other%20western%20security%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIsraeli%20military%20tanks%20besiege%20Al-Ahli%20Baptist%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%2C%20and%20violent%20attack%20is%20underway.%20(Red%20Crescent)%20teams%20are%20unable%20to%20move%20and%20reach%20those%20who%20are%20injured%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20group%20said%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Meaningless'%20UN%20resolution%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20Security%20Council%20on%20Wednesday%20set%20aside%20deep%20divisions%20over%20the%20conflict%20to%20agree%20a%20resolution%20calling%20for%20%26quot%3Burgent%20and%20extended%20humanitarian%20pauses%26quot%3B%20in%20fighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20--%20which%20passed%20with%20abstentions%20from%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Britain%20and%20Russia%20--%20called%20on%20Hamas%20and%20Israel%20to%20protect%20civilians%2C%20%26quot%3Bespecially%20children%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20agreed%20to%20temporary%20localised%20pauses%20in%20fighting%2C%20but%20has%20rejected%20calls%20for%20a%20broader%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20%40UN%20Security%20Council's%20resolution%20is%20disconnected%20from%20reality%20and%20is%20meaningless%2C%26quot%3B%20Israel's%20Ambassador%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20Gilad%20Erdan%2C%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20reiterated%20the%20Israeli%20government's%20war%20aims%2C%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BIsrael%20will%20continue%20to%20act%20until%20Hamas%20is%20destroyed%20and%20the%20hostages%20are%20returned.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20foreign%20ministry%20called%20Thursday%20on%20the%20Security%20Council%20and%20the%20international%20community%20to%20%26quot%3Bstand%20firm%20on%20the%20prompt%20release%26quot%3B%20of%20all%20those%20kidnapped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExtended%20humanitarian%20pauses%20are%20untenable%20as%20long%20as%20239%20abductees%20remain%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20Hamas%20terrorists%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAttack%20victim%20'believed%20in%20peace'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20concentrated%20its%20heavy%20bombardment%20and%20ground%20offensive%20in%20Gaza%20City%2C%20announcing%20this%20week%20the%20seizure%20of%20the%20parliament%20building%2C%20government%20offices%2C%20Hamas%20police%20headquarters%20and%20key%20port.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20army%20claimed%20an%20initial%20raid%20in%20Al-Shifa%20had%20uncovered%20military%20equipment%2C%20weapons%20and%20what%20spokesman%20Daniel%20Hagari%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Ban%20operational%20headquarters%20with%20comms%20equipment%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20narrated%20by%20another%20Israeli%20army%20spokesman%20showed%20rifles%20and%20ammunition%20magazines%20inside%20an%20area%20he%20identified%20as%20Al-Shifa's%20MRI%20scanner%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20hidden%20very%20conveniently%2C%20secretly%20behind%20the%20MRI%20machine%2C%20said%20the%20spokesman%2C%20Jonathan%20Conricus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20health%20ministry%20in%20Hamas-run%20Gaza%20argued%20Wednesday%20the%20Israeli%20military%20did%20not%20find%20any%20weapons%20when%20it%20raided%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20and%20suffering%20in%20the%20densely%20populated%20coastal%20territory%20has%20prompted%20growing%20concern%20for%20Gaza's%20civilians%2C%20who%20have%20fled%20south%20to%20try%20to%20escape%20the%20heaviest%20combat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaza%20City's%20Al-Quds%20Hospital%20was%20evacuated%20during%20fighting%20in%20the%20area%2C%20forcing%20patients%20to%20make%20their%20way%20south%20to%20other%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20in%20pain%20along%20the%20road...%20I%20feel%20pain%20in%20the%20knee%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ahmad%20Abou-Sabra%2C%20wounded%20evacuee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20was%20bad%2C%20and%20the%20distance.%20We%20stayed%20in%20the%20army%20(checkpoint)%20for%20more%20than%20two%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20AFP%20at%20at%20a%20Palestinian%20Red%20Crescent%20hospital%20in%20Khan%20Yunis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20a%20month%20after%20the%20Hamas%20attack%2C%20mourners%20gathered%20for%20the%20funeral%20of%2074-year-old%20Israeli-Canadian%20peace%20activist%20Vivian%20Silver%20whose%20killing%20was%20confirmed%20days%20ago.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVivian%20was%20a%20woman%20who%20believed%20in%20peace.%20She%20was%20a%20woman%20who%2C%20in%20moments%20of%20despair%2C%20would%20bring%20us%20back%20the%20hope%2C%26quot%3B%20peace%20activist%20Ghadir%20Hani%20said.%20%26quot%3BShe%20believed%20that%2C%20both%20in%20Gaza%20and%20around%20Gaza%2C%20we%20all%20deserve%20to%20live%20in%20peace.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECall%20for%20war%20probe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUN%20human%20rights%20chief%20Volker%20Turk%20pointed%20to%20what%20he%20called%20serious%20allegations%20of%20international%20law%20violations%20in%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20and%20suggested%20an%20international%20investigation%20was%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhere%20national%20authorities%20prove%20unwilling%20or%20unable%20to%20carry%20out%20such%20investigations%2C%20and%20where%20there%20are%20contested%20narratives%20on%20particularly%20significant%20incidents%2C%20international%20investigation%20is%20called%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20briefing%20to%20UN%20member%20states%20in%20Geneva.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolls%20in%20Israel%20show%20widespread%20public%20support%20for%20military%20action%20against%20Hamas%20following%20the%20October%207%20attacks%2C%20the%20worst%20in%20the%20country's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20who%20has%20led%20Israel%20on-and-off%20for%2016%20years%2C%20is%20under%20intense%20domestic%20pressure%20to%20account%20for%20political%20and%20security%20failings%20surrounding%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtesters%20have%20taken%20to%20the%20streets%20demanding%20greater%20efforts%20to%20free%20the%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700150520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F5c0tb9h4_a