global%20ambassador%20in%202015...With%20UNICEF%2C%20we%20focus%20on%20boys%20and%20girls%2C%20but%20our%20main%20focus%20is%20on%20girls%20at%20the%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20David%20Beckham%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700150160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F2bg4scj8_david-beckham_625x300_16_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fambanis-special-welcome-for-football-legend-david-beckham-in-mumbai-4580160%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Ambani%20family%20hosted%20English%20football%20legend%20David%20Beckham%20who%20is%20visiting%20India%20for%20the%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fambanis-special-welcome-for-football-legend-david-beckham-in-mumbai-4580160%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fambanis-special-welcome-for-football-legend-david-beckham-in-mumbai-4580160%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fambanis-special-welcome-for-football-legend-david-beckham-in-mumbai-4580160%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22More%20Options%20En%20Route%20For%20Rescue%20Work%20After%20Earlier%20Attempts%20Fail%3B%20Workers%20Protest%20at%20Tunnel%20Site%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14115024%2FScreenshot-2023-11-14-at-11.50.16%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20On%20Wednesday%20(November%2015)%2C%20a%20specialised%20drill%20machine%20was%20flown%20in%20to%20hasten%20the%20ongoing%20operation%20to%20rescue%2040%20workers%20who%20have%20been%20trapped%20in%20an%20under-construction%20tunnel%20in%20Uttarakhand%20since%20Sunday%2C%20per%20latest%20reports.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20officials%2C%20the%20machine%20can%20bore%20t