20hour.%20The%20machine%20will%20drill%20a%20passage%20wide%20enough%20for%20authorities%20to%20insert%20a%20900%20mm%20steel%20pipe%20through%20which%20the%20trapped%20workers%20can%20crawl%20out.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EColonel%20Deepak%20Patil%2C%20who%20is%20overseeing%20the%20rescue%20work%20for%20the%20National%20Highways%20%26amp%3B%20Infrastructure%20Development%20Corporation%20Limited%20(NHIDCL%2C%20which%20was%20sanctioned%20the%20tunneling%20project%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways)%2C%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20the%20drilling%20work%20had%20resumed%20and%20that%20it%20was%20three%20meters%20inside%20the%20tunnel%20after%20half%20an%20hour%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20third%20plan%20is%20also%20in%20the%20works%2C%20he%20said.%20Equipment%20and%20machines%20for%20a%20possible%20option%20three%20are%20already%20on%20wheels%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-collapse-live-updates-uttarkashi-rescue-operation-workers-trapped-9027226%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Equoted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20him%20as%20saying%20on%20Thursday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20there%20were%20%E2%80%9Chigh%20chances%E2%80%9D%20that%20the%20current%20rescue%20plan%20%E2%80%93%20of%20the%20faster%20and%20specialised%20drilling%20machine%20already%20at%20work%20%E2%80%93%20will%20work%2C%20the%20news%20house%20quoted%20Patil%20as%20saying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20authorities%20cannot%20give%20%E2%80%9Can%20exact%20timeline%E2%80%9D%20as%20the%20speed%20of%20the%20drilling%20could%20increase%20or%20decrease%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20have%20a%20machine%20to%20look%20inside%20the%20debris%20and%20determine%20what%20is%20in%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIE%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20quoted%20him%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20colleagues%20of%20the%20trapped%20workers%20held%20a%20protest%20outside%20the%20under-construction%20tunnel%20against%20the%20NHIDCL%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20%E2%80%9Cignoring%20the%20safety%20guidelines%20which%20led%20to%20the%20incident%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdehradun%2Fworkers-protest-against-slow-pace-of-rescue-operations-at-silkyara%2Farticleshow%2F105243677.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20workers%20also%20expressed%20%E2%80%9Cdissatisfaction%20at%20the%20slow%20pace%20of%20%5Bthe%5D%20rescue%20operation%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETOI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20worker%20also%20told%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fdehradun-news%2Fworkers-protest-in-front-of-tunnel-against-delay-in-rescue-of-trapped-labourers-101700046833233.html%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20authorities%20were%20not%20allowing%20them%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20trapped%20workers%20and%20that%20they%20were%20keeping%20information%20hidden%20from%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20trapped%20workers%20would%20need%20both%20physical%20and%20mental%20rehabilitation%20upon%20being%20rescued%20%E2%80%93%20the%20incident%20could%20be%20traumatic%20for%20them%20as%20they%20are%20likely%20undergoing%20mental%20strain%20as%20well%20as%20physical%20stress%2C%20doctors%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptinews.com%2Fnews%2Fbig-story%2Futtarkashi-tunnel-collapse-survivors-would-need-physical-and-mental-rehabilitation-say-doctors%2F689807.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPTI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20November%2016.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reported%20on%20November%2016%20that%20the%20chief%20medical%20officer%20of%20Uttarkashi%2C%20R.C.S.%20Panwar%2C%20said%20that%20there%20were%20some%20concerns%20regarding%20the%20health%20of%20the%20trapped%20workers%20since%20some%20had%20complained%20of%20minor%20headaches%20and%20nausea.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPer%20the%20report%2C%20a%20six-inch%20pipe%20is%20being%20used%20to%20deliver%20essential%20medicines%2C%20multivitamins%2C%20glucose%20and%20dry%20fruits%20to%20the%20workers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ERescue%20to%20take%20more%20days%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20road%20transport%20minister%20Singh%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20said%20on%20Thursday%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eafter%20assessing%20the%20rescue%20work%20at%20the%20tunnel%20collapse%20site%20that%20the%20rescue%20would%20take%20two%20or%20three%20days%20to%20complete.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20initial%20rescue%20work%2C%20the%20%5Bdrilling%5D%20machine%20which%20was%20being%20used%20led%20to%20some%20portions%20being%20disturbed%2C%20which%20is%20why%20we%20stopped%20it%20as%20it%20could%20prove%20to%20be%20more%20dangerous.%20Now%2C%20a%20new%20machine%20is%20being%20used.%20We%20are%20trying%20to%20successfully%20complete%20this%20task%20in%202-3%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20PTI%20quoted%20him%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EVIDEO%20%7C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20initial%20rescue%20work%2C%20the%20(drilling)%20machine%20which%20was%20being%20used%2C%20led%20to%20some%20portions%20being%20disturbed%2C%20which%20is%20why%20we%20stopped%20it%20as%20it%20could%20prove%20to%20be%20more%20dangerous.%20Now%2C%20a%20new%20machine%20is%20being%20used.%20We%20are%20trying%20to%20successfully%20complete%20this%20task%20in%202-3%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FPNY57PZ6Im%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FPNY57PZ6Im%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20(%40PTI_News)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPTI_News%2Fstatus%2F1725069128254328919%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2016%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20is%20also%20taking%20the%20help%20of%20international%20experts%2C%20news%20agency%20ANI%20quoted%20Singh%20as%20saying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fdehradun-news%2Fworkers-protest-in-front-of-tunnel-against-delay-in-rescue-of-trapped-labourers-101700046833233.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20officials%20as%20saying%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20the%20state%20government%20was%20planning%20to%20take%20help%20from%20special%20rescue%20teams%20in%20Norway%20and%20Thailand%20to%20evacuate%20the%20trapped%20workers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERegarding%20Thailand%2C%20they%20specified%20rescue%20personnel%20having%20contacted%20a%20company%20that%20had%20rescued%2012%20people%20who%20had%20been%20trapped%20in%20a%20cave%20system%20in%202018%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20northern%20Chiang%20Rai%20province.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReuters%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Findian-workers-remain-trapped-collapsed-tunnel-rescue-hampered-2023-11-15%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20loose%20rocks%20falling%20into%20a%20tunnel%20that%20authorities%20are%20trying%20to%20create%20is%20hampering%20the%20rescue%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20main%20challenge%E2%80%9D%20that%20the%20operation%20currently%20faces%2C%20an%20anonymous%20%E2%80%9Ctop%E2%80%9D%20official%20in%20Uttarakhand%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPart%20of%20the%20Char%20Dham%20project%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1976714%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20November%2013%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways%20had%20confirmed%20that%20the%20tunneling%20work%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20ambitious%20and%20controversial%20Char%20Dham%20road%20project%20under%20the%20Ministry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20said%20that%20the%204.531%20km-long%2C%20two%20lane%20bi-directional%20tunnel%20at%20Silkyara%20will%20join%20the%20%E2%80%9CGangotri%20and%20Yamunotri%20axis%20under%20the%20Radi%20pass%20in%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20construction%20of%20this%20tunnel%20will%20immensely%20benefit%20the%20pilgrims%20as%20it%20will%20provide%20an%20all-weather%20connectivity%20and%20reduce%2025.6%20km%20snow-affected%20length%20of%20NH-134%20(Dharasu-Barkot%20-Yamunotri%20road)%20to%204.531%20km%20resulting%20in%20reduction%20of%20travel%20time%20to%205%20min%20i.e.%20one%20tenth%20of%2050%20min%20being%20taken%20at%20present%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20press%20release%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20tunnel%20project%20was%20sanctioned%20for%20Rs%201383%20crore%20in%202018%20and%20is%20being%20implemented%20by%20the%20Ministry%E2%80%99s%20company%2C%20the%20NHIDCL%2C%20the%20press%20release%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%20that%20year%2C%20the%20NHIDCL%20signed%20a%20contract%20with%20the%20Navyuga%20Engineering%20Company%20Limited%20for%20Rs%20853.79%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20the%20work%20was%20intended%20to%20be%20completed%20by%20July%202022%2C%20it%20has%20been%20delayed%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpresent%20progress%20of%20work%E2%80%9D%20is%20at%2056%25.%20Per%20the%20press%20release%2C%20it%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20completed%20by%20May%202024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Char%20Dham%20Project%2C%20which%20claims%20to%20also%20aid%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsupreme-court-char-dham-highway-national-security-wider-landslide-prone-roads-uttarakhand%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enational%20security%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(for%20it%20will%20lead%20up%20to%20the%20Indo-Tibet%20border)%2C%20includes%20widening%20around%20900%20km%20of%20existing%20national%20highways.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20experts%20have%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fit-doesnt-make-sense-for-char-dham-project-case-to-be-heard-by-a-new-bench%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecriticised%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20project%20saying%20it%20does%20not%20take%20into%20account%20the%20environmental%2C%20geological%20and%20ecological%20fragility%20of%20the%20area.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700149576000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F14115024%2FScreenshot-2023-11-14-at-11.50.16%25E2%2580%25AFAM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fmore-options-en-route-for-uttarakhand-tunnel-rescue%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20minister%20of%20state%20General%20V.K.%20Singh%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20rescue%20operation%20could%20take%20two%20to%20three%20more%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22e