%20roots%20in%20MP%2C%20right%20from%20the%20days%20of%20the%20Jan%20Sangh.%20Most%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20rule%20since%202003%20has%20been%20uninterrupted%2C%20barring%20a%2015-month%20stint%20of%20the%20Kamal%20Nath-led%20Congress%20government%20between%202018%20and%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20substantial%20section%20of%20voters%20across%20caste%20and%20class%20expressed%20a%20negative%20sentiment%20against%20the%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20government%2C%20either%20based%20on%20fatigue%2C%20dissatisfaction%20or%20simply%20a%20desire%20for%20change%2C%20the%20saffron%20party%20still%20enjoys%20a%20solid%20base%20of%20committed%20voters%20in%20this%C2%A0central%20Indian%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16202212%2FIMG20231108140455.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16202212%2FIMG20231108140455.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16202212%2FIMG20231108140455-300x225.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685121%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20group%20of%20BJP%20workers%20while%20campaigning%20in%20Sonkatch%20constituency%20in%20Dewas%20district.%20Photo%3A%20Omar%20Rashid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20long%20association%20with%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20style%20of%20governance%20%E2%80%93%20targeted%20welfare%20schemes%20and%20monetary%20assistance%2C%20especially%20to%20women%20and%20girls%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20deep%20roots%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20ideology%20with%20no%20counter-narrative%20at%20the%20grassroots%2C%20have%20kept%20the%20BJP%20as%20a%20dominant%2C%20if%20not%20hegemonic%20force%20in%20the%20state%20over%20the%20last%20few%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20even%20though%20the%20BJP%20lost%20the%20election%20to%20the%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%20the%20BJP%20got%20109%20seats%20against%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20114%20seats%20%E2%80%93%20it%20secured%20almost%2048%2C000%20more%20votes%20than%20the%20Congress%20and%20enjoyed%20a%20lead%20of%200.13%25%20in%20the%20popular%20vote%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EModi%20as%20Hindutva%20propellant%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Mehatwara%20town%20in%20Sehore%2C%20situated%20roughly%20between%20the%20capital%20Bhopal%20and%20the%20key%20city%20of%20Indore%2C%20Kumer%20Singh%20Thakur%20and%20others%20are%20seated%20outside%20a%20local%20BJP%20office%2C%20distributing%20white%20T-shirts%20with%20%E2%80%98MP%20%3Cem%3Eke%20mann%20mein%3C%2Fem%3E%20Modi%E2%80%99%20printed%20on%20them.%20%E2%80%98Modi%20sits%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20MP%2C%E2%80%99%20it%20roughly%20translates%20into.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20T-shirts%20are%20targeted%20at%20the%20labourers%20and%20working-class%20people%20who%20cross%20the%20bus%20station.%20They%20can%20wear%20it%20and%20advertise%20the%20party%20in%20the%20market%20and%20also%20back%20in%20their%20village%2C%20says%20Kumer%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20praised%20Chouhan%20for%20his%20%E2%80%98simplicity%E2%80%99%20and%20compared%20his%20long%20rule%20in%20the%20state%20with%20the%2015%20months%20of%20the%20Kamal%20Nath%20government%20through%20a%20communal%20lens.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EMiya%E2%80%99on%20ke%20nakhoon%20badh%20gaye%20thay%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5BMuslims%20had%20got%20emboldened%20under%20the%20Congress%20government%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kumer%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20to%20elaborate%2C%20he%20referred%20to%20the%20controversy%20that%20erupted%20in%20January%202020%20when%20a%20sub-divisional%20magistrate%20under%20the%20Congress%20rule%20ordered%20a%20temple%20management%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20town%20of%20Ashta%20to%20remove%20loudspeakers%20from%20an%20old%20Shiva%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmp-can-modis-tribal-push-help-bjp-regain-in-st-seats-where-it-suffered-losses-in-2018%5C%22%3EMP%3A%20Can%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Tribal%20Push%20Help%20BJP%20Recover%20in%20ST%20Seats%20Where%20it%20Suffered%20Losses%20in%202018%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20administration%20had%20clarified%20it%20was%20only%20following%20rules%20based%20on%20directives%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20noise%20pollution%2C%20the%20BJP%20accused%20the%20government%20of%20being%20prejudiced%20against%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShameless%20appeasement%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Chouhan%20then%2C%20asking%20Kamal%20Nath%20if%20the%20order%20issued%20to%20remove%20loudspeakers%20from%20the%20temple%20in%20the%20name%20of%20noise%20control%20would%20also%20be%20implemented%20in%20other%20religious%20places%20where%20speakers%20were%20used%20from%2010%20pm%20to%206%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECore%20BJP%20voters%20also%20lauded%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20Union%20government%20for%20nearing%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20Ram%20%3Cem%3EMandir%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Ayodhya%20and%20abrogating%20Article%20370%2C%20which%20granted%20special%20status%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20association%20of%20Hindutva%20with%20the%20BJP%20was%20often%20coupled%20with%20claims%20that%20the%20party%20had%20improved%20the%20infrastructure%20of%20the%20state%2C%20once%20a%20part%20of%20states%20dubbed%20as%20%E2%80%98BIMARU%E2%80%99%20for%20doing%20poorly%20in%20various%20parameters%20of%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Rahatgarh%20town%20in%20the%20backward%20region%20of%20Bundelkhand%2C%20Jagdish%20Goswami%20runs%20a%20small%20%3Cem%3Edhaba%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20highway%20to%20Bhopal.%20He%20is%2068-years-old%20and%20has%20lived%20through%20long%20stretches%20of%20both%20the%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EZameen%20aasman%20ka%20farak%20hain%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%3Cem%3EPehle%20kuch%20nahi%20tha%2C%20ab%20sab%20kuch%20hain%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5BThey%20are%20like%20the%20heaven%20and%20earth.%20We%20had%20nothing%20under%20the%20Congress%20rule.%20Now%2C%20we%20have%20everything%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Goswami.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20roads%20have%20improved%20and%20business%20has%20got%20better%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20promises%20made%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20this%20election%2C%20such%20as%20cheaper%20gas%20cylinders%2C%20were%20also%20attractive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20more%20than%20everything%20else%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20promoted%20a%20%E2%80%9CHindutva%20%3Cem%3Eki%20bhavna%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20or%20feeling%20of%20Hindutva%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20does%20not%20have%20a%20feeling%20of%20Hindutva.%20They%20didn%E2%80%99t%20solve%20any%20of%20the%20problems%20such%20as%20Article%20370%2C%20Ram%20Mandir%20or%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Goswami.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fwasnt-my-mother-your-ladli-behna-madhya-pradesh%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Wasn%E2%80%99t%20My%20Mother%20Your%20Ladli%20Behna%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeep%20dissatisfaction%20with%20Chouhan%20government%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20that%20core%20BJP%20voters%20did%20not%20discuss%20the%20shortcomings%20of%20the%20Chouhan%20government.%20Across%20districts%2C%20almost%20all%20of%20the%20pro-BJP%20respondents%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0spoke%20to%20said%20they%20were%20not%20fully%20satisfied%20and%20expected%20some%20improvements%20in%20different%20sectors%2C%20especially%20inflation%2C%20unemployment%20and%20local-level%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20ideology%2C%20the%20appeal%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20suspicion%20of%20the%20Congress%20ensured%20they%20did%20not%20stray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESidhnath%20Singh%2C%20a%20farmer%20in%20Sehore%2C%20said%20the%20Chouhan%20government%20had%20been%20lax%20in%20many%20departments%2C%20especially%20regarding%20allegations%20of%20corruption%2C%20and%20that%20it%20had%20been%20riddled%20with%20controversies.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20should%20be%20as%20solid%20as%20the%20one%20run%20by%20Modi%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20disruptive%20strategy%20to%20not%20have%20a%20%E2%80%98CM%20face%E2%80%99%20in%20MP%20this%20time%20and%20use%20Modi%20as%20an%20anchor%20while%20creating%20the%20feeling%20that%20there%20could%20be%20multiple%20claimants%20for%20the%20CM%20post%2C%20revealed%20its%20assessment%20that%20it%20could%20not%20bank%20on%20the%20image%20of%20the%20Chouhan%20government%20alone.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20it%20was%20an%20admission%20of%20anti-incumbency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20campaign%20banners%20and%20posters%2C%20Modi%20overshadows%20Chouhan%2C%20who%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20just%20another%20face%20among%20the%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20BJP%20campaign%20vehicle%20in%20Dewas%20district%20illustrated%20the%20BJP%20campaign%20strategy%20in%20one%20frame.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%98MP%20%3Cem%3Eke%20Mann%20mein%3C%2Fem%3E%20Modi%E2%80%99%2C%20it%20said%20in%20large%20font.%20Below%20it%20was%20a%20large%20cut-out%20of%20Modi%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20frame.%20On%20his%20right%20was%20a%20slightly%20smaller%20photo%20of%20BJP%20president%20J.P.%20Nadda%20and%20on%20his%20left%20an%20even%20smaller%20cut-out%20of%20Chouhan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20left%20were%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%2C%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%2C%20Virendra%20Kumar%20Khatik%20and%20Narrotam%20Mishra.%20On%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20right%20were%20cut-outs%20of%20Kailash%20Vijayavargiya%2C%20V.D.%20Sharma%2C%20Prahlad%20Singh%20Patel%20and%20Faggan%20Singh%20Kulaste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20above%20names%20include%20possible%20replacements%20for%20Chouhan%20if%20the%20BJP%20wins%20again.%20The%20BJP%20has%20fielded%20three%20Union%20ministers%2C%20four%20MPs%20and%20one%20national%20general%20secretary%20in%20this%20election.%20Many%20see%20it%20as%20an%20obvious%20downsizing%20of%20Chouhan%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20most%20popular%20face%20in%20the%20state%2C%20and%20an%20OBC%20to%20boot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-congresss-obc-politics-in-madhya-pradesh-is-to-shivraj-singh-chauhans-benefit%5C%22%3EThe%20BJP%20High%20Command%20Is%20Alarmed%20by%20MP%20CM%20Shivraj%20Blowing%20Hot%20and%20Cold%20on%20His%20Future%20Plans%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20BJP%20voters%20did%20not%20seem%20to%20care%20much%20about%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20reduced%20stature%2C%20with%20many%20maintaining%20a%20neutral%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20he%20returns%20as%20CM%2C%20its%20good.%20If%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%2C%20even%20that%20works%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sajjan%20Singh%20Thakur%2C%20who%20runs%20a%20%3Cem%3Ekirana%3C%2Fem%3E%20shop%20in%20Sehore%2C%20the%20district%20from%20where%20Chouhan%20is%20contesting%20elections%20(Budhni%20seat)%20and%20which%20is%20also%20the%20CM%E2%80%99s%20native.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20long%20as%20the%20CM%20is%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20be%20it%20anybody%2C%20I%20am%20happy%20with%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Goswami.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAryan%20Sahu%2C%20an%20OBC%2C%20said%20he%20was%20confident%20that%20despite%20the%20setbacks%2C%20the%20BJP%20would%20have%20no%20option%20but%20to%20pick%20Chouhan%20as%20CM.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20may%20not%20have%20declared%20him%20as%20the%20CM%20face%2C%20but%20we%20are%20confident%20that%20nobody%20else%20will%20become%20CM%20but%20%3Cem%3Emamaji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn-house%20squabbles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20BJP%20voters%20even%20argued%20that%20a%20change%20in%20guard%20might%20do%20the%20party%20well.%20%E2%80%9CNarendra%20Singh%20Tomar%20will%20be%20the%20CM%2C%E2%80%9D%20quipped%20Bhairon%20Singh%2C%20an%20upper-caste%20farmer%20in%20Sehore.%20Hari%20Singh%2C%20also%20an%20upper%20caste%20farmer%2C%20said%20ultimately%20for%20him%2C%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20symbol%20mattered%2C%20regardless%20of%20who%20was%20fielded%20as%20CM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20country%20will%20remain%20intact%20as%20long%20as%20there%20is%20Modiji.%20If%20the%20Congress%20party%20comes%20to%20power%2C%20the%20country%20will%20be%20enslaved%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Sonkatch%20assembly%20seat%20in%20Dewas%2C%20young%20BJP%20leader%20Sandeep%20Patel%2C%20campaigning%20for%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20candidate%2C%20said%20that%20all%20the%20voters%20cared%20about%20was%20the%20lotus%20symbol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Cem%3Ejanata%3C%2Fem%3E%20only%20cares%20about%20the%20lotus%2C%20meaning%20Modiji.%20We%20are%20witnessing%20Ram%20%3Cem%3Erajya%3C%2Fem%3E%20under%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CModiji%20ji%20%3Cem%3Eke%20diwane%20hain%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Modiji%20%3Cem%3Ejo%20bolde%20wo%20sarva%20manniya%20hain%20hamare%20liye%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%5BWe%20are%20crazy%20about%20Modiji.%20We%20will%20accept%20whoever%20he%20picks%5D.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20an%20hour%E2%80%99s%20drive%20from%20there%2C%20in%20Hathpipliya%20constituency%2C%20a%20roadside%20banner%20also%20describes%20another%20dimension%20of%20this%20election%3A%20will%20the%20entry%20of%20Congress%20rebels%20disrupt%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20internal%20harmony%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20banner%20features%20BJP%20candidate%20Manoj%20Narayansingh%20Choudhary.%20In%202020%2C%20he%20was%20among%20the%20many%20Congress%20MLAs%20who%20rebelled%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP%20to%20topple%20the%20Kamal%20Nath%20government.%20The%20banner%20has%20a%20large%20frame%20of%20him%20with%20folded%20hands%20in%20its%20left%20corner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16201850%2FIMG20231108143639.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16201850%2FIMG20231108143639.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16201850%2FIMG20231108143639-300x225.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685120%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20roadside%20banner%20of%20a%20BJP%20candidate%20showing%20the%20reduced%20stature%20of%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20campaign.%20Photo%3A%20Omar%20Rashid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbove%20him%20is%20a%20frame%20of%20Modi%20with%20a%20raised%20hand.%20In%20the%20right-hand%20corner%2C%20above%20a%20lotus%20logo%2C%20are%20frames%20of%20two%20leaders%2C%20almost%20similar%20in%20size%20and%20dimension%3A%20Scindia%20and%20Chouhan.%20The%20latter%20is%20relegated%20to%20the%20extreme%20end.%20A%20telling%20commentary%20on%20the%20many%20battles%20being%20fought%20in%20MP%20this%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20vs%20Congress%20for%202024%20will%20have%20to%20be%20crafted%20afresh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Hindutva%20and%20the%20deep%20roots%20of%20the%20BJP%20organisation%20in%20MP%20are%20serving%20as%20its%20bedrock%2C%20the%20party%20has%20also%20developed%20a%20strong%20support%20base%20over%20the%20years%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20its%20welfare%20schemes%20as%20well%20as%20the%20negative%20impression%20built%20over%20the%20years%20of%20the%20last