dard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsjvn-inks-pact-with-solar-energy-corporation-to-supply-200-mw-wind-power-123111601018_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsjvn-inks-pact-with-solar-energy-corporation-to-supply-200-mw-wind-power-123111601018_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsjvn-inks-pact-with-solar-energy-corporation-to-supply-200-mw-wind-power-123111601018_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ascertain%20Whether%20People%20You%20Sue%20Are%20Dead%20Or%20Alive%3A%20Court%20To%20SBI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAny%20bank%2C%20especially%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%20being%20the%20leading%20bank%20of%20the%20country%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20take%20proactive%20steps%20to%20ascertain%20whether%20the%20people%20being%20sued%20by%20it%20are%20dead%20or%20alive%2C%20a%20Delhi%20court%20has%20said%20while%20rejecting%20a%20suit%20for%20recovery%20against%20a%20loan%20defaulter%20who%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDistrict%20Judge%20Surinder%20S%20Rathi%20was%20hearing%20a%20suit%20filed%20by%20the%20SBI%20for%20the%20recovery%20of%20around%20Rs%2013.51%20lakh%2C%20along%20with%20interest%2C%20against%20defendant%20Siya%20Nand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20earlier%20asked%20the%20bank%20to%20conduct%20an%20enquiry%20about%20the%20defendant%2C%20following%20which%20it%20came%20to%20light%20that%20Nand%20had%20expired%20two%20years%20prior%20to%20the%20filing%20of%20the%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20then%20issued%20notices%20to%20the%20branch%20manager%20concerned%20for%20swearing%20a%20false%20affidavit%20and%20the%20general%20manager%20(law%2C%20recovery%20and%20litigation)%20to%20explain%20why%20the%20bank%20had%20decided%20to%20sue%20a%20dead%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20response%20thereof%2C%20the%20SBI%20has%20accepted%20its%20mistake%20and%20assured%20the%20court%20that%20they%20are%20taking%20appropriate%20action%20against%20the%20erring%20officials%20for%20non-compliance%20of%20an%20existing%20internal%20circular%20in%20this%20regard%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said%20in%20an%20order%20passed%20on%20November%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20there%20is%20nothing%20provided%20in%20the%20standard%20operating%20procedures%20(SOPs)%20being%20followed%20by%20the%20bank%20on%20how%20to%20ascertain%20whether%20a%20defendant%2C%20who%20is%20sought%20to%20be%20sued%2C%20is%20dead%20or%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20bank%20is%20not%20expected%20to%20sit%20and%20wait%20for%20information%20in%20this%20regard%20and%20if%20no%20information%20is%20received%2C%20proceed%20to%20sue%20a%20dead%20man.%20Any%20bank%2C%20especially%20the%20SBI%20being%20the%20leading%20bank%20in%20our%20country%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20take%20proactive%20steps%20to%20ascertain%20whether%20the%20people%20being%20sought%20to%20be%20sued%20by%20it%20are%20dead%20or%20alive%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%2C%20however%2C%20noted%20that%20the%20SBI%20had%20accepted%20the%20court's%20suggestion%20that%20its%20litigation%20officer%20would%20access%20the%20database%20of%20the%20chief%20registrar%20of%20births%20and%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20note%20of%20the%20unconditional%20apology%20tendered%20by%20the%20branch%20manager%2C%20the%20judge%20discharged%20the%20notice%20issued%20to%20him%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20reiterated%20that%20the%20SBI%20is%20the%20leading%20nationalised%20bank%20in%20our%20country%20and%20shall%20lead%20the%20banking%20industry%20as%20the%20torchbearer%20of%20efficiency%2C%20professionalism%2C%20transparency%20and%20ethics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERejecting%20the%20suit%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20a%20dead%20man%20cannot%20be%20sued%20under%20the%20laws%20of%20the%20country%2C%20the%20court%20said%20in%20the%20light%20of%20the%20SBI's%20%26quot%3Bcourse%20correction%26quot%3B%20so%20that%20such%20mistakes%20are%20not%20repeated%2C%20no%20extra%20cost%20is%20being%20imposed%20on%20the%20bank%20except%20forfeiture%20of%20the%20court%20fees%20already%20paid.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700145780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fcourt-generic_625x300_1527245477936.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fascertain-whether-people-you-sue-are-dead-or-alive-court-to-sbi-4580250%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Any%20bank%2C%20especially%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%20being%20the%20leading%20bank%20of%20the%20country%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20take%20proactive%20steps%20to%20ascertain%20whether%20the%20people%20being%20sued%20by%20it%20are%20dead%20or%20alive%2C%20a%20Delhi%20court%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fascertain-whether-people-you-sue-are-dead-or-alive-court-to-sbi-4580250%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fascertain-whether-people-you-sue-are-dead-or-alive-court-to-sbi-4580250%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fascertain-whether-people-you-sue-are-dead-or-alive-court-to-sbi-4580250%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20targets%20Hamas%20tunnels%20with%20attack%20dogs%2C%20%E2%80%98sponge%E2%80%99%20bombs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700145732000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105267650%2Cimgsize-82288.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-targets-hamas-tunnels-with-attack-dogs-sponge-bombs%2Farticleshow%2F105267642.cms%2