d%20I%20then%20became%20a%20global%20ambassador%20in%202015...With%20UNICEF%2C%20we%20focus%20on%20boys%20and%20girls%2C%20but%20our%20main%20focus%20is%20on%20girls%20at%20the%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20David%20Beckham%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700144100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F2bg4scj8_david-beckham_625x300_16_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fambanis-special-welcome-for-football-legend-david-beckham-in-mumbai-4580160%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Ambani%20family%20hosted%20English%20football%20legend%20David%20Beckham%20who%20is%20visiting%20India%20for%20the%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fambanis-special-welcome-for-football-legend-david-beckham-in-mumbai-4580160%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fambanis-special-welcome-for-football-legend-david-beckham-in-mumbai-4580160%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fambanis-special-welcome-for-football-legend-david-beckham-in-mumbai-4580160%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Satellite%20TV%20broadcaster%20Dish%20TV%20India%20shares%20up%207.5%25%20on%20settlement%20reports%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700144083000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-02%2F12%2Ffull%2F1644660431-0189.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsatellite-tv-broadcaster-dish-tv-india-shares-up-7-5-on-settlement-reports-123111601009_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dish%20TV%20India%2C%20a%20direct-to-home%20broadcaster%2C%20is%20facing%20intense%20competition%20from%20OTTs%20and%20cable%20TV%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busin