agement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334236%2Fclay-innovations-mitti-cool-fridge-terracotta-home-decor-mangalore-tiles-zero-electricity-cooler%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Drop%20Plaque%2C%20Replace%20It%20With%20Tagore's%20Name%2C%20Says%20Centre%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20has%20asked%20Visva%20Bharati%20University%20to%20replace%20the%20controversial%20plaques%20commemorating%20UNESCO's%20award%20of%20World%20Heritage%20Site%20to%20Santiniketan%2C%20a%20varsity%20source%20said%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20education%20ministry%20has%20told%20the%20university%20to%20remove%20the%20plaques%20and%20replace%20them%20with%20ones%20having%20Nobel%20laureate%20Rabindranath%20Tagore's%20name%2C%20the%20source%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisva%20Bharati%20spokesperson%20Mahua%20Bandyopadhyay%20told%20PTI%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20cannot%20confirm%20anything%20about%20the%20plaques%20unless%20we%20have%20a%20written%20communique%20from%20the%20Union%20education%20ministry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20Santiniketan%20got%20the%20UNESCO%20tag%20on%20September%2017%2C%20three%20plaques%20commemorating%20the%20honour%20came%20up%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20campus%20having%20the%20names%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20former%20VB%20vice-chancellor%20Bidyut%20Chakrabarty%20but%20did%20not%20mention%20Tagore's%20name%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Santiniketan%20and%20Visva%20Bharati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20triggered%20an%20uproar%20from%20students%2C%20faculty%20and%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2026%2C%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20asked%20Visva%20Bharati%20to%20immediately%20change%20the%20plaques%20or%20face%20indefinite%20protests%20by%20her%20party%20activists%20on%20the%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20the%20protests%20were%20withdrawn%20after%20Chakrabarty's%20five-year%20term%20ended%20on%20November%208%20and%20Kala%20Bhavan%20principal%20VC%20Sanjoy%20Kumar%20Mallik%20took%20over%20as%20the%20officiating%20VC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20taking%20over%2C%20Mallik%20told%20reporters%20that%20he%20would%20ensure%20the%20ideals%20and%20values%20cherished%20by%20Tagore%20are%20retained%20in%20the%20university's%20functioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700140800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fnnd743i_santiniketan-plaque_625x300_26_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-tells-visva-bharati-to-replace-controversial-plaques-4579848%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Centre%20has%20asked%20Visva%20Bharati%20University%20to%20replace%20the%20controversial%20plaques%20commemorating%20UNESCO's%20award%20of%20World%20Heritage%20Site%20to%20Santiniketan%2C%20a%20varsity%20source%20said%20on%20Thursday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-tells-visva-bharati-to-replace-controversial-plaques-4579848%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-tells-visva-bharati-to-replace-controversial-plaques-4579848%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-tells-visva-bharati-to-replace-controversial-plaques-4579848%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Army%3A%20Indigenously%20Developed%20%E2%80%98Zorawar%E2%80%99%20Light%20Tank%20to%20Begin%20Trials%20Later%20This%20Month%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16181340%2FArjun.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChandigarh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20first%20prototype%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20indigenously%20developed%20light%20tank%2C%20principally%20for%20deployment%20in%20Himalayan%20border%20regions%20along%20the%20disputed%20border%20with%20China%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20begin%20trials%20later%20this%20month%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20eventual%20construction%20of%20at%20least%20354%20examples%20of%20the%20platform%20for%20the%20Indian%20Army%20(IA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuoting%20official%20sources%2C%20media%20reports%20recently%20revealed%20that%20although%20somewhat%20delayed%2C%20the%2025-tonne%20air-transportable%20and%20amphibious%20light%20tank%20named%20Zorawar%20would%20undergo%20rigorous%20high-altitude%20trials%20for%20an%20extended%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeveloped%20jointly%20by%20the%20Defence%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation%20(DRDO)%20and%20private%20vendor%20Larsen%20%26amp%3B%20Toubro%20(L%26amp%3BT)%2C%20the%20artificial%20intelligence-enabled%20tank%20is%20agile%20and%20fitted%20with%20an%20active%20protection%20system%2C%20industry%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20that%20developmental%20setbacks%20followed%20troublesome%20negotiations%20with%20Germany%20over%20supplying%20the%20DRDO%20MTU%20800-1%2C000hp%20water-cooled%20V8%20high-altitude-optimised%20engines%20for%20the%20tank%2C%20which%20were%20recently%20scrapped%20despite%20diplomatic%20intervention%20to%20help%20clinch%20the%20purchase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20an%20alternate%201%2C000hp%20advanced%20combat%20engine%20from%20Cummins%20in%20the%20US%20was%20acquired%20to%20power%20the%20tank%2C%20which%20is%20armed%20with%20a%20105mm%20gun%20acquired%20off-the-shelf%20from%20Belgium-based%20multi-national%20armament%20manufacturers%20John%20Cockerill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntegrated%20with%20tactical%20drones%20to%20provide%20situational%20awareness%20and%20loitering%20munition%20capability%2C%20these%20light%20tanks%20were%20primarily%20for%20employment%20along%20the%20line%20of%20actual%20control%20(LAC)%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20where%20the%20IA%20has%20been%20locked%20in%20a%20stand-off%20with%20China%E2%80%99s%20People%E2%80%99s%20Liberation%20Army%20(PLA)%20since%20May%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20believed%20that%20the%20DRDO-L%26amp%3BT%20designed%20tanks%20will%20more%20than%20match%20the%20mobility%2C%20fire%20power%20and%20accuracy%20of%20the%20PLA%E2%80%99s%2030-33%20ton%20ZTQ105%2FType%2015%20light%20tanks%2C%20presently%20deployed%20along%20the%20LAC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16172142%2FChinas-Type-15-tank.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22845%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16172142%2FChinas-Type-15-tank.jpg%201000w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16172142%2FChinas-Type-15-tank-300x225.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685101%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22634%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EChina%E2%80%99s%20Type-15%20tank.%20Photo%3A%20%E9%A2%90%E5%9B%AD%E5%B1%85%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFitted%20with%20a%20105mm%20rifled%20gun%20with%20a%203%2C000m%20range%2C%20the%20Chinese%20light%20tanks%20were%20capable%20of%20being%20airlifted%20and%20even%20paradropped%20by%20the%20PLA%20Air%20Force%E2%80%99s%20Y%2020%20military%20transporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IA%20ultimately%20aims%20on%20inducting%20seven%20light%20tank%20regiments%20of%20around%20315%20tanks%20%E2%80%93%20with%20another%2040-odd%20platforms%20in%20reserve%20%E2%80%93%20for%20which%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20(MoD)%20had%20accorded%20its%20Acceptance%20of%20Necessity%20(AoN)%20in%20December%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20AoN%20is%20the%20first%20of%20around%2010-11%20procurement%20procedures%20needing%20completion%20under%20the%20MoD%E2%80%99s%20Defence%20Acquisition%20Procedure-2020%20(DAP-2020)%20for%20most%20materiel%20purchases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DRDO%20had%20shortlisted%20L%26amp%3BT%20as%20its%20developmental%20partner%20for%20the%20light%20tank%20programme%20in%20an%20arrangement%20in%20which%20the%20latter%20would%2C%20after%20trials%2C%20series-build%2059%20of%20these%20armoured%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remaining%20290-odd%20vehicles%20would%20be%20tendered%20out%20to%20other%20local%20manufacturers%20under%20DAP-2020s%20%E2%80%98Make%20in%20India%E2%80%99%20category%20to%20obviate%20charges%20of%20%E2%80%98partiality%E2%80%99%20towards%20L%26amp%3BT%2C%20industry%20officials%20said%2C%20but%20added%20that%20these%20arrangements%20were%20%E2%80%98flexible%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IA%E2%80%99s%20light%20tank%20project%2C%20like%20a%20myriad%20other%20of%20its%20programmes%2C%20has%20endured%20extended%20birth%20pangs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDesultory%20attempts%20to%20develop%20one%20such%20armoured%20vehicle%20were%20initiated%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20in%20which%20the%20DRDO%20replaced%20the%20turret%20of%20the%20Soviet-designed%20BMP%20infantry%20combat%20vehicle%20(ICV)%20with%20a%20105mm%20gun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20project%20was%20eventually%20terminated%20in%201994%20due%20to%20indifference%20by%20the%20army%20which%2C%20by%20then%2C%20had%20declared%20light%20tanks%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98superfluous%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16173415%2F20190922_155047.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16173415%2F20190922_155047.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16173415%2F20190922_155047-300x225.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685102%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDRDO%2C%20which%20is%20the%20R%26amp%3BD%20wing%20of%20the%20Union%20defence%20ministry%2C%20shortlisted%20L%26amp%3BT%20as%20its%20developmental%20partner%20for%20the%20light%20tank%20programme.%20Photo%3A%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUndaunted%2C%20the%20DRDO%20designed%20another%20light%20tank%20based%20on%20the%20same%20licence-built%20ICV%20chassis%20by%20mounting%20it%20with%20a%20French%20GIAT%20TS-90%20turret%20and%20a%20105%20mm%20gun.%20Firing%20and%20stability%20trials%20were%20conducted%2C%20but%20once%20again%20due%20to%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20indifference%20the%20project%20was%20shelved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsequently%2C%20like%20most%20such%20projects%20which%2C%20like%20a%20yo-yo%2C%20alternate%20between%20conception%2C%20abandonment%20and%20revival%2C%20the%20light%20tank%20programme%20surfaced%20once%20again%20in%202008%20after%20Indian%20military%20planners%20shifted%20their%20strategic%20focus%20from%20Pakistan%20to%20the%20security%20threat%20posed%20by%20China%2C%20which%20was%20designated%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20number-one%20enemy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20prompted%20the%20IA%20to%20issue%20a%20global%20request%20for%20information%20(RFI)%20in%202009%20for%20200%20wheeled%20and%20100%20tracked%20light%20tanks%2C%20weighing%2022%20tons%20each%2C%20that%20required%20the%20modularly%20constructed%20platforms%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98highly%20manoeuvrable%E2%80%99%20with%20surveillance%20and%20communication%20capability%20to%20execute%20multi-purpose%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Preliminary%20General%20Staff%20Qualitative%20Requirements%20(PGSQRs)%20formulated%20by%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20Mechanised%20Forces%20Directorate%20at%20the%20time%2C%20both%20the%208%C3%978%20wheeled%20and%20tracked%20light%20tanks%20were%20to%20be%202.8m%20high%20and%207.8m%20long%20and%20needed%20to%20possess%20a%20low%20silhouette%20and%20amphibious%20capability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PGSQRs%20further%20stated%20that%20they%20were%20required%20to%20be%20fitted%20with%20a%20105mm%20or%20120mm%20gun%2C%20capable%20of%20firing%20an%20assortment%20of%20projectiles.%20High%20ground%20clearance%2C%20defensive%20aid%20suites%20offering%20protection%20against%20laser%2C%20thermal%20and%20radar-guided%20munitions%20and%20nuclear%2C%20biological%20and%20chemical%20protection%20completed%20the%20projected%20tanks%E2%80%99%20specifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fon-the-india-china-border-disengagement-is-not-resolution%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20India-China%20Border%2C%20Disengagement%20Is%20Not%20Resolution%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOperationally%2C%20these%20light%20tanks%20were%20envisaged%20as%20being%20part%20of%20the%20two%20mountain%20divisions%20that%20were%20then%20under%20raising%20%E2%80%93%20since%20commissioned%20%E2%80%93%20for%20deployment%20along%20the%203%2C488km-long%20LAC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20proportion%20of%20them%20were%20also%20considered%20as%20potential%20force%20multipliers%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98cold%20start%E2%80%99%20doctrine%20against%20Pakistan%20of%20going%20on%20the%20offensive%20in%20a%20limited%20war%20scenario%2C%20under%20the%20nuclear%20umbrella%2C%20to%20achieve%20%E2%80%98bargainable%E2%80%99%20military%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlongside%20this%2C%20it%20was%20argued%20that%20these%20platforms%20could%20also%20be%20deployed%20in%20urban%20and%20semi-urban%20environments%2C%20and%20in%20riverine%20terrain%20and%20marshy%20ground%20along%20India%E2%80%99s%20eastern%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponses%20to%20the%20RFI%20were%20received%2C%20but%20thereafter%20no%20formal%20tender%20or%20request%20for%20proposal%20was%20issued%2C%20as%20the%20entire%20proposal%2C%20like%20many%20others%2C%20was%20shelved%20because%20of%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20apathy%20and%20internal%20disputes%20over%20indigenising%20the%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20above%20all%2C%20competing%20financial%20claims%20concerning%20existing%20T72M%2C%20T90S%20and%20Arjun%20main%20battle%20tank%20(MBT)%20ventures%20sealed%20the%20light%20tanks%E2%80%99%20fate%2C%20and%20it%20was%20consigned%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98out%E2%80%99%20tray%20at%20army%20headquarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20short-sightedness%20and%20myopia%20would%20come%20back%20to%20haunt%20the%20IA%20decades%20later%20in%202020%2C%20when%20the%20PLA%20occupied%20large%20swathes%20of%20territory%20claimed%20by%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FoNbB277GITw%3Fsi%3DR6CFPVrsrMUtlHYG%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20with%20the%20subsequent%20induction%20of%20light%20tanks%20into%20service%2C%20the%20IA%20will%20have%20the%20dubious%20distinction%20of%20becoming%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20fewer%20armies%20that%20deployed%20four%20different%20tank%20types.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20the%20IA%20operates%203%2C500-odd%20licence-built%20Russian%20T72M1%20%E2%80%98Ajeya%E2%80%99%20MBTs%2C%20and%20directly%20imported%20and%20domestically%20assembled%20and%20constructed%20T90S%20%E2%80%98Bhishma%E2%80%99%20platforms%2C%20alongside%20124%20indigenous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdefence-arjun-mk-1a-main-battle-tanks-indian-army%5C%22%3EArjun%20Mk1%20MBTs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20118%20Arjun%20Mk1A%20variants%20worth%20Rs%208%2C350%20crores%20were%20on%20order%20from%20the%20state-owned%20Heavy%20Vehicles%20Factory%20at%20Avadi%20near%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20more%20incredulously%2C%20if%20the%20IA%20proceeds%20apace%20with%20its%202021%20plans%2C%20made%20known%20via%20an%20RFI%2C%20to%20acquire%20a%20%E2%80%98family%E2%80%99%20of%201%2C770%20medium%20weight%20Future%20Ready%20Combat%20Vehicles%20(FRCV)%20by%202030%2C%20the%20army%20will%20have%20the%20dubious%20distinction%20of%20simultaneously%20fielding%20five%20kinds%20of%20light%20and%20heavier%20MBTs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBesides%20the%20massive%20capital%20investment%20needed%20to%20acquire%20new%20tanks%2C%20their%20inventory%20management%2C%20which%20even%20today%20poses%20a%20formidable%20challenge%20to%20the%20army%2C%20will%20become%20even%20more%20acute%20with%20diverse%20additional%20platforms%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20military%20analyst%20Major%20General%20A.P.%20Singh%20(retired).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20another%20two%20entirely%20new%20tank%20types%20to%20the%20existing%20assortment%20will%20only%20make%20this%20task%20nightmarish%2C%20he%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20acquiring%20sector-specific%20platforms%20like%20light%20tanks%2C%20principally%20for%20deployment%20in%20mountainous%20regions%20along%20the%20LAC%2C%20would%20significantly%20exacerbate%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20logistical%20obligations%20by%20imposing%20an%20additional%20financial%20burden%2C%20the%20former%20armoured%20corps%20officer%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Findia-china-ladakh-border-tension-explainer%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Two%20Steps%20Forward%2C%20One%20Step%20Back%E2%80%99%3A%20The%20Chequered%20Story%20of%20India%20and%20China%E2%80%99s%20Border%20Tensions%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParadoxically%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20Army%20(PA)%20too%20matches%20the%20IA%20in%20that%20it%20has%20five%20MBT%20types%2C%20qualifying%20such%20tank-upmanship%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20competing%20rivalry%20between%20the%20neighbouring%20nuclear%20states%2C%20which%20underscores%20sundry%20aspects%20of%20existence%20in%20the%20respective%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PA%20fields%201%2C800%20to%202%2C000%20tanks%2C%20of%20which%20only%20the%20Ukrainian%20T-80UD%20MBT%20is%20the%20outlier%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remaining%20four%20MBTs%20%E2%80%93%20Type%2085-11AP%2C%20Al-Zarar%2C%20Al-Khalid%20and%20VT-4%2FMBT3000%20%E2%80%93%20are%20either%20licence-built%20Chinese%20models%20or%20have%20been%20jointly%20developed%20in%20conjunction%20with%20China%2C%20thereby%20conferring%20a%20high%20degree%20of%20structural%20correlation%20between%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20renders%20not%20only%20their%20manufacture%20but%20also%20their%20logistic%20and%20maintenance%20support%20less%20problematic%20compared%20to%20that%20of%20the%20IA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20major%20armies%2C%20the%20US%20operates%20variants%20of%20the%20M1%20Abrams%20MBT%2C%20whilst%20Israel%20fields%20the%20Merkav%2C%20Britain%20the%20Challenger-2%2C%20Canada%20the%20Leopard%202A6M%2C%20Germany%20the%20Leopard%20and%20France%20the%20Leclerc%20MBT%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20army%2C%20for%20its%20part%2C%20has%20T72%2C%20T80%20and%20T90%20MBTs%20%E2%80%93%20all%20with%20a%20high%20degree%20of%20commonality%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20only%20recently%20begun%20inducting%20the%20T-14%20Armata%20based%20on%20a%20common%20Universal%20Combat%20Platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20senior%20military%20analysts%20and%20veterans%20have%20critiqued%20the%20IA%20for%20focusing%20unduly%20on%20major%20platforms%20like%20MBTs%20and%20not%20enough%20on%20future%20technologies%20like%20robotics%2C%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20and%20cyber%20and%20electronic%20warfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20writings%2C%20they%20have%20observed%20that%20relatively%20inexpensive%20%E2%80%98swarm%20drone%E2%80%99%20squadrons%20have%20in%20recent%20months%20effectively%20destroyed%20advancing%20columns%20of%20hugely%20expensive%20MBTs%2C%20rendering%20them%20ineffective%20on%20the%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20an%20operational%20audit%20on%20the%20nature%20of%20future%20conflicts%20is%20overdue%20for%20the%20IA%2C%20instead%20of%20persisting%20with%20what%20generations%20of%20army%20commanders%20feel%20%E2%80%98comfortable%E2%80%99%20planning%20for%20and%20executing%2C%20with%20numerous%20tank%20types%20like%20in%20the%201965%20and%201971%20wars%20with%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700138766000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16181340%2FArjun.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Findigenously-developed-zorawar-light-tank-expected-to-begin-trials-later-this-month%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20army's%20light%20tank%20project%2C%20like%20a%20myriad%20other%20of%20its%20programmes%2C%20has%20endured%20extended%20birth%20pangs.%20And%20if%20it%20proceeds%20with%20plans%20it%20made%20in%202021%2C%20it%20will%20have%20the%20dubious%20distinction%20of%20simultaneously%20fielding%20five%20kinds%20of%20light%20and%20heavier%20battle%20tanks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Findigenously-developed-zorawar-light-tank-expected-to-begin-trials-later-this-month%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RBI%20approves%20Isha%20Ambani%2C%20others%20as%20directors%20of%20Jio%20Financial%20Services%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700138091000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-08%2F22%2Ffull%2F1692674822-4327.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Frbi-approves-isha-ambani-others-as-directors-of-jio-financial-services-123111600862_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20July%202023%2C%20the%20company%20had%20informed%20the%20exchanges%20about%20the%20appointment%20of%20the%20three%20directors%2C%20which%20was%20subject%20to%20approval%20from%20the%20central%20bank%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Frbi-approves-isha-ambani-others-as-directors-of-jio-financial-services-123111600862_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Frbi-approves-isha-ambani-others-as-directors-of-jio-financial-services-123111600862_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Frbi-approves-isha-ambani-others-as-directors-of-jio-financial-services-123111600862_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22By%20Coming%20to%20the%20Aid%20of%20Myanmar%20Soldiers%2C%20India%20Signals%20Willingness%20to%20Support%20the%20Junta%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15111451%2FThe-Wire-77.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIndia%20came%20to%20the%20unexpected%20aid%20of%20the%20Myanmar%20military%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20on%20the%20night%20of%20November%2012%2C%20when%20it%20allowed%2046%20soldiers%20of%20the%20Burmese%20junta%20to%20enter%20neighbouring%20Mizoram.%20The%20Myanmarese%20soldiers%20were%20trying%20to%20escape%20from%20Chin%20pro-democracy%20militias%20who%20overran%20their%20camps%20in%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20Chin%20state%2C%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20Mizoram%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unusual%20SOS%20request%20from%20the%20Myanmarese%20junta%20first%20came%20to%20the%20Indian%20embassy%20in%20Naypidaw%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20conveyed%20the%20urgency%20of%20the%20request%20to%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20instructions%20went%20out%20from%20New%20Delhi%20to%20security%20officials%20in%20the%20North-East%20to%20allow%20the%20Myanmarese%20soldiers%20to%20enter%20Mizoram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mizoram%20state%20police%20took%20charge%20of%20the%20soldiers%20early%20Monday%20morning.%20One%20day%20later%2C%20they%20were%20airlifted%20to%20the%20Moreh%20border%20in%20Manipur.%20From%20Moreh%2C%C2%A039%C2%A0soldiers%20were%20sent%20across%2C%20via%20the%20established%20border%20crossing%20point%2C%20to%20Tamu%20on%20the%20Myanmar%20side.%20Seven%20more%20soldiers%20were%20expected%20to%20return%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20perhaps%20the%20first%20time%20that%20India%20has%20rescued%20soldiers%20of%20another%20country%E2%80%99s%20army%20fleeing%C2%A0the%C2%A0fighting%20on%20their%20own%20soil.%20It%20signals%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20increasing%20willingness%20to%20collaborate%20with%20the%20military%20regime%20in%20Myanmar%20in%20the%20protection%20of%20its%20own%20national%20interest%C2%A0despite%20the%20junta%E2%80%99s%20shaky%20hold%20on%20the%20country%3Cb%3E%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20the%20Myanmar%20military%E2%80%99s%20defeat%20in%C2%A0the%20Shan%20state%20on%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20north-east%20border%20with%20China%2C%20the%20incident%20is%20a%20further%20embarrassment%20to%20the%20junta%2C%20which%20has%20been%20struggling%20to%20establish%20its%20writ%20since%20seizing%20power%20in%20a%20coup%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20certainly%20not%20been%20easy.%20Armed%20pro-democracy%20militias%2C%20called%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Defence%20Forces%20(PDF)%2C%20have%20taken%20back%20large%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20from%20the%20Myanmar%20military.%20The%20PDF%20has%20declared%20its%20allegiance%20to%20the%20National%20Unity%20Government%2C%20which%20handsomely%20won%20the%20February%202021%20election%2C%20which%20was%20soon%20after%20voided%20by%20the%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20time%20this%20year%20that%20fighting%20between%20the%20junta%20and%20pro-democracy%20forces%20in%20Myanmar%20has%20spilled%20over%20into%20India.%20In%20January%2C%20the%20junta%20bombed%20the%20pro-democracy%20Chin%20National%20Front%20(CNF)%20headquarters%20called%20Camp%20Victoria%2C%20located%20on%20the%20border%20with%C2%A0Champhai%20in%20Mizoram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fsecurity-forces-send-back-39-myanmar-soldiers-taking-refuge-in-mizoram%5C%22%3ESecurity%20Forces%20Send%20Back%2039%20Myanmar%20Soldiers%20Taking%20Refuge%20in%20Mizoram%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShrapnel%20fell%20into%20the%20Tiau%20river%20that%20flows%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20forming%20a%20natural%20boundary%2C%20and%20destroyed%20a%20vehicle%2C%20sending%20people%20in%20the%20area%20fleeing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20the%20fighting%20claimed%20one%20life%20and%20injured%20another%20person%20in%20a%20Chin%20refugee%20camp%20inside%20Mizoram%20close%20to%20the%20border.%20The%20camp%20was%20hit%20by%20shrapnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20felt%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20Myanmar%20military%20coup%20in%20other%20ways%20too.%20More%20than%2040%2C000%20Chin%20refugees%20from%20Myanmar%20have%20taken%20refuge%20in%20Mizoram%20since%20the%20February%202021%20coup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%C2%A0the%20fighting%C2%A0triggered%20a%20fresh%20influx%20of%20civilian%C2%A0refugees%20into%20Mizoram%C2%A0to%20save%20themselves%20from%20getting%20caught%20in%20the%20crossfire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20episode%20in%20Indian-Myanmar%20military%20collaboration%20began%20late%20Sunday%20(November%2012)%2C%20when%20Chin%20Defence%20Forces%20and%20other%20pro-democracy%20groups%20attacked%20two%20military%20posts%20in%20Rehkhawdar%20town%20in%20Chin%20state%20to%20wrest%20it%20from%20the%20junta.%20The%20CDF%20captured%20the%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERehkhawdar%20is%20located%20opposite%20Zokhawthar%20in%C2%A0Mizoram%E2%80%99s%C2%A0Champhai%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20fighting%20raged%20through%20Sunday%20night%2C%20Zokhawthar%2C%20which%20already%20hosts%20some%205%2C000%20Chin%20refugees%2C%20took%20in%20another%20batch%20of%204%2C000%20civilians.%20Thousands%20of%20civilian%20refugees%20crossed%20the%20Tiau%20river%20and%20came%20into%20Mizoram%20to%20escape%20the%20fighting%2C%20according%20to%20Vanlalchanna%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20Myanmar%20Refugees%20Relief%20Committee%20of%20Mizoram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20two%20places%20are%20very%20close.%20Some%20are%20staying%20in%20camps%2C%20some%20are%20staying%20in%20homes%20of%20people%20they%20know%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Vanlalchanna%2C%20whose%20organisation%20is%20helping%20with%20food%20rations%20and%20other%20arrangements%20for%20the%20refugees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Indian%20security%20sources%2C%20the%20soldiers%20in%20Rehkhawdar%20were%20completely%20cut%20off%20on%20the%20Myanmar%20side%2C%20and%20had%20no%20way%20of%20finding%20their%20way%20back%20to%20safety.%20So%20they%20got%20in%20touch%20with%20Indian%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20border%20security%20management%2C%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20cooperation%20and%20understanding%20between%20security%20forces%20on%20both%20sides.%20So%20they%20felt%20they%20could%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20Indian%20side%20for%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20Indian%20security%20official%20told%20%3Cem%3EAwaaz%20South%20Asia%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Mizoram%2C%20where%20the%20rescued%20soldiers%20spent%20a%20night%20in%20Zorkhwathar%20police%20station%2C%20resentment%20against%20the%20Myanmar%20Army%20is%20high.%20That%E2%80%99s%20because%20Chin%20refugees%20bring%20first-hand%20accounts%20of%20aerial%20bombing%20and%20shelling%20by%20the%20Myanmar%20military%2C%20which%20has%20also%20burnt%20down%20entire%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20from%20Zorkhawthar%2C%20Ramtharnghaka%2C%20president%20of%20the%20local%20chapter%20of%20the%20Young%20Mizo%20Association%2C%20an%20NGO%20that%20has%20been%20actively%20supporting%20the%20refugees%2C%20said%20the%20people%20of%20the%20area%20had%20gathered%20outside%20the%20police%20station%20where%20the%20soldiers%20were%20being%20kept%20and%20had%20demanded%20%E2%80%9Cto%20see%20the%20faces%20of%20the%20soldiers%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20police%20told%20them%20that%20was%20not%20possible%2C%20and%20the%20people%20dispersed%20obediently%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20two%20helicopters%20landed%20in%20Hnalan%20village%20in%20Myanmar%2C%20picked%20up%20the%20Myanmarese%20soldiers%20in%20two%20batches%20each%20and%20evacuated%20them%20to%20the%20Manipuri%20town%20of%20Moreh%2C%20from%20where%20they%20were%20sent%20back%20by%20road%20across%20to%20Tamu%20in%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F12153337%2F2021_Myanmar_Armed_Forces_Day_05-e1699949248972.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F12153337%2F2021_Myanmar_Armed_Forces_Day_05-e1699949248972.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F12153337%2F2021_Myanmar_Armed_Forces_Day_05-e1699949248972-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F12153337%2F2021_Myanmar_Armed_Forces_Day_05-e1699949248972-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F12153337%2F2021_Myanmar_Armed_Forces_Day_05-e1699949248972-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-640151%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMin%20Aung%20Hlaing.%20Photo%3A%20Mil.ru%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20CC%20BY%204.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20fighting%20subsiding%2C%20for%20now%2C%20some%20of%20the%20civilian%20refugees%20have%20gone%20back%20too%2C%20said%20Vanlalchanna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20is%20no%20telling%20when%20India%20will%20again%20be%20drawn%20into%20the%20arc%20of%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20instability.%20So%20far%20India%20has%20signalled%20that%20it%20will%20work%20with%20the%20junta%20to%20secure%20its%20own%20interests.%20India%20is%20also%20keenly%20aware%20that%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20other%20neighbours%2C%20especially%20China%2C%20keep%20a%20close%20watch%20on%20developments%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Deputy%20National%20Security%20Adviser%20Vikram%20Misri%20was%20in%20Naypidaw%20along%20with%20representatives%20from%20Thailand%20and%20China%2C%20for%20the%20anniversary%20commemoration%20of%20a%202015%20ceasefire%20agreement%20with%20ethnic%20armed%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%202021%20military%20coup%20frayed%20the%20ceasefire%20and%20it%20is%20dead%20in%20all%20but%20name.%20The%20Myanmar%20military%E2%80%99s%20attempts%20to%20revive%20this%20truce%20and%20separate%20the%20ethnic%20armed%20organisations%20from%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Defence%20Forces%20have%20so%20far%20failed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202015%2C%20eight%20ethnic%20armed%20groups%20signed%20the%C2%A0National%20Ceasefire%20Agreement.%20In%20February%202018%2C%20two%20more%20ethnic%20rebel%20groups%20joined%20the%20cease-fire%20brokered%20by%20Aung%20San%20Suu%20Kyi%E2%80%99s%20civilian%20government%2C%20bringing%20the%20total%20number%20of%20signatories%20to%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20three%20pro-democracy%20groups%20that%20signed%20the%20truce%20agreement%20are%20now%20allied%20with%20the%20PDF%2C%20including%20the%20Chin%20National%20Front%2C%20which%20did%20not%20attend%20last%20month%E2%80%99s%20anniversary%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Arakkan%20Army%20and%20the%20Myanmar%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20Army%20which%C2%A0also%C2%A0signed%20the%20ceasefire%20are%20part%20of%20the%20Three%20Brotherhood%20Alliance%20that%20delivered%20a%20crushing%20blow%20to%20the%20junta%20in%20Shan%20state%20on%20China%E2%80%99s%20border.%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20military%20defeat%20in%20Chin%20state%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20Mizoram%20border%20underlines%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20face%20of%20the%20Myanmar%20military%E2%80%99s%20weakening%20hold%2C%20India%20may%20soon%20have%20to%20take%20a%20call%20on%20whether%20it%20can%20put%20all%20its%20eggs%20in%20that%20basket.%20Or%2C%20whether%20it%20should%20start%20reaching%20out%20more%20proactively%20than%20it%20has%20done%20so%20far%20to%20the%20National%20Unity%20Government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fawaazsouthasia.com%2Farticle.php%2Fwhen-indian-army-rescued-myanmar-soldiers-escaping-from-prodemocracy-militias-back-home-into-mizoram%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20first%20appeared%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fawaazsouthasia.com%2F%5C%22%3EAwaazSouthAsia%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENirupama%20Subramanian%20is%20Founder-Editor%20of%3C%2Fem%3E%20AwaazSouthAsia.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700137491000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15111451%2FThe-Wire-77.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fby-coming-to-the-aid-of-myanmar-soldiers-india-signals-willingness-to-support-the-junta%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20November%2012%2C%20India%20allowed%2046%20soldiers%20of%20the%20Burmese%20junta%20to%20enter%20neighbouring%20Mizoram.%20This%20is%20perhaps%20the%20first%20time%20that%20India%20has%20rescued%20soldiers%20of%20another%20country's%20army%20fleeing%C2%A0the%C2%A0fighting%20on%20their%20own%20soil.%22%2C%22author