0first%20phase%20of%20its%20operation%20in%20Gaza%20and%20with%20it%20comes%20a%20dilemma.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A953%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fisrael-now-occupies-gaza-having-completely-destroyed-it-so-what-does-it-do-with-the-smouldering-ruins-13009530%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fisrael-now-occupies-gaza-having-completely-destroyed-it-so-what-does-it-do-with-the-smouldering-ruins-13009530%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fisrael-now-occupies-gaza-having-completely-destroyed-it-so-what-does-it-do-with-the-smouldering-ruins-13009530%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20World%20Must%20Wake%20Up%20to%20Israel's%20Lies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17151101%2FF8PxlS-a4AAO8nS.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20of%20Israel%20scored%20a%20major%20victory%20in%20its%20war%20against%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20when%20it%20captured%20%E2%80%98al-Shifa%E2%80%99%20hospital%20on%20Wednesday%20(November%2016).%20Israeli%20soldiers%2C%20the%20IDF%2C%20were%20seen%20foisting%20their%20flag%20on%20the%20top%20of%20the%20hospital.%20Their%20claim%20was%20that%20this%20hospital%20was%20a%20cover%20for%20the%20military%20operation%20of%20Hamas.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20was%20much%20more%20sinister%20than%20that.%20It%20was%20the%20base%20from%20which%20Hamas%20was%20conducting%20its%20military%20action.%20This%20claim%20made%20al-Shifa%20a%20%E2%80%98legitimate%E2%80%99%20target%20for%20Israeli%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20a%20day%20before%20the%20Israeli%20forces%20tightened%20their%20siege%20on%20the%20hospital%2C%20the%20Pentagon%20felt%20it%20necessary%20to%20justify%20this%20by%20claiming%20that%20it%20had%20credible%20intelligence%20inputs%20that%20al-Shifa%20was%20being%20used%20by%20Hamas.%20When%20asked%20about%20the%20source%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20refused%20to%20comment%20but%20admitted%20that%20the%20USA%20did%20not%20have%20its%20own%20boots%20on%20the%20ground.%20Which%20is%20to%20say%20that%20what%20it%20is%20presenting%20before%20the%20world%20as%20evidence%20is%20supplied%20by%20Israel%20and%20there%20is%20no%20independent%20party%20to%20verify%20its%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20Israel%20has%20been%20lying%20all%20along%20was%20proven%20after%20it%20conquered%20the%20hospital%20which%20it%20alleged%20was%20a%20military%20base%20of%20its%20enemy.%20It%20was%20reported%20by%20sympathetic%20media%20that%20%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20video%20filmed%20at%20al-Shifa%20Hospital%20in%20Gaza%20City%2C%20a%20military%20spokesman%2C%20Lt.%20Col.%20Jonathan%20Conricus%2C%20showed%20about%2010%20guns%2C%20ammunition%2C%20protective%20vests%20and%20Hamas%20military%20uniforms%2C%20some%20of%20which%20he%20said%20were%20hidden%20behind%20M.R.I.%20machines%2C%20others%20in%20nearby%20storage%20units%20and%20some%20behind%20what%20he%20described%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98blast-proof%20door.'%E2%80%9D%20But%20the%20media%20platform%20took%20caution%20to%20say%20that%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20assertions%20made%20in%20the%20video%20could%20not%20be%20independently%20verified.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F685067%2Fus-based-journalists-condemn-israels-killing-of-journalists-in-gaza%2F%5C%22%3EUS-Based%20Reporters%20Condemn%20%E2%80%98Israel%E2%80%99s%20Killing%20of%20Journalists%20in%20Gaza%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20independent%20verification%2C%20no%20third%20party%20check%20and%20yet%2C%20we%20are%20asked%20to%20trust%20Israel.%20Only%20because%20NATO%20and%20the%20Americans%20say%20so%3F%20We%20are%20shamed%20if%20we%20raise%20doubt.%20And%20asked%20how%20can%20we%20not%20trust%20a%20country%20like%20Israel%3F%20Is%20it%20not%20the%20only%20true%20democracy%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%3F%20Does%20it%20not%20espouse%20the%20values%20of%20enlightenment%3F%20And%20above%20all%2C%20was%20it%20not%20wronged%20on%20October%207%20and%20does%20it%20not%20have%20the%20right%20to%20defend%20itself%3F%20The%20last%20one%20seems%20to%20click%20all%20arguments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernments%20have%20been%20asking%20us%20to%20believe%20what%20Israel%20presents%20before%20us%20as%20evidence%20because%20it%20is%20a%20victim%20of%20Hamas%20%E2%80%93%20an%20assertion%20presented%20as%20truth%20without%20verification.%20American%20political%20scientist%20Norman%20Finkelstein%20rightly%20asked%2C%20even%20if%20slightly%20sarcastically%2C%20as%20to%20why%20%E2%80%9CHamas%20didn%E2%80%99t%20take%20the%20weapons%20to%20its%20command-and-control%20centre%20beneath%20al-Shifa.%20No%2C%20it%20decided%20to%20leave%20these%20weapons%20lying%20around%20in%20the%20radiology%20ward%20so%20as%20to%20give%20Israel%20a%20photo-op.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20it%20was%20all%20a%20set%20up%20by%20Israel%20is%20so%20clear%20from%20the%20video%20that%20it%20was%20immediately%20called%20out%20and%20laughed%20at.%20The%20video%20was%20so%20embarrassing%20that%20the%20IDF%20quietly%20deleted%20it%20without%20any%20explanation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29182252%2FF9l7tShWEAAHqvL.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29182252%2FF9l7tShWEAAHqvL.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29182252%2FF9l7tShWEAAHqvL-300x140.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29182252%2FF9l7tShWEAAHqvL-1024x476.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682394%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22558%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDestroyed%20buildings%20in%20Gaza.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40UNRWA%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20explanation%20because%20Israel%20knows%20that%20it%20does%20not%20need%20to%20explain%20its%20lies.%20They%20are%20seen%20as%20necessary%20by%20its%20patrons%20or%20allies%20to%20justify%20its%20massacre%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20al-Shifa-lie%20was%20the%20latest%20but%20it%20was%20preceded%20by%20several%20others%20that%20tell%20us%20about%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20Israeli%20state.%20One%20of%20the%20many%20close%20observers%20of%20Israeli%20propaganda%2C%20journalist%20Dalia%20Hatuqa%2C%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDaliaHatuqa%2Fstatus%2F1724795309698752831%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Earchiving%3C%2Fa%3E%20them.%20Let%20us%20take%20a%20look%20at%20some%20of%20them%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20%E2%80%98infamous%E2%80%99%20calendar%3A%20They%20showed%20a%20paper%20on%20a%20wall%20of%20a%20hospital%20that%20they%20said%20was%20a%20%E2%80%98list%20of%20terrorist%20names%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20Those%20who%20read%20Arabic%20recognised%20it%20as%20having%20the%20days%20of%20the%20week%20written%20down.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThey%20claimed%20they%E2%80%99re%20sending%20incubators%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20despite%20the%20issue%20being%20the%20lack%20of%20fuel%20needed%20to%20run%20said%20incubators%2C%20which%20are%20available%20anyway.%20Three%20premature%20babies%20and%20many%20ICU%20patients%20died%20as%20a%20result.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThey%20claimed%20that%20projectiles%20fired%20by%20Palestinian%20militants%20hit%20al-Shifa%20hospital%20on%20November%2010.%20The%20NYT%20debunked%20that%20claim%20and%20showed%20that%20it%20was%20Israeli%20shelling%20that%20led%20to%20the%20death%20of%207%20Palestinians%20there%20that%20day.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThey%20said%20they%20targeted%20a%20car%20with%20%E2%80%9Cterrorists%E2%80%9D%20in%20Lebanon.%20It%20emerged%20that%20the%20vehicle%20had%20three%20little%20girls%2C%20their%20mother%20and%20grandmother.%20Only%20the%20mom%20survived%20the%20shelling.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThey%20showed%20a%20video%20of%20a%20nurse%20in%20a%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%20saying%20Hamas%20is%20holding%20people%20as%20human%20shields.%20That%20video%20was%20debunked%20as%20fake%20and%20that%20the%20woman%20was%20a%20Mexican-Israeli%20actor.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%20the%20claim%20was%20that%20Hamas%20was%20using%20al-Shifa%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccommand%20centre%E2%80%9D%20to%20hold%20hostages%2C%20and%20that%20they%20stored%20weapons%20there.%20Now%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20tunnels.%20A%20senior%20Israeli%20official%20said%20that%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20IDF%20operation%20at%20the%20al-Shifa%20hospital%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20to%20rescue%20hostages%20but%20to%20locate%20and%20expose%20a%20Hamas%20tunnels%20hub%20that%20connects%20the%20hospital%20with%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20Gaza%20strip.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELie%20after%20lie.%20And%20one%20after%20the%20other%2C%20they%20get%20debunked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20and%20should%20be%20treated%20as%20true%20by%20any%20sensible%20person%20is%20what%20independent%20sources%2C%20that%20is%20those%20who%20are%20neither%20Palestinian%20nor%20Israeli%2C%20have%20been%20saying.%20Those%20who%20have%20worked%20at%20al-Shifa%20for%20decades.%20They%20have%20been%20refusing%20Israeli%20claims%20of%20the%20hospital%20being%20a%20military%20base%20or%20cover%20of%20Hamas.%20But%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20powerful%20allies%20choose%20to%20believe%20its%20lies.%20Or%2C%20knowing%20well%20that%20Israel%20was%20lying%20they%20decided%20to%20back%20it.%20After%20all%2C%20are%20these%20not%20the%20same%20countries%20which%20had%20invented%20the%20truth%20of%20Iraq%20hoarding%20WMD%20to%20invade%20the%20country%20and%20destroy%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F685036%2Fisraeli-forces-raid-al-shifa-hospital-complex-communications-blackout-in-gaza%2F%5C%22%3EIsraeli%20Forces%20Raid%20al-Shifa%20Hospital%20Complex%2C%20Communications%20Blackout%20in%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELies%20are%20necessary%20because%20they%20work.%20They%20work%20because%20they%20appeal%20to%20our%20prejudices.%20It%20is%20more%20likely%20that%20the%20civilised%20world%20would%20accept%20that%20Hamas%20beheaded%20babies%20and%20burnt%20them%20because%20there%20is%20already%20a%20belief%20that%20Hamas%20is%20made%20of%20non-humans.%20They%20are%20capable%20of%20such%20horrible%20act!%20But%20Israeli%20leaders%20are%20part%20of%20us.%20They%20have%20been%20trained%20in%20modern%20institutions.%20They%20share%20our%20sensibility.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20they%20follow%20the%20famed%20European%20values.%20They%20have%20to%20be%20trustworthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20lie%20first.%20Because%20it%20sticks%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20the%20people.%20Then%20after%20it%20is%20found%20to%20be%20a%20lie%20you%20claim%20that%20it%20was%20immaterial%20because%20irrespective%20of%20truth%2C%20was%20it%20not%20necessary%20to%20attack%20Gaza%3F%20Was%20it%20not%20important%20to%20remove%20Hamas%3F%20If%20the%20lie%20serves%20a%20purpose%2C%20why%20not%20use%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20what%20we%20heard%20after%20the%20USA%20and%20UK%20shamelessly%20accepted%20that%20they%20were%20lying%20about%20the%20WMD%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20Saddam%20Hussain%20was%20a%20despot%20more%20important.%20So%20was%20removing%20him%20not%20a%20duty%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20we%20are%20asked%20to%20disregard%20the%20fact%20of%20Israel%20lying%20because%20removing%20the%20horrible%20Hamas%20is%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20is%20more%20frightening%20is%20that%20even%20after%20being%20proven%20wrong%2C%20lies%20are%20repeated%20by%20powerful%20people.%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20repeated%20only%20yesterday%20the%20lie%20of%20Hamas%20beheading%20and%20burning%20babies%20even%20after%20it%20was%20debunked%20and%20Israel%20itself%20went%20silent%20about%20it.%20This%20lie%20is%20repeated%20brazenly%20because%20the%20lier%20knows%20that%20there%20is%20a%20constituency%20for%20it.%20He%20also%20repeated%20the%20lie%20that%20Hamas%20was%20working%20from%20under%20the%20hospitals%20even%20when%20Israel%20has%20failed%20to%20provide%20any%20evidence%20for%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lie%20of%20hospitals%20being%20command%20centres%20or%20hiding%20tunnels%20was%20used%20by%20the%20West%20to%20give%20a%20free%20pass%20to%20Israel%20to%20attack%20hospitals.%20Then%20Israel%20said%20that%20everyone%20it%20attacks%20or%20kills%20is%20bound%20to%20be%20a%20Hamas-front%20or%20accomplice.%20So%2C%20doctors%2C%20journalists%20and%20United%20Nations%20workers%20have%20all%20been%20declared%20as%20Hamas%20fronts%20and%20therefore%20legitimate%20targets.%20There%20is%20no%20outrage%20in%20the%20civilised%20world!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20is%20Israel%20so%20confident%20that%20its%20lies%20would%20be%20bought%20by%20the%20civilised%20world%3F%20Is%20it%20because%20there%20is%20a%20powerful%20opinion%20which%20supports%20the%20elimination%20of%20people%20like%20the%20Palestinians%20who%20are%20seen%20as%20backward%20and%20less%20human%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20might%20sound%20slightly%20offending%20but%20is%20it%20not%20the%20case%20that%2C%20as%20an%20observer%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CIsrael%E2%80%99s%20obvious%20lies%20aren%E2%80%99t%20meant%20to%20convince%20people%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20kill%20Palestinian%20children%2C%20they%20are%20meant%20to%20placate%20the%20guilt%20of%20people%20who%20DO%20want%20to%20kill%20Palestinian%20children.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20encouraging%20is%20that%20there%20is%20an%20equally%20significant%20number%20of%20people%20even%20in%20the%20countries%20which%20are%20officially%20backing%20Israel%20who%20are%20not%20ready%20to%20be%20driven%20by%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20lies.%20Who%20are%20not%20ready%20to%20give%20Israel%20a%20free%20pass%20and%20who%20know%20that%20the%20most%20ethical%20thing%20is%20to%20stand%20by%20the%20oppressed%20people.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20they%20have%20to%20stand%20with%20the%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700134850000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17151101%2FF8PxlS-a4AAO8nS.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fthe-world-must-wake-up-to-israels-lies%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israeli%20propaganda%20is%20deemed%20necessary%20by%20its%20patrons%20or%20allies%20to%20justify%20its%20massacre%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fthe-world-must-wake-up-to-israels-lies%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%20%7C%20%E2%80%98I%E2%80%99m%20Extremely%20Confident%20We%E2%80%99ll%20Have%20a%20Good%20FTA%20With%20India%E2%80%99%3A%20UK%20Deputy%20Foreign%20Secretary%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16165153%2FKT-16-Nov-C.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20an%20interview%20to%20discuss%20the%20consequences%20and%20implications%20of%20the%20appointment%20of%20David%20Cameron%2C%20a%20former%20British%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20as%20the%20new%20British%20foreign%20secretary%2C%20Britain%E2%80%99s%20deputy%20foreign%20secretary%20and%20one%20of%20the%20Conservative%20Party%E2%80%99s%20MPs%20of%20longest%20standing%2C%20has%20said%20that%20he%20is%20%E2%80%9Cextremely%20confident%E2%80%9D%20that%20India%20and%20Britain%20will%20be%20able%20to%20agree%20upon%20a%20good%20Free%20Trade%20Agreement%20(FTA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20was%20reluctant%20to%20say%20whether%20it%20would%20happen%2