%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F10163131%2FD3UNUZfXsAARk-y.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERaipur%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20On%20November%203%2C%20in%20a%20surprise%20raid%20at%20a%20housing%20board%20colony%20house%20in%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20Bhilai%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20arrested%20a%2034-year-old%20man%2C%20Asim%20Das.%20Das%20was%20arrested%20along%20with%20a%20Chhattisgarh%20police%20constable%20Bheem%20Yadav%20in%20the%20Mahadev%20app%20betting%20and%20money%20laundering%20case.%20Yadav%20is%20the%20third%20police%20personnel%20arrested%20by%20ED%20in%20this%20case%2C%20and%20Das%2C%20a%20driver%20by%20profession%2C%20was%20allegedly%20running%20a%20chapter%20of%20the%20Mahadev%20App%20from%20Supela%2C%20a%20suburb%20in%20Bhilai.%20After%20their%20arrest%2C%20ED%20released%20a%20press%20release%2C%20alleging%20that%20kickbacks%20amounting%20to%20Rs%20508%20crore%20were%20received%20by%20Chhattisgarh%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFollowing%20the%20ED%20press%20release%2C%20Shubham%20Soni%2C%20the%20alleged%20owner%20of%20the%20Mahadev%20Betting%20App%2C%20released%20a%20statement%20alleging%20that%20he%20paid%20security%20money%20to%20a%202008%20batch%20Indian%20Police%20Service%20officer%20%E2%80%9CVerma%20Ji%E2%80%9D%20and%20even%20held%20meetings%20with%20Baghel%20and%20his%20son%2C%20%E2%80%9CBittu%20Bhaiya%E2%80%9D.%20Following%20this%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20in%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20alleged%20that%20Soni%20in%20his%20video%20claimed%20that%20he%20had%20links%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%20house%20through%20Baghel%E2%80%99s%20political%20advisor%20Vinod%20Verma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20poll-bound%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20where%2070%20out%20of%2090%20seats%20are%20set%20to%20go%20to%20polls%20on%20November%2017%2C%20the%20press%20release%20and%20the%20video%20had%20an%20intentional%20effect%3A%20all%20conversations%20turned%20towards%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20chief%20minister.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20have%20been%20saying%20for%20months%20has%20finally%20come%20to%20fruition.%20The%20ED%20and%20IT%20are%20here%20to%20malign%20me.%20Look%20how%20shrewd%20ED%20is%20%E2%80%94%20after%20accusing%20me%20of%20taking%20Rs%20508%20crore%20based%20on%20the%20statement%20of%20an%20unknown%20person%2C%20they%20have%20said%20in%20a%20short%20sentence%20that%20his%20statement%20is%20a%20subject%20of%20investigation.%20Issuing%20a%20press%20release%20without%20any%20investigation%20only%20reveals%20the%20ill-intent%20of%20ED%20and%20the%20Central%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20Baghel%20said%20on%20November%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchhattisgarh-ed-conducts-raids-at-locations-linked-to-3-of-bhupesh-baghels-aids%5C%22%3EChhattisgarh%3A%20ED%20Conducts%20Raids%20at%20Locations%20Linked%20to%203%20of%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%E2%80%99s%20Aides%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBaghel%20and%20Congress%20party%20leaders%20have%20continuously%20maintained%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20using%20central%20investigating%20agencies%20to%20destabilise%20the%20Congress%20governments%20in%20poll-bound%20states%20of%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20with%20Baghel%20even%20commenting%20that%20the%20real%20challenger%20from%20BJP%20against%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20upcoming%20election%20is%20ED.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBetween%20January%20and%20October%20this%20year%2C%20the%20ED%20released%2011%20press%20releases%20of%20actions%20across%20Chhattisgarh.%20Among%20the%20accused%20named%20in%20the%20press%20statements%20were%20Saumya%20Chaurasia%2C%20a%20Chhattisgarh%20state%20civil%20service%20officer%20who%20was%20ex-assistant%20to%20CM%20Baghel%2C%20and%20Anwar%20Dhebar%2C%20brother%20of%20Raipur%20mayor%20Aijaz%20Dhebar.%20It%20also%20attached%20properties%20of%20Congress%20leader%20Devendra%20Yadav%2C%20Ramgopal%20Verma%20and%20others.%20Yadav%2C%20the%20youngest%20MLA%20from%20the%20Bhilai%20city%20seat%2C%20is%20contesting%20again%20from%20the%20same%20seat%20and%20is%20known%20to%20be%20a%20Baghel%20loyalist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20ED%2C%20in%20its%20dozen%20press%20releases%20just%20this%20year%20%E2%80%93%20(in%202022%2C%20the%20ED%20released%20only%202%20press%20notes%20from%20Chhattisgarh)%20%E2%80%93%20went%20from%20ascribing%20the%20actions%20to%20%E2%80%9Chigher%20powers%E2%80%9D%20to%20hinting%20at%20political%20involvement.%20In%20the%20Mahadev%20app%20money%20laundering%20case%2C%20the%20central%20investigating%20agency%20raided%20the%20house%20of%20former%20journalist%20Vinod%20Verma%2C%20political%20advisor%20and%20close%20aide%20of%20CM%20Baghel.%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20showing%20them%20all%20the%20records%2C%20they%20seized%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20belongings.%20They%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20leave%20the%20jewellery%20my%20wife%20wears%20regularly%20on%20her%20ears%20and%20nose%2C%E2%80%9D%20Verma%20had%20said%20after%20his%20house%20was%20raided%20on%20August%2023%2C%20Baghel%E2%80%99s%20birthday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%2C%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20competitive%20campaigns%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EEarlier%20on%20November%203%2C%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20who%20was%20visiting%20the%20state%20to%20conduct%20political%20rallies%2C%20launched%20the%20BJP%20manifesto%20for%20the%20upcoming%20election%2C%20in%20Raipur.%20The%20Manifesto%20titled%20%3Cem%3EModi%20Ki%20Guarantee%3C%2Fem%3E%20didn%E2%80%99t%20gain%20much%20traction.%20In%20a%20slew%20of%20promises%20focused%20on%20direct%20benefit%20transfers%2C%20the%20BJP%20promised%20much%20less%20than%20the%20ruling%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CPaddy%20has%20always%20been%20an%20election%20issue%20in%20the%20state.%20Farmer%20factions%20were%20waiting%20for%20some%20bigger%20scheme%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20but%20they%20seem%20to%20have%20only%20tried%20to%20one-up%20the%20Congress.%20By%20increasing%20one%20quintal%20in%20the%20acquisition%20quota%20and%20raising%20the%20price%20slightly%2C%20they%20have%20challenged%20Congress%2C%20albeit%20weakly.%20However%2C%20without%20the%20promise%20of%20a%20loan%20waiver%2C%20the%20challenge%20is%20empty%20and%20means%20less%20for%20the%20small%20to%20medium%20farmer.%20Although%20the%20payment%20of%20money%20in%20one-go%20instead%20of%20instalments%20might%20work%20for%20a%20large%20group%20of%20farmers%20in%20the%20hinterland%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20political%20commentator%20with%20a%20strong%20grasp%20of%20agrarian%20politics%20commented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16164306%2FF-56lSvWEAAHcSa.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221159%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16164306%2FF-56lSvWEAAHcSa.jpg%201159w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16164306%2FF-56lSvWEAAHcSa-290x300.jpg%20290w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16164306%2FF-56lSvWEAAHcSa-989x1024.jpg%20989w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685089%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EChhattisgarh%20chief%20minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20during%20election%20campaign%20in%20the%20state.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%2F%40bhupeshbaghel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EEven%20as%20PM%20Modi%2C%20Union%20home%20minister%20Shah%20and%20other%20BJP%20bigwigs%20like%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20and%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%20campaign%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Baghel%20has%20repeatedly%20maintained%20that%20the%20ED%20and%20IT%20are%20real%20faces%20of%20BJP%20in%20the%20election.%20Even%20the%20BJP%20on%20the%20ground%20seems%20to%20have%20utilised%20the%20investigation%20conducted%20by%20the%20central%20agencies%20heavily%20in%20their%20campaigning%20material.%20Through%20apps%20and%20digital%20and%20print%20magazines%20published%20enlisting%20all%20the%20scams%20the%20government%20is%20accused%20of%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20entire%20campaign%20is%20designed%20around%20the%20corruption%20of%20the%20Congress%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20can%20entail%20all%20the%20details%20through%20various%20media%2C%20but%20it%20is%20merely%20a%20topic%20of%20gossip%2C%20nothing%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20political%20analyst%20in%20the%20state%20said.%20He%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20two%20major%20reasons%20for%20it%2C%20primarily%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20was%20accused%20of%20a%20lot%20of%20corruption.%20Second%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20failed%20to%20prove%20beyond%20doubt%20that%20corruption%20is%20affecting%20the%20people.%20The%20investigation%20has%20led%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20speculation%20and%20technical%20browbeating%2C%20but%20beyond%20the%20allegation%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20siphoning%20off%20money%20to%20supply%20to%20the%20Delhi%20headquarters%2C%20not%20much%20has%20gotten%20through%20to%20the%20public%20on%20the%20ground.%20All%20of%20this%20is%20helping%20Baghel%E2%80%99s%20narrative%2C%20that%20he%20is%20being%20targeted%20by%20the%20Central%20BJP%20further.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchhattisgarh-numbers-poll-congress-bjp-operation-lotus%5C%22%3EChhattisgarh%3A%20To%C2%A0Remain%C2%A0Impervious%C2%A0to%C2%A0a%C2%A0Future%20Operation%20Lotus%2C%20Can%20Congress%20Pull%20Off%20a%20Big%20Victory%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EEven%20as%20state%20BJP%20leaders%20are%20still%20infighting%2C%20the%20central%20leadership%20of%20the%20party%20seems%20to%20have%20made%20Baghel%20a%20worthy%20target%3B%20countering%20his%20tactic%20through%20a%20response%2C%20including%20the%20appointment%20of%20an%20OBC%20state%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAll%20this%20should%20bolster%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20image%20and%20public%20perception.%20And%20yet%2C%20the%20Congress%20seems%20to%20be%20feeling%20insecure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EEven%20as%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20manifesto%20went%20above%20and%20beyond%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%2C%20days%20after%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20voting%2C%20the%20Congress%20added%20to%20its%20announcements%2C%20a%20Rs%2015%2C000%20scheme%20for%20women.%20A%20reaction%20to%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Mahtari%20Vandan%20Scheme%2C%20the%20Congress%20decided%20to%20pay%20women%20across%20the%20state%20Rs%203000%20more%20than%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20promises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Congress%E2%80%99%20knee-jerk%20reaction%20comes%20as%20the%20BJP%20attacks%20alleging%20a%20rise%20in%20corruption%20before%20the%2070%20constituencies%20in%20the%20state%20go%20to%20vote.%20In%202018%2C%20despite%20the%20strong%20anti-incumbency%20against%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20it%20managed%20to%20win%2012%20seats%20among%20the%2046%20seats%20spread%20in%20six%20districts%20that%20are%20set%20to%20go%20to%20poll%20on%20November%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOpposed%20not%20only%20by%20BJP%20but%20a%20combination%20of%20small%20parties%20like%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%2C%20Janta%20Congress%20Chhattisgarh%20Jogi%2C%20Hamar%20Raj%20party%2C%20Gondwana%20Gantantra%20Party%20and%20Janta%20Congress%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%20is%20also%20facing%20disgruntled%20opposition%20from%20former%20MLAs%20whose%20tickets%20were%20not%20renewed.%20Add%20to%20that%20mix%20a%20barrage%20of%20independent%20candidates%20from%20each%20seat%20who%20will%20inflict%20small%20damages%2C%20if%20at%20all%2C%20and%20Congress%20seems%20to%20be%20sitting%20a%20hard%20test%20of%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20however%2C%20is%20responding%20to%20the%20multi-faceted%20opposition%20mounted%20by%20the%20BJP%20by%20increasing%20its%20facetime%20with%20the%20public.%20Even%20as%20leaders%20are%20holding%20more%20on-ground%20rallies%2C%20Vinod%20Verma%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20informed%20the%20media%20that%20he%20was%20filing%20a%20defamation%20suit%20against%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20who%20connected%20his%20name%20to%20the%20Mahadev%20betting%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20government%20was%20the%20first%20to%20initiate%20action%20against%20the%20Mahadev%20betting%20app%2C%20with%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20police%20even%20getting%20a%20red%20corner%20notice%20issued%20against%20the%20main%20accused.%20It%20is%20a%20failure%20of%20the%20central%20BJP%20government%20that%20they%20are%20still%20at%20large%2C%E2%80%9D%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Sushil%20Anand%20Shukla%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20press%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20accused%20Asim%20Das%20has%20accepted%20in%20court%20that%20he%20was%20pressured%20to%20name%20CM%20Baghel%20in%20his%20statement.%20It%20seems%20the%20BJP%20is%20compromised%20with%20the%20owners%20of%20the%20Mahadev%20betting%20app%20and%20is%20working%20with%20them%20to%20implicate%20the%20Congress.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700134220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F10163131%2FD3UNUZfXsAARk-y.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchhattisgarh-has-the-mahadev-app-scam-paradoxically-bolstered-congresss-electoral-prospects%22%2C%22summary%22%