ess%20and%20for%20its%20faster%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hypocrisy%20and%20fraudulence%20in%20the%20confession%20and%20the%20deceit%20in%20the%20solution%20provided%20are%20obvious%20to%20those%20who%20are%20barely%20acquainted%20with%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20a%20decades-long%20demand%20for%20the%20internal%20reclassification%20of%20the%20SC%20reservation%20since%20benefits%20are%20allegedly%20accruing%20to%20a%20few%20untouchable%20castes%20within%20the%20category%20which%20were%20historically%20in%20an%20advantageous%20position%20to%20make%20use%20of%20the%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20states%20like%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20addressed%20the%20issue%20at%20the%20state%20level%20way%20back%20in%20the%201970s%20by%20providing%20one%20or%20other%20form%20of%20reclassification%20within%20the%20SC%20category%2C%20the%20issue%20still%20remains%20unaddressed%20in%20Telangana%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20government%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20undivided%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20government%20did%20heed%20to%20decade-long%20massive%20movement%20led%20by%20Krishna%20Madiga%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20Madiga%20Dandora%20and%20reclassified%20the%20SC%20reservation%2C%20but%20it%20has%20been%20since%20challenged%20in%20the%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16141908%2F400614377_1113711610123070_2354398928774795984_n.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16141908%2F400614377_1113711610123070_2354398928774795984_n.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16141908%2F400614377_1113711610123070_2354398928774795984_n-300x209.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16141908%2F400614377_1113711610123070_2354398928774795984_n-1024x713.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685051%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22836%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMRPS%20meeting%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20November%2011%2C%202023.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2FNarendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202004%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20quashed%20the%20SC%20reclassification%20order%20of%20the%20AP%20government%20in%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EE.V.%20Chinnaiah%20vs%20State%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%3C%2Fem%3E%20case%2C%20declaring%20that%20further%20reclassification%20of%20SC%20reservation%20is%20%E2%80%9Cunconstitutional%E2%80%9D.%20It%20also%20asserted%20that%20a%20state%20government%20does%20not%20have%20legislative%20competence%20to%20legislate%20on%20the%20said%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Chinnaiah%20judgement%2C%20the%20hitherto%20state-level%20reclassification%20in%20AP%20became%20null%20and%20void.%20Still%2C%20when%20the%20Punjab%20government%20resorted%20to%20providing%20preferential%20reservation%20for%20the%20most%20disadvantageous%20groups%20within%20the%20SC%20category%20during%20the%201990s%2C%20it%20was%20challenged%20against%20the%20SC%20order%20of%202004.%20In%202020%2C%20another%20five-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EDavinder%20Singh%20vs%20State%20Of%20Punjab%3C%2Fem%3E%20case%2C%20upheld%20reclassification%20as%20constitutional.%20But%20both%20judgements%20had%20to%20be%20referred%20to%20a%20higher%20bench%20since%20judgments%2C%20that%20in%20favour%20of%20and%20against%20reclassification%2C%20were%20pronounced%20by%20the%20benches%20of%20equal%20strength%2C%20of%20five%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhyderabad-modi-mrps-dalit-sub-categorisation%5C%22%3EHyderabad%3A%20With%20Modi%20Attending%20MRPS%20Meeting%2C%20Will%20Dalit%20Sub-Categorisation%20Gain%20Steam%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20order%20was%20pronounced%20in%20August%202020.%20Later%20in%202022%2C%20even%20though%20it%20came%20before%20the%20then%20Chief%20Justice%20Ramana%2C%20the%20solicitor%20general%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20did%20not%20press%20for%20the%20speedy%20constitution%20of%20a%20seven-judge%20committee%20and%20the%20case%20remained%20in%20the%20cold%20storage%20till%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meanwhile%2C%20since%20the%20%3Cem%3EChinnaiah%3C%2Fem%3E%20judgement%20foreclosed%20any%20legislative%20initiative%20of%20the%20state%20governments%20to%20provide%20social%20justice%20to%20the%20marginalised%20within%20the%20SC%20category%2C%20on%20a%20unanimous%20plea%20made%20by%20the%20AP%20assembly%2C%20the%20then%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20government%20at%20the%20centre%20constituted%20Justice%20Usha%20Mehra%20Commission%20to%20look%20into%20the%20ways%20in%20which%20internal%20reclassification%20could%20be%20provided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Usha%20Mehra%20committee%20gave%20its%20report%20in%202008%20in%20which%20it%20recommended%20the%20inclusion%20of%20Clause%20(3)%20in%20Article%20341%20through%20a%20constitutional%20amendment%20empowering%20state%20legislature%20to%20enact%20reclassification%20of%20the%20SC%20category%20subjected%20to%20Presidential%20confirmation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%20after%20the%20%3Cem%3EChinnaiah%3C%2Fem%3E%20judgement%20and%20the%20Justice%20Usha%20Mehra%20Commission%20report%2C%20there%20are%20only%20two%20ways%20to%20reach%20solutions%20for%20the%20larger%20question%20of%20the%20constitutionality%20of%20subclassification%20of%20Scheduled%20Caste%20reservations%2C%20both%20of%20which%20are%20in%20the%20domain%20of%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20Union%20government%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20option%20available%20is%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20should%20initiate%20the%20process%20of%20constitutional%20amendment%20to%20insert%20clause%20341%20(3)%20which%20will%20allow%20reclassification%20of%20the%20Schedule%20caste%20reservation%20and%20enable%20state%20legislatures%20to%20enact%20the%20same.%20The%20second%20option%20would%20be%20to%20appeal%20for%20the%20expeditious%20constitution%20of%20a%20seven-judge%20bench%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20has%20the%20Modi%20government%20done%20on%20both%20counts%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJudicial%20option%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20first%20look%20at%20the%20judicial%20option%20and%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judgement%20favouring%20the%20reclassification%20of%20SC%20reservation%20by%20the%20constitutional%20bench%20of%20five%20judges%20in%20%3Cem%3EDavinder%20Singh%20vs%20State%20of%20Punjab%3C%2Fem%3E%20came%20on%20August%2027%2C%202020.%20The%20Bench%20itself%20had%20placed%20the%20appeal%20before%20CJI%20to%20constitute%20a%20higher%20bench%20along%20with%20its%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20been%20more%20than%20three%20years%20since%20that%20verdict%2C%20but%20no%20Bench%20has%20still%20been%20constituted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20petition%20appeared%20before%20the%20then%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Bench%20regularly%20there%20has%20been%20no%20pressure%20or%20appeal%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20headed%20by%20Modi%20at%20any%20point.%20When%20it%20came%20before%20a%20three-judge%20Bench%20headed%20by%20the%20then%20CJI%20N.V.%20Ramana%20just%20before%20his%20retirement%20in%20August%202022%2C%20the%20CJI%20had%20even%20asked%20the%20petitioner%20why%20had%20not%20they%20prayed%20for%20an%20expeditious%20hearing%20by%20a%20seven-judge%20Bench.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F24181353%2F11.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F24181353%2F11.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F24181353%2F11-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F24181353%2F11-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-474913%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20next%20CJI%20U.U.%20Lalit%20expedited%20constitutional%20matters%20and%20constituted%20many%20constitutional%20Benches%2C%20including%20one%20for%20EWS%20reservations%2C%20the%20issue%20of%20subclassification%20of%20Scheduled%20Caste%20reservation%20was%20not%20taken%20on%20the%20board.%20The%20reason%20being%20there%20was%20no%20urgency%20expressed%20or%20pressed%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20contrary%20to%20the%20way%20it%20was%20expedited%20in%20the%20EWS%20reservation%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20changed%20then%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKishan%20Reddy%20has%20unveiled%20the%20real%20story%2C%20though%20unintentionally%2C%20in%20the%20press%20conference%20that%20he%20addressed%20after%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20speech%20at%20the%20MRPS%20meeting%20in%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Reddy%2C%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20fast-approaching%20Telangana%20elections%2C%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20MRPS%20had%20called%20on%20Modi%20in%20Warangal%20in%20July%202023.%20This%20was%20followed%20up%20with%20another%20meeting%20with%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20in%20Delhi.%20It%20was%20only%20then%20the%20solicitor%20general%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftelangana%2Fcentre-to-form-task-force-to-implement-sc-categorisation-kishan-reddy%2Farticle67528539.ece%5C%22%3Emoved%20the%20petition%20to%20expedite%20the%20issue%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9C.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%20Modi%20was%20totally%20untrue%20when%20he%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20always%20fought%20for%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20marginalised%20Dalits%20relentlessly.%20If%20not%20for%20elections%2C%20the%20government%20would%20have%20not%20pressed%20for%20the%20expeditious%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20no%20one%20could%20be%20sure%20about%20the%20judgement.%20In%20fact%2C%20sub-classification%20among%20SCs%20is%20a%20policy%20issue.%20Thus%20a%20legislative%20rather%20than%20judicial%20intervention%20is%20more%20prudent%2C%20democratic%2C%20and%20certain.%20Even%20the%20Justice%20Usha%20Mehra%20Commission%20recommended%20the%20same%20way%20back%20in%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20though%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20government%20constituted%20the%20commission%2C%20it%20did%20not%20take%20any%20steps%20to%20conjure%20the%20non-partisan%20consensus%20required%20for%20a%20constitutional%20amendment%2C%20since%20it%20did%20not%20command%20the%20required%20strength%20in%20the%20Upper%20House.%20Congress%20as%20a%20party%20was%20never%20inclined%20towards%20antagonising%20entrenched%20interests%20for%20any%20noble%20cause%20with%20uncertain%20electoral%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%20the%20UPA%20government%20and%20the%20Congress%20betrayed%20the%20Dalit%20community%20in%20this%20respect.%20But%20at%20least%20it%20had%20the%20pretext%20of%20not%20having%20adequate%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20had%20adequate%20numbers%20in%20both%20the%2016%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%2017%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Since%202014%2C%20when%20the%20BJP%20assumed%20power%2C%20it%20has%20shown%20cunning%20prowess%20to%20muster%20a%20majority%20even%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20where%20it%20does%20not%20have%20a%20majority.%20It%20is%20how%20many%20anti-people%20and%20anti-social%20justice%20Bills%20like%20EWS%20reservation%2C%20UAPA%20amendments%2C%20Triple%20Talaq%2C%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20etc.%2C%20became%20laws%2C%20especially%20after%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20re-election%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fscheduled-castes-chinnaiah-arun-mishra-supreme-court%5C%22%3ESub-Classification%20of%20Scheduled%20Castes%3A%20Why%20the%20Chinnaiah%20Judgment%20Must%20Go%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20if%20the%20Modi%20government%20had%20been%20sincere%20to%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20reclassification%20of%20SC%20reservation%2C%20it%20could%20have%20moved%20the%20amendment%20to%20include%20clause%20(3)%20to%20Article%20341%2C%20immediately%20after%20coming%20to%20power%20in%202014.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20had%20even%20promised%20the%20same%20in%20its%202014%20and%202019%20electoral%20manifestos%20within%20100%20days%20of%20assuming%20power.%20But%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20never%20looked%20into%20it%20thus%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20many%20a%20time%20questions%20have%20been%20asked%20about%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20stand%20on%20the%20issue.%20And%2C%20every%20time%2C%20it%20has%20been%20evasive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20month%20of%20July%2C%20even%20after%20promising%20Krishna%20Madiga%20about%20the%20sub-classification%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20made%20it%20very%20clear%20to%20the%20parliament%20that%20it%20does%20not%20have%20any%20plans%20to%20legislate%20on%20that%20issue.%C2%A0This%20response%20needs%20a%20little%20more%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EG.V.L.%20Narasimha%20Rao%2C%20a%20BJP%20MP%2C%20had%20asked%20a%20question%20about%20whether%20the%20government%20is%20considering%20amendments%20to%20the%20constitution%20to%20empower%20states%20to%20provide%20internal%20reclassification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20answer%20given%20on%20July%2026%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20did%20not%20give%20any%20answer%20to%20this%20question%20by%20stating%20it%20as%20sub%20judice.%20In%20response%20to%20another%20question%2C%20however%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20made%20it%20clear%20indirectly%20that%20it%20would%20not%20venture%20to%20do%20that%20since%20most%20states%20are%20against%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20reply%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsansad.in%2FgetFile%2Fannex%2F260%2FAU774.pdf%3Fsource%3Dpqars%26fbclid%3DIwAR1nyhMjUMVOG1UJfxHYQoGFHAp4f2AvlYkY2eofcgfOKRr5VNXABzyjWxA%5C%22%3Estated%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20out%20of%2020%20states%20and%20two%20Union%20territories%2C%20that%20responded%20to%20the%20query%20sent%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20about%20their%20stand%20on%20internal%20reclassification%2C%2013%20states%20and%20one%20UT%20opposed%20the%20proposal%20and%20only%20seven%20states%20have%20agreed%20upon%20it!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20lies%20the%20reason%20for%20the%20reluctance%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20for%20that%20matter%20all%20previous%20governments%20in%20pressing%20for%20fuller%20social%20justice.%20Here%20also%20lies%20the%20clue%20as%20to%20how%20and%20why%20the%20BJP%20and%20Modi%20government%20are%20likely%20to%20renege%20on%20their%20promise%20made%20at%20MRPS%20meeting%20in%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20irony%20is%20that%20when%20Modi%20said%20the%20Dalits%20have%20been%20betrayed%20by%20the%20governments%20in%20the%20last%2030%20years%2C%20one-third%20of%20that%20period%2C%20which%20is%2010%20years%2C%20the%20country%20has%20been%20under%20the%20Modi-led%20BJP%20government.%20When%20he%20said%20in%20that%20rally%20that%20he%20is%20with%20the%20MRPS%20in%20its%20struggle%20for%20justice%2C%20what%20does%20he%20mean%3F%20Does%20he%20mean%20he%20is%20fighting%20against%20his%20own%20government%2C%20helmed%20by%20him%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20never%20going%20to%20antagonise%20the%20entrenched%20interests%20for%20a%20noble%20cause.%20If%20not%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20which%20is%20the%20only%20government%20which%20has%20had%20required%20legislative%20strength%20in%20the%20last%2030%20years%2C%20could%20have%20initiated%20the%20process%20of%20constitutional%20amendment%20long%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20the%20constitutional%20process%20is%20relegated%20to%20backstage%20since%20the%20case%20is%20sub%20judice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20never%20ventured%20to%20promise%20or%20hint%20even%20indirectly%2C%20in%20the%20Hyderabad%20rally%2C%20that%20if%20the%20judgement%20goes%20against%20the%20idea%20of%20sub-classification%2C%20he%20would%20go%20in%20for%20a%20constitutional%20amendment%20to%20ensure%20reclassification%2C%20as%20he%20did%20in%20the%20case%20of%20EWS%20reservation%20or%20in%20the%20case%20taking%20control%20of%20Delhi%20administration%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20the%20previous%20conduct%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20and%20the%20evasive%20and%20hypocritical%20stand%20it%20has%20taken%20in%20the%20parliament%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%20as%20explained%20above%2C%20and%20its%20ideological%20antipathy%20against%20social%20justice%20are%20testimonies%20to%20prove%20that%20Modi%20betrayed%20the%20Dalits%20once%20again%20in%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fshivasundar%5C%22%3EShivasundar%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20an%20activist%20and%20a%20freelance%20journalist%20based%20in%20Bangalore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700130514000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16141604%2FThe-Wire-82.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-modis-latest-assurance-on-the-sc-sub-classification-doesnt-exude-confidence%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20answer%20to%20the%20long-pending%20issue%20is%20either%20through%20Centre's%20intervention%20in%20the%20ongoing%20judicial%20process%20or%20through%20a%20constitutional%20amendment.%20However%2C%20the%20PM%20chose%20to%20announce%20yet%20another%20committee%20to%20push%20the%20issue%20into%20cold%20storage%20at%20the%20recent%20MRPS%20meeting%20in%20Hyderabad.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-modis-latest-assurance-on-the-sc-sub-classification-doesnt-exude-confidence%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22France%20issues%20arrest%20warrant%20for%20Syria's%20President%20Assad%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700129400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F11%2F768x432%2Fskynews-bashar-al-assad-syria_6362394.jpg%3F20231116111127%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ffrance-issues-arrest-warrant-for-syrias-president-assad-over-alleged-war-crimes-13009450%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22France%20has%20issued%20an%20international%20arrest%20warrant%20for%20Syrian%20President%20Bashar%20al%20Assad%20over%20the%20alleged%20use%20of%20banned%20chemical%20weapons%20against%20civilians.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A243%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ffrance-issues-arrest-warrant-for-syrias-president-assad-over-alleged-war-crimes-13009450%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ffrance-issues-arrest-warrant-for-syrias-president-assad-over-alleged-war-crimes-13009450%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ffrance-issues-arrest-warrant-for-syrias-president-assad-over-alleged-war-crimes-13009450%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China's%20president%20signals%20more%20pandas%20could%20be%20sent%20to%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700129220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F11%2F768x432%2Fskynews-panda-xiao-qi-ji-u