he%20prize%20%E2%80%9Cendeavours%20to%20to%20elevate%20the%20prestige%20of%20science%20and%20research%20in%20India%20and%20inspire%20young%20Indians%20to%20choose%20a%20vocation%20in%20research%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20prize%20carries%20a%20gold%20medal%2C%20a%20citation%20and%20the%20Indian%20rupee%20equivalent%20of%20US%24100%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInfosys%20is%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20multinational%20IT%20and%20consulting%20company%20and%20it%20awarded%20the%20first%20Infosys%20Prize%20in%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202023%20laureates%20were%20shortlisted%20from%20224%20nominations%20by%20%E2%80%9Can%20international%20panel%20of%20jurors%20comprising%20world-renowned%20scholars%20and%20experts%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.infosys.com%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-releases%2F2023%2Fannounces-winners-15th-infosys-prize.html%5C%22%3EInfosys%E2%80%99s%20website%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20will%20be%20presented%20with%20their%20prizes%20in%20January%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20a%20short%20summary%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.infosysprize.org%2Flaureates%2F2023%2F%5C%22%3Elaureates%E2%80%99%20achievements%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESachchida%20Nand%20Tripathi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20professor%20at%20IIT%20Kanpur%E2%80%99s%20civil%20engineering%20department%2C%20Tripathi%20won%20the%20engineering%20and%20computer%20science%20prize%20for%20his%20work%20in%20deploying%20large-scale%20air%20quality%20sensors%20in%20India%20and%20a%20mobile%20laboratory%20for%20processing%20the%20relevant%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CProf.%20Tripathi%E2%80%99s%20work%20has%20shown%20that%20the%20important%20differences%20between%20observations%20of%20winter%20haze%20formation%20in%20Delhi%20and%20those%20in%20other%20places%20like%20Beijing%20are%20that%20the%20nano-particle%20growth-rate%20in%20Delhi%20is%20much%20higher%20and%20happens%20at%20night%20without%20photochemistry%2C%E2%80%9D%20Infosys%20explained%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CThis%20finding%20holds%20the%20key%20to%20mitigating%20air%20pollution%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJahnavi%20Palkey%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounding%20director%20of%20the%20Science%20Gallery%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Palkey%20was%20awarded%20the%20humanities%20prize%20for%20%E2%80%9Cher%20brilliant%20and%20granular%20insights%20into%20the%20individual%2C%20institutional%20and%20material%20histories%20of%20scientific%20research%20in%20modern%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20Infosys%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prize%E2%80%99s%20website%20congratulated%20her%20for%20her%20work%20on%20the%20history%20of%20nuclear%20science%20research%20in%2020th-century%20India%20as%20well%20as%20scientific%20research%20more%20broadly%2C%20calling%20her%20research%20and%20expertise%20%E2%80%9Cwithout%20peer%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArun%20Kumar%20Shukla%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20professor%20at%20IIT%20Kanpur%E2%80%99s%20biological%20sciences%20and%20bioengineering%20department%2C%20Shukla%20won%20the%20life%20sciences%20prize%20for%20his%20%E2%80%9Coutstanding%20contributions%20to%20the%20biology%20of%20G-protein%20coupled%20receptors%20(GPCRs).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CProf.%20Shukla%E2%80%99s%20research%20has%20established%20a%20new%20understanding%20of%20GPCRs%2C%20which%20are%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20classes%20of%20drug%20targets.%20His%20work%20has%20opened%20up%20previously%20uncharted%20avenues%20for%20designing%20novel%20and%20effective%20therapeutics%2C%E2%80%9D%20Infosys%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBhargav%20Bhatt%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhatt%20is%20joint%20professor%20at%20the%20Institute%20for%20Advanced%20Study%20and%20at%20Princeton%20University%2C%20both%20in%20Princeton%2C%20New%20Jersey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Infosys%2C%20he%20was%20awarded%20the%20mathematical%20sciences%20prize%20for%20his%20%E2%80%9Coutstanding%20and%20fundamental%20contributions%20to%20arithmetic%20geometry%20and%20commutative%20algebra%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CProf.%20Bhatt%E2%80%99s%20joint%20work%20in%20prismatic%20cohomology%20with%20German%20mathematician%20Peter%20Scholze%20introduces%20new%20ideas%20and%20powerful%20methods%20in%20this%20area%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20pure%20mathematics%2C%E2%80%9D%20its%20website%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prize%E2%80%99s%20site%20also%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cmuch%20of%20work%20by%20mathematicians%20over%20the%20past%20five%20decades%20can%20now%20be%20viewed%20retrospectively%20as%20steps%20toward%20the%20Bhatt-Scholze%20theory%20of%20prismatic%20cohomology%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMukund%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cstrong%3EThattai%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20of%20biochemistry%2C%20biophysics%20and%20bioinformatics%20at%20the%20Tata%20Institute%20of%20Fundamental%20Research%E2%80%99s%20National%20Centre%20for%20Biological%20Sciences%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Thattai%20was%20awarded%20the%20physical%20sciences%20prize%20this%20year%20for%20his%20work%20on%20evolutionary%20cell%20biology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20has%20explored%20the%20origins%20of%20endomembrane%20organelles%2C%20shedding%20new%20light%20on%20how%20they%20emerged%20from%20ancient%2C%20primordial%20cells%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20prize%20website%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInfosys%E2%80%99s%20press%20release%20added%20that%20his%20work%20%E2%80%9Ccould%20have%20profound%20implications%20in%20one%20of%20biology%E2%80%99s%20central%20mysteries%20of%20how%20complex%20cells%20emerged%20from%20primordial%20ones.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKaruna%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cstrong%3EMantena%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20social%20sciences%20prize%20went%20to%20Columbia%20University%20political%20science%20professor%20Karuna%20Mantena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHer%20groundbreaking%20research%20on%20the%20theory%20of%20imperial%20rule%2C%20and%20the%20claim%20that%20this%20late%20imperial%20ideology%20became%20one%20of%20the%20important%20factors%20in%20the%20emergence%20of%20modern%20social%20theory%E2%80%9D%20earned%20her%20the%20prize%2C%20according%20to%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CProf.%20Mantena%E2%80%99s%20book%20%3Cem%3EAlibis%20of%20Empire%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20related%20papers%20are%20landmark%20publications%20in%20political%20theory%20with%20implications%20for%20all%20social%20sciences%2C%E2%80%9D%20Infosys%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700128198000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16142905%2FLaureates.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Finfosys-science-foundation-announces-laureates-of-2023-infosys-prize%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20prize%20is%20given%20in%20six%20categories%20spanning%20the%20sciences%2C%20social%20sciences%20and%20humanities.%20This%20year's%20six%20laureates%20will%20be%20presented%20with%20their%20prizes%20in%20January%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Finfosys-science-foundation-announces-laureates-of-2023-infosys-prize%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gaza%20Diaries%3A%20Life%20in%20a%20Land%20of%20Death%2C%20Through%20the%20Eyes%20of%20Mental%20Health%20Professionals%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16145449%2FUntitled-design-7-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20two%20part%20series%20is%20written%20by%20mental%20health%20professionals%20affiliated%20with%20the%20United%20Palestinian%20Appeal%20%E2%80%93%20an%20organisation%20which%20works%20in%20devising%20socially%20responsible%20and%20sustainable%20programmes%20in%20health%2C%20education%2C%20and%20community%20and%20economic%20development%20for%20Palestinians.%20UPA%20is%20headquartered%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20and%20works%20in%20the%20occupied%20Palestinian%20territories%20and%20refugee%20camps%20in%20Jordan%20and%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20part%20one.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStory%201%3A%20October%2023%2C%202023.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20me%2C%20Yasmine!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20seventeenth%20day%20of%20aggression%20on%20the%20Strip%2C%20we%20continue%20a%20long%20journey%20of%20looking%20for%20a%20safe%20place%20inside%20or%20outside%20our%20home.%20You%20see%2C%20after%20we%20received%20messages%20stressing%20that%20we%20leave%20our%20homes%20and%20head%20to%20the%20south%2C%20we%20believed%20that%20the%20south%20is%20truly%20the%20safe%20place!%20But%20after%20we%20headed%20south%2C%20we%20discovered%20for%20ourselves%20that%20there%20is%20really%20no%20safe%20place%20in%20Gaza!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20targets%20for%20this%20fascist%20occupation%20wherever%20we%20were.%20We%20then%20decided%20to%20go%20back%20home%2C%20telling%20each%20other%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20dead%2C%20either%20way.%20Better%20to%20die%20in%20our%20homes%2C%20for%20at%20least%20then%20people%20would%20know%20we%20rose%20as%20martyrs.%20But%20outside%20our%20homes%2C%20we%20may%20die%20and%20nobody%20will%20know%20we%20passed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20313px)%2085vw%2C%20313px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16145001%2FIMG_2767-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22313%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16145001%2FIMG_2767-1.jpg%20846w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16145001%2FIMG_2767-1-212x300.jpg%20212w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16145001%2FIMG_2767-1-722x1024.jpg%20722w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685065%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22444%5C%22%3EFor%20this%20reason%2C%20we%20came%20back%20home.%20My%20husband%2C%20Mohammad%2C%20has%20been%20preoccupied%20with%20keeping%20me%20in%20the%20house.%20He%20wants%20to%20protect%20me%20from%20any%20danger%20that%20may%20hurt%20me.%20You%20see%2C%20Mohammad%20and%20I%20have%20a%20strong%20and%20special%20bond.%20With%20our%20love%20for%20each%20other%2C%20we%20had%20barely%20survived%20the%20loss%20of%20our%20baby%20Sofia%2C%20just%20a%20month%20before%20these%20attacks%20started.%20Sofia%20turned%20into%20an%20angel%2C%20days%20before%20her%20first%20birthday%20because%20the%20hospitals%20in%20Gaza%20did%20not%20have%20the%20proper%20equipment%20to%20care%20for%20a%20baby%20born%20pre-maturely.%20Our%20best%20was%20not%20enough%20to%20keep%20her%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Mohammad%20wants%20to%20do%20all%20he%20can%20to%20keep%20me%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20he%20looked%20for%20a%20place%20he%20thought%20may%20be%20the%20least%20dangerous%2C%20and%20so%20he%20decided%20on%20under%20the%20stairs.%20He%20made%20me%20a%20safe%20%E2%80%9CStaircase%20House%E2%80%9D%20to%20protect%20me%20from%20any%20of%20the%20rockets%20of%20the%20brute%20occupation%20that%20could%20hit%20any%20time.%20I%20keep%20by%20me%20a%20bag%20with%20important%20papers%20and%20some%20money%2C%20and%20I%20have%20another%20bag%20with%20essential%20clothing%2C%20knowing%20very%20well%20that%20if%20an%20emergency%20happened%20and%20we%20had%20to%20leave%20suddenly%2C%20I%20will%20carry%20none%20of%20it!%20But%20simply%20having%20them%20next%20to%20me%20gives%20me%20a%20sense%20of%20safety.%20You%20know%20how%20they%20say%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20have%20to%20secure%20ourselves%E2%80%9D.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20to%20secure%20ourselves%20from%20in%20this%20case%2C%20with%20these%20bags%2C%20if%20we%20lost%20our%20homes%20or%20our%20families!%20Will%20any%20safety%20remain%20afterwards%2C%20anyway%3F!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20run%20to%20seek%20refuge%20in%20my%20safe%20staircase%20house%20every%20time%20I%20hear%20the%20sound%20of%20a%20falling%20missile%2C%20horrified%20that%20this%20may%20be%20the%20moment%20that%20would%20end%20our%20lives!%20Although%20I%20know%20very%20well%20that%20if%20any%20of%20these%20missiles%20fell%20on%20us%2C%20there%20will%20be%20no%20safe%20place%2C%20and%20even%20this%20little%20safe%20house%20of%20mine%20will%20disappear!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYasmine%20Ayoub%20is%20a%20mental%20health%20practitioner%20at%20Gaza%2C%20who%20works%20at%20UPA.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStory%202%3A%20October%2024%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20situation%20is%20terror%20of%20dying%20any%20minute.%20As%20much%20as%20possible%2C%20we%20portion%20food%20and%20water.%20Every%20day%2C%20there%20are%20long%20lines%20for%20food%20and%20drinking%20water.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20when%20we%20feel%20the%20wrath%20of%20the%20airplanes%20as%20we%20are%20filling%20up%20our%20drinking%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFear%20and%20worry%20all%20around%20the%20clock%2C%20day%20and%20night.%20We%20barely%20sleep%20interrupted%203-4%20hours%2C%20because%20the%20madness%20of%20the%20attacks%20escalates%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20kids%20are%20terrified.%20My%20son%20is%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20old%20and%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20get%20off%20his%20mom%E2%80%99s%20lap%20or%20mine%2C%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20eat%2C%20he%20just%20wants%20to%20nurse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20midst%20of%20all%20these%20conditions%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20big%20hope%20that%20things%20resolve%20in%20a%20minute.%20Every%20day%20we%20thank%20God%20that%20we%20still%20have%20life%20in%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERoo7%20is%20a%20mental%20health%20professional%2C%20anonymous%20for%20fear%20of%20being%20targeted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStory%203%3A%20October%2025%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWishing%20there%20was%20no%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20worst%20time%20of%20the%20day%20in%20this%20savage%20war%20is%20when%20the%20sun%20starts%20setting%2C%20as%20if%20the%20night%20has%20been%20weaponized%20by%20the%20colonizer%20to%20instil%20fear%20and%20horror.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20the%20nights%20of%20terror.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETotal%20darkness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncessant%20trepidation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExaggerated%20sounds%20of%20explosions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFear%20for%20our%20kids%20is%20multiples%20of%20our%20fear%20for%20ourselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20have%20the%20chance%20to%20follow%20the%20news%20or%20see%20the%20martyrs%2C%20especially%20the%20children%2C%20we%20are%20overtaken%20by%20an%20overwhelming%20sense%20of%20fear%20that%20shakes%20us%20to%20the%20core.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20excessive%20fear%20and%20cumulative%20exhaustion%20can%20put%20the%20kids%20to%20sleep.%20We%20thank%20God%20when%20they%20sleep%2C%20even%20if%20from%20fear%20and%20exhaustion%2C%20so%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20wake%20to%20some%20of%20the%20terrifying%20sounds%20of%20shelling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUs%20adults%20push%20each%20other%20on%20with%20prayers%2C%20praise%2C%20and%20wishes%20that%20we%20are%20not%20the%20next%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20of%20the%20night%20are%20slow%20and%20motionless.%20We%20pray%20to%20God%20that%20we%20see%20another%20morning%20in%20a%20new%20life%E2%80%A6%20although%20daylight%20is%20no%20less%20dangerous%2C%20but%20we%20find%20solace%20in%20the%20company%20of%20people%20around%20us%20who%20remained%20alive.%20The%20occupiers%20transformed%20the%20night%20that%20God%20made%20for%20rest%20and%20contentment%20to%20an%20unwanted%20visitor%20of%20daily%20terror.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20wives%20keep%20themselves%20busy%20by%20preparing%20food%20and%20caring%20for%20the%20children%20as%20much%20as%20they%20can.%20And%20us%20husbands%20leave%20the%20house%20holding%20our%20souls%20in%20our%20hands%20to%20make%20available%20whatever%20we%20can%20find%20of%20basic%20necessities.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20wether%20I%20will%20return%20with%20water%20for%20my%20family%20or%20wether%20my%20blood%20will%20water%20the%20earth%20beneath%20me.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20if%20I%20will%20come%20back%20to%20find%20my%20family%20alive%20and%20well%20or%20under%20the%20rubble.%20And%20if%20I%20am%20destined%20to%20return%20to%20my%20beloved%20wife%2C%20I%20support%20her%20as%20much%20as%20possible.%20Oh%20how%20I%20missed%20talking%20to%20her%20about%20the%20children%20and%20my%20problems%20at%20work!%20Now%20our%20conversations%20are%20about%20listening%20and%20supporting%20(considering%20emergency%20plans%20%E2%80%93%20problem-solving%20solutions%20for%20water%20shortage%20%E2%80%93%20arranging%20for%20general%20daily%20challenges%20and%20so%20on).%20We%20hold%20on%20to%20dear%20life%20with%20all%20what%20is%20left%20of%20our%20strength%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20a%20better%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20console%20each%20other%20that%20we%20are%20still%20alive%20and%20that%20hope%20is%20enough%20to%20hold%20us%20until%20tomorrow.%20All%20for%20tomorrow.%20A%20tomorrow%20we%20pray%20would%20be%20better%20than%20yesterday%E2%80%99s%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERoo7%20is%20a%20mental%20health%20professional%2C%20anonymous%20for%20fear%20of%20being%20targeted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29182252%2FF9l7tShWEAAHqvL.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29182252%2FF9l7tShWEAAHqvL.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29182252%2FF9l7tShWEAAHqvL-300x140.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F29182252%2FF9l7tShWEAAHqvL-1024x476.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682394%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22558%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDestroyed%20buildings%20in%20Gaza.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40UNRWA%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStory%204%3A%20October%2026%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20war%20is%20not%20like%20any%20previous%20war%2C%20at%20least%20not%20for%20me.%20Wars%20and%20aggressions%20are%20typical%20for%20us.%20Never%20did%20we%20know%20peace%20or%20security.%20In%20the%20thirty%20years%20of%20my%20life%2C%20I%20was%20always%20known%20for%20my%20strength%20and%20tenacity%20in%20difficult%20times.%20I%20was%20always%20the%20wise%20and%20dependable%20one%20in%20the%20family%2C%20especially%20caring%20for%20my%20ill%20mother.%20But%20this%20time%20is%20not%20like%20every%20other%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20look%20after%20my%20mother%20and%20nephew%2C%20who%20had%20come%20to%20visit%20and%20spend%20some%20time%20with%20his%20grandmother%20and%20aunt%20(me).%20On%20the%20thirteenth%20of%20October%2C%20I%20was%20sitting%20with%20my%20mother%20in%20the%20corner%20we%20deemed%20to%20be%20the%20safest%20in%20the%20house.%20Suddenly%2C%20we%20heard%20the%20sounds%20of%20people%20screaming%20and%20learned%20at%20the%20time%20that%20they%20forced%20the%20evacuation%20of%20a%20building%20nearby%20because%20the%20Israelis%20were%20about%20to%20bomb%20it.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20but%20yell%20to%20my%20mom%20and%20nephew%20that%20they%20will%20bomb!%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20I%20picked%20up%20the%20bags%20I%20previously%20prepared%2C%20with%20some%20of%20my%20important%20papers%2C%20pictures%20of%20my%20deceased%20father%20(may%20his%20soul%20RIP)%2C%20and%20some%20clothes.%20I%20made%20sure%20my%20mom%20and%20nephew%20were%20ahead%20of%20me%20and%20we%20quickly%20ran%20down%20the%20stairs%20yelling%20as%20loud%20as%20we%20could%20to%20warn%20our%20neighbours%20%E2%80%9CEVACUATION%E2%80%A6%20EVACUATION%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20entrance%20of%20our%20building%2C%20our%20screams%20met%20those%20of%20my%20brother%E2%80%99s%20wife%20and%20his%20two%20daughters.%20I%20looked%20everywhere%20around%20me%20and%20could%20not%20find%20my%20brother.%20I%20felt%20my%20heart%20beat%20in%20super%20speed%20and%20I%20got%20in%20the%20car%20with%20my%20mom%20and%20nieces.%20My%206-%20and%2010-year-old%20nieces%20were%20crying%20hysterically.%20Then%20I%20drove%20the%20car%20outside%20the%20parking%20as%20I%20was%20shouting%20my%20brother%E2%80%99s%20name%20%2C%20%E2%80%9CFIND%20ME%20MY%20BROTHER!!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20all%20these%20souls%20being%20my%20responsibility%20now%2C%20I%20had%20to%20drive%20to%20a%20place%20somewhat%20away%20from%20the%20shelling.%20My%20mom%20was%20trying%20hard%20to%20get%20the%20phone%20out%20to%20call%20my%20brother%2C%20but%20her%20hands%20were%20shaking%20so%20hard%20from%20shock%20and%20terror%20that%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20call.%20I%20remember%20well%20how%20I%20climbed%20over%20the%20sidewalk%20%2C%20completely%20overwhelmed%20with%20my%20fear%20and%20worry%20about%20my%20brother%2C%20about%20whom%20I%20knew%20nothing.%20Finally%2C%20I%20stopped%20the%20car%2C%20picked%20up%20the%20phone%2C%20and%20called%20my%20brother%2C%20who%20finally%20answered.%20As%20soon%20as%20he%20answered%2C%20I%20broke%20into%20tears%20as%20I%20was%20terrified%20something%20horrible%20had%20befallen%20him!%20He%20told%20me%20he%20was%20going%20around%20knocking%20at%20the%20neighbors%E2%80%99%20houses%20to%20evacuate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%20my%20sadness%20and%20worries%2C%20feelings%20of%20pride%20and%20gratitude%20arose%20because%20I%20have%20a%20brother%20who%20chose%20to%20save%20the%20lives%20of%20others%20before%20his%20own%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20hung%20up%20the%20phone%20and%20then%20looked%20to%20the%20back%20and%20saw%20my%20nieces%20crying.%20I%20will%20never%20forget%20the%20sight%20of%20my%206-year-old%20neice%20who%20could%20barely%20breathe%20as%20she%20looked%20at%20me%20fearful%20and%20shivering.%20When%20I%20looked%20at%20her%2C%20she%20hugged%20and%20kissed%20me%20and%20held%20on%20to%20me%20for%20dear%20life.%20I%20could%20not%20tell%20whether%20she%20was%20supporting%20me%20or%20looking%20for%20any%20sense%20of%20safety%20and%20security%20in%20my%20arms%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHayat%20is%20a%20mental%20health%20professional%20in%20Gaza%2C%20Palestine.%20Anonymous%20for%20fear%20of%20being%20targeted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01111519%2Fimage1170x530cropped.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01111519%2Fimage1170x530cropped.jpg%201170w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01111519%2Fimage1170x530cropped-300x136.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01111519%2Fimage1170x530cropped-1024x464.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682873%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22530%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20young%20boy%20plays%20in%20the%20street%20amidst%20the%20wreckage%20of%20homes%20destroyed%20by%20airstrikes%20in%20Al%20Shati%20Refugee%20Camp%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20Photo%3A%20UNICEF%2FMohammad%20Ajjour%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStory%205%3A%20October%2027%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20winter%20of%20paper%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20an%2011-year-old%20son.%20He%20is%20my%20eldest%20boy.%20He%20loves%20me%20very%20much%20and%20wants%20nothing%20more%20in%20life%20than%20to%20be%20like%20me.%20Rowdy-dowdy%20and%20fun-loving%2C%20just%20like%20me!%20He%20even%20mimics%20my%20humorous%20style%20and%20watches%20how%20I%20make%20his%20mother%20laugh.%20Gradually%2C%20I%20watch%20him%20turn%20into%20a%20mini-me.%20He%20loves%20to%20make%20his%20mother%20laugh%20even%20in%20silly%20situations.%20His%20happiness%20peaks%20when%20he%20makes%20his%20mother%20laugh%2C%20for%20he%20feels%20like%20he%20owns%20the%20world!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20son%E2%80%99s%20most%20joyful%20moments%20is%20the%20time%20I%20challenge%20him%20in%20PlayStation%20soccer%20at%20the%20gaming%20store%20next%20door.%20Here%20he%20starts%20teasing%20me%20and%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9Cyou%20play%20better%20than%20me%20because%20you%20are%20older%20but%20there%20will%20come%20a%20day%20when%20I%20will%20beat%20you%20like%20my%20maternal%20uncles%20beat%20you%2C%20for%20they%20play%20better%20than%20you%20hahahaha%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20I%20start%20running%20after%20him%20pretending%20to%20be%20angry%2C%20as%20he%20hides%20in%20his%20mother%E2%80%99s%20lap.%20She%20looks%20at%20me%20and%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9Cyour%20game%20is%20weak%20compared%20to%20my%20brothers%E2%80%99%20hahaha%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20first%20Friday%20of%20this%20vile%20offensive%2C%20I%20was%20washing%20for%20prayer%20when%20my%20son%20rushed%20through%20the%20door%20and%20said%3A%E2%80%9D%20Daddy%2C%20daddy%2C%20the%20sky%20is%20raining%20papers!!%E2%80%9D%20I%20immediately%20realized%20that%20the%20occupier%20planned%20an%20atrocity%20as%20per%20usual.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Leave%20to%20the%20south%20of%20the%20Strip%20as%20this%20is%20the%20safe%20place.%20You%20have%2024%20hours.%20If%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20go%2C%20we%20will%20consider%20you%20to%20be%20terrorists.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20nonsense%20is%20this%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20logic%20are%20you%20using%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20went%20down%20to%20the%20street%20to%20find%20my%20neighborhood%20evacuating.%20Lucky%20he%20who%20owns%20a%20car!%20He%20could%20take%20his%20family%20and%20went%20to%20the%20allegedly%20safe%20south.%20Not%20me.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20own%20a%20car.%20Even%20if%20I%20had%20a%20car%2C%20how%20do%20I%20move%20when%20I%20am%20responsible%20for%2019%20people%20of%20my%20family%2C%20father%2C%20sister%2C%20and%20siblings%E2%80%99%20families%20who%20all%20live%20in%20the%20same%20building%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20most%20difficult%20decision%20I%20will%20ever%20make.%20On%20it%20henges%20not%20only%20my%20future%2C%20but%20also%20that%20of%20every%20person%20under%20my%20care.%20We%20may%20never%20come%20to%20our%20home%20again%2C%20we%20may%20die%20on%20the%20way%2C%20we%20may%20truly%20find%20safety.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOh%20dear%20God%2C%20what%20do%20I%20do%3F%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20look%20at%20the%20kids%20and%20my%20dad%20and%20my%20family%20to%20find%20everyone%20asking%20what%20do%20we%20do%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20helpless.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20in%20my%20life%20I%20lose%20control%20like%20this.%20My%20thoughts%20froze%20as%20if%20I%20turned%20into%20an%20object.%20I%20suddenly%20told%20everyone%20to%20take%20as%20much%20water%20as%20they%20could%2C%20to%20empty%20their%20school%20bags%20and%20fill%20them%20with%20some%20clothes%2C%20water%2C%20and%20food%20so%20we%20can%20start%20heading%20south.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%3A%20%E2%80%9CDo%20we%20leave%20our%20house%20that%20we%20built%20with%20blood%20and%20sweat%2C%20one%20brick%20at%20a%20time%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20she%20started%20looking%20at%20every%20detail%2C%20every%20room%2C%20and%20every%20part%20of%20the%20house.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20say%20a%20thing%20because%20I%20was%20feeling%20the%20exact%20same%20way.%20At%20that%20moment%2C%20that%20mischievous%20child%2C%20who%20always%20wanted%20to%20be%20like%20his%20father%2C%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CMama%2C%20let%20us%20leave%20and%20if%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20continue%2C%20we%20can%20come%20back%20home.%20And%20if%20we%20die%2C%20we%20go%20to%20heaven.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20you%20always%20tell%20us%20that%20when%20we%20die%20we%20go%20to%20heaven%20and%20be%20rid%20of%20terror%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20looked%20at%20him%20as%20if%20God%20had%20spoken%20to%20us%20through%20him%20to%20ease%20us%20into%20the%20lesser%20of%20two%20evils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDo%20I%20feel%20proud%20that%20this%20boy%20has%20truly%20become%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20son%20or%20do%20I%20weep%20that%20he%20grew%20up%20so%20early%20that%20he%20accepted%20death%20at%2011%3F%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know.%20But%20I%20did%20thank%20God%20that%20he%20was%20my%20son%2C%20the%20apple%20of%20my%20eye.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20finally%20managed%20to%20get%20ourselves%20out%20of%20the%20house%3B%20the%20sight%20infront%20of%20us%20full%20of%20glass%20and%20destruction%2C%20and%20the%20sight%20behind%20us%20of%20our%20home%20that%20we%20may%20be%20looking%20at%20for%20the%20last%20time.%20The%20plan%20was%20to%20head%20to%20the%20hospital%20and%20from%20there%20look%20for%20cars%20to%20drive%20us%20to%20the%20allegedly%20safe%20south.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERoo7%20is%20a%20mental%20health%20professional%2C%20anonymous%20for%20fear%20of%20being%20targeted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStory%206%3A%20October%2028%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20night%20of%20the%20hospital%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20sole%20night%20spent%20at%20the%20hospital%20was%20enough%20to%20realize%20that%20dying%20under%20the%20rubble%20of%20our%20home%20was%20much%20easier%20than%20staying%20only%20for%20a%20few%20hours%20at%20the%20hospital.%20The%20plan%20was%20to%20head%20to%20the%20hospital%20on%20foot%20as%20a%20first%20stop%20so%20we%20can%20find%20some%20cars%20to%20take%20us%20to%20the%20supposedly%20safe%20south.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20gathered%20all%20my%2019%20family%20members%20in%20one%20of%20the%20hallways%20of%20the%20hospital%20so%20I%20can%20go%20find%20some%20cars%20to%20drop%20us%20off%20at%20the%20supposedly%20safe%20south%2C%20without%20having%20to%20worry%20about%20leaving%20them%20out%20in%20the%20street.%20Little%20did%20I%20know%20that%20we%20would%20be%20spending%20the%20night%20in%20that%20tiny%20corridor%20designed%20as%20a%20walking%20passage%20way%20in%20which%20you%20can%20barely%20sit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20left%20the%20hospital%20to%20look%20for%20two%20to%20three%20cars.%20What%20an%20idiot!%20Even%20he%20who%20finds%20one%20car%20would%20be%20lucky%2C%20yet%20here%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20three.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20much%20turmoil%20and%20an%20exhausting%2C%20ongoing%20search%20under%20the%20burning%20sun%2C%20feeling%20thirsty%20and%20fatigued%2C%20I%20found%20one%20small%20car%20that%20holds%20the%20driver%20and%20three%20passengers.%20I%20begged%20him%20to%20take%20us%20to%20the%20south.%20He%20said%20he%20would%20drop%20us%20off%20as%20passengers%20only%20without%20any%20bags%2C%20for%20the%20price%20of%20100%20Shekels%20per%20rider.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20stood%20in%20total%20shock.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20I%20affirmed%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ride%20is%206%20Shekels%20per%20person%2C%20how%20did%20it%20now%20become%20100%3F%20What%20is%20this%20exploitation%3F%20Isn%E2%80%99t%20it%20enough%20that%20we%20are%20showered%20with%20pieces%20of%20death%3F%20You%2C%20too%3F%20What%20is%20wrong%20with%20you%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CBrother%2C%20I%20have%20a%20family%20just%20like%20you%20and%20this%20car%20is%20my%20only%20source%20of%20income.%20If%20I%20take%20you%2C%20I%20will%20use%20this%20money%20to%20buy%20basic%20necessities%20for%20my%20family%20for%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20awaits%20me%20in%20the%20south%20or%20if%20I%20will%20come%20back%20alive.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20consider%20this%20exploitation%2C%20please%20see%20it%20as%20survival%20for%20my%20family%20and%20I.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20looked%20at%20him%20with%20forgiveness%20and%20compassion%2C%20and%20I%20was%20speechless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20finally%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CMay%20God%20bless%20you%20and%20be%20with%20you.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20went%20back%20to%20my%20family%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%20feeling%20completely%20helpless%20with%20my%20inability%20to%20procure%20cars%20to%20get%20us%20to%20the%20so-called%20safety.%20When%20my%20wife%2C%20father%2C%20brother%2C%20and%20sisters-in-law%20saw%20me%20like%20this%2C%20they%20reassured%20me%20and%20noted%20that%20God%20may%20not%20want%20us%20to%20go%20to%20the%20south%2C%20after%20all.%20My%20wife%20held%20my%20hand%20and%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CTake%20it%20easy.%20You%20are%20not%20the%20only%20one%20responsible%20for%20our%20safety%20here.%20We%20are%20all%20in%20this%20together.%20Rest%20now%2C%20my%20love%2C%20and%20God%20will%20show%20us%20the%20way.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20decided%20to%20spend%20the%20night%20at%20this%20hallway.%20This%20hallway%20is%20barely%20good%20to%20pass%20through%3B%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20even%20sit%2C%20let%20alone%20sleep.%20We%20stuck%20to%20the%20walls%20to%20allow%20pedestrians%20to%20pass.%20That%20night%2C%20we%20saw%20all%20types%20of%20injured%20victims%20who%20lost%20legs%20and%20arms%2C%20and%20had%20bleeding%20heads%2C%20and%20many%20more%20tragedies%20and%20pains.%20If%20I%20myself%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20tolerate%20these%20scenes%2C%20how%20could%20I%20expect%20our%20children%20to%20do%20so%3F!%20How%20do%20I%20protect%20my%20children%20from%20exposure%20to%20all%20this%20madness%3F%20The%20impact%20of%20this%20particular%20night%20will%20forever%20be%20in%20our%20children%E2%80%99s%20memories%20and%20I%2C%20a%20trauma%20psychologist%2C%20am%20clueless%20on%20how%20to%20handle%20that%20if%20we%20were%20destined%20to%20survive%20this%20brutal%20aggression.%20For%20now%2C%20I%20have%20to%20figure%20out%20a%20way%20to%20boost%20our%20chances%20of%20survival.%20But%20how%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20stood%20by%20the%20window%20that%20overlooks%20the%20registration%20desk%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%20looking%20for%20some%20fresh%20air.%20The%20building%20was%20so%20over%20crowded%20that%20the%20air%20was%20polluted%20with%20the%20smells%20and%20breaths%20of%20people%3A%20their%20sweat%2C%20food%2C%20and%20the%20dirty%20bathrooms%E2%80%A6%20all%20these%20odours%20and%20more%20in%20this%20building%20we%20sought%20refuge%20in.%20We%20have%20no%20place%20except%20this%20hallway.%20Where%20could%20we%20go%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20looked%20out%20of%20the%20window%D8%8C%20the%20aggressors%20had%20committed%20a%20new%20massacre%20near%20the%20hospital%2C%20destroying%20a%20house%20over%20its%20residents.%20I%20saw%20the%20martyrs%20being%20laid%20out%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20registration%20area%2C%20being%20readied%20for%20transport%20to%20the%20tent%20of%20the%20dead%2C%20a%20space%20you%20can%20barely%20call%20a%20tent!%20I%20saw%20human%20parts%20and%20blood.%20I%20saw%20the%20chopped%20legs%20and%20beheaded%20bodies.%20I%20saw%20all%20this%20with%20my%20own%20eyes.%20I%20wept%20and%20wept%20and%20wept%20until%20I%20had%20no%20breath%20left.%20Smelling%20all%20the%20foul%20odours%20inside%20the%20hospital%20was%20much%20easier%20than%20watching%20outside%20this%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20recall%20how%20this%20night%20ended%2C%20nor%20do%20I%20want%20to%20know.%20It%E2%80%99s%20over%20and%20we%20are%20not%20going%20to%20the%20hospital%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20first%20light%20of%20the%20second%20day%2C%20my%20wife%20told%20me%3A%20%E2%80%9CCome%20on%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20go%20to%20our%20home%3B%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20take%20it%20anymore.%E2%80%9D%20Then%20the%20entire%20family%20asked%20to%20go%20back%20home%20and%20that%20they%20had%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20went%20back%20home%20knowing%20fully%20well%20that%20we%20are%20walking%20back%20to%20death.%20But%20this%20time%2C%20we%20are%20content%20with%20what%20will%20happen%20to%20us%20and%20are%20leaving%20our%20fate%20to%20God%2C%20for%20He%20is%20our%20saviour%20and%20protector.%20We%20find%20solace%20in%20knowing%20we%20had%20done%20all%20we%20can%20to%20stay%20out%20of%20the%20house%2C%20but%20all%20in%20vain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20at%20our%20home%20now%20and%20will%20not%20leave.%20With%20the%20sunrise%20of%20every%20new%20day%2C%20we%20pray%20in%20thanks%20to%20God%20for%20the%20gift%20of%20being%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERoo7%20is%20a%20mental%20health%20professional%2C%20anonymous%20for%20fear%20of%20being%20targeted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20152423%2FF80RehHW4AA4TR0.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20152423%2FF80RehHW4AA4TR0.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20152423%2FF80RehHW4AA4TR0-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20152423%2FF80RehHW4AA4TR0-1024x576.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681050%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20damaged%20school%20building%20in%20Gaza.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40UN_SPExperts%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStory%207%3A%20October%2029%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYasmine%20here%E2%80%A6%20miraculously%20spared%20by%20the%20angel%20of%20death%20after%20the%20shelling%20of%20the%20past%20few%20days%2C%20next%20to%20which%20we%20had%20never%20seen%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20had%20told%20you%20before%20about%20my%20safe%20house%20%E2%80%9Cunder%20the%20staircase%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20I%20would%20like%20to%20update%20you%20about%20that.%20I%20left%20my%20safe%20house%203%20days%20ago%20because%20it%20is%20no%20longer%20safe.%20A%20house%20across%20from%20us%20was%20targeted%20and%20that%20bombing%20seriously%20damaged%20our%20home.%20We%20thank%20God%20that%20we%20are%20breathing%20and%20as%20the%20popular%20proverb%20goes%3A%20%E2%80%9Cin%20wealth%20and%20not%20people%E2%80%9D!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Mohammad%2C%20my%20husband%2C%20went%20to%20check%20on%20the%20house%20and%20the%20damage%20incurred%20in%20the%20last%20shelling.%20He%20first%20went%20into%20our%20beloved%20baby%20Sofia%E2%80%99s%20room%2C%20the%20little%20birdy%20of%20my%20heart.%20I%20kept%20her%20toys%20and%20clothes%2C%20and%20her%20oxygen%20concentrators%20that%20gave%20me%20a%20few%20additional%20months%20of%20her%20life%E2%80%A6%20and%20the%20memory%20book%20that%20I%20had%20started%20for%20her%20since%20the%20first%20day%20she%20lived%20inside%20of%20me!%20I%20insisted%20on%20going%20to%20check%20on%20them%20everyday%2C%20and%20smell%20her%20in%20them.%20Today%2C%20Mohammad%20went%20to%20find%20nothing%20in%20place!%20A%20shattered%20window.%20Dirt%20and%20sand%20filling%20up%20the%20place.%20When%20we%20fled%20the%20house%2C%20I%20could%20take%20nothing%20except%20her%20favourite%20toy%20with%20me.%20That%20toy%20is%20always%20with%20me%2C%20even%20in%20my%20normal%20days%2C%20inseparable%20from%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20my%20heart%20sink%20when%20my%20husband%20sent%20me%20the%20picture%20of%20the%20room!%20The%20smell%20of%20dust%20and%20gunpowder%20overshadowed%20Sofia%E2%80%99s%20smell%20in%20the%20place%E2%80%A6%20her%20toys%20scrambled%20here%20and%20there%E2%80%A6%20and%20the%20memory%20book%20full%20of%20dirt%20and%20gunpowder!%20I%20miss%20her%20so%20much.%20I%20miss%20visiting%20and%20talking%20to%20her.%20I%20weep%20everyday%20longing%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20thought%20of%20death%20used%20to%20terrify%20me%2C%20but%20not%20anymore%2C%20for%20perhaps%20I%20can%20meet%20my%20only%20sanctuary%20and%20my%20eternal%20love%2C%20Sofia%2C%20without%20fear%20or%20pain%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYasmine%20Ayoub%20is%20a%20mental%20health%20practitioner%20at%20Gaza%2C%20who%20works%20at%20UPA.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13095608%2Fimage1170x530cropped.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13095608%2Fimage1170x530cropped.jpg%201170w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13095608%2Fimage1170x530cropped-300x136.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13095608%2Fimage1170x530cropped-1024x464.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679846%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22530%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMany%20parts%20of%20Gaza%20lie%20in%20ruins%20following%20airstrikes.%20Photo%3A%20UN%20News%2FZiad%20Taleb%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStory%208%3A%20October%2030%2C%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20nights%20of%20terror.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20every%20family%20with%20many%20siblings%2C%20there%20is%20always%20a%20child%20who%20steals%20your%20heart%20with%20their%20light%20spirit%2C%20wit%2C%20and%20an%20adorable%20presence%20that%20everybody%20seems%20to%20love.%20This%20poses%20a%20challenge%20for%20a%20father%20so%20as%20to%20avoid%20provoking%20rivalry%20in%20other%20siblings%2C%20but%20to%20no%20avail!%20The%20eyes%20talk%20and%20expose%20you.%20You%20try%20to%20save%20face%20and%20say%20%E2%80%9CI%20love%20you%20all%E2%80%9D%E2%80%A6%20and%20I%20believe%2C%20according%20to%20my%20limited%20experience%20in%20life%2C%20that%20this%20is%20part%20of%20the%20struggle%20of%20most%20fathers%20and%20mothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20younger%20daughter%20of%20mine%E2%80%A6%20the%20first%20day%20she%20was%20born%2C%20my%20heart%20skipped%20a%20beat%20in%20a%20way%20I%20never%20experienced%20with%20her%20siblings.%20I%20felt%20a%20unique%20connection%20with%20her%20that%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20explain.%20From%20the%20very%20first%20moment%2C%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20her%20features%2C%20I%20was%20captivated%20by%20her%20smile%2C%20and%20I%20knew%20she%20took%20over%20my%20life%E2%80%A6%20for%20she%20is%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20apple%20of%20my%20eye%E2%80%9D%20as%20we%20say%20in%20slang.%20We%20share%C2%A0%C2%A0a%20secret%20that%20%E2%80%9Cyou%20are%20my%20favorite%20child%E2%80%9D!%20A%20secret%20she%20whispered%20in%20my%20ear%20each%20time%20she%20felt%20jealous%20of%20her%20siblings%20%E2%80%9Cdaddy%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20forget%20I%20am%20your%20favorite%20child%E2%80%9D%20hahaha%E2%80%A6%20oh%20how%20much%20I%20love%20her%20and%20fear%20for%20her%20and%20how%20weak%20I%20become%20infront%20of%20her%20sparkling%20eyes!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20night%20that%20we%20called%20%E2%80%98night%20of%20death%E2%80%99%2C%20suddenly%2C%20all%20connectivity%20and%20communications%20were%20cut%20off%20and%20radios%20declared%20Gaza%20as%20dark%20and%20isolated%2C%20with%20all%20the%20dire%20implications%20this%20declaration%20brings.%20You%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20even%20check%20on%20your%20family%20and%20relatives%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20minutes%20later%2C%20the%20shelling%20exploded%20from%20all%20directions.%20Suddenly%2C%20the%20skies%20lit%20up%20with%20the%20colors%20of%20fire%20and%20then%20switched%20off%2C%20fire%20belts%20here%20and%20there%2C%20homes%20bombed%20over%20the%20heads%20of%20their%20occupants%2C%20the%20sounds%20of%20people%20screaming%20all%20around%20us%E2%80%A6%20our%20hearts%20nearly%20stopped.%20A%20terrifying%20idea%20overtook%20our%20minds%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthis%20is%20our%20last%20night.%E2%80%9D%20I%20heard%20my%20brother%20speak%20the%20shahada%20(praising%20God%20before%20one%20dies)%3B%20my%20seventy%20five-year-old%20father%20frozen%20and%20paralyzed%20in%20horror%3B%20my%20sisters-in-law%20screaming%20with%20every%20explosion%3B%20their%20children%20trembling.%20My%20wife%20took%20the%20boys%20in%20her%20lap%20and%20I%20took%20in%20the%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20older%20daughter%20was%20terrified%2C%20but%20she%20stuck%20her%20head%20between%20my%20shoulder%20and%20neck%20and%20held%20on%20to%20me%20so%20tightly%2C%20it%20felt%20we%20were%20one%20body.%20This%20also%20meant%20she%20felt%20my%20fear%20and%20fast%20heartbeats%20the%20most.%20As%20for%20my%20younger%20daughter%2C%20every%20inch%20of%20her%20was%20shaking%2C%20her%20face%20yellow%2C%20her%20lips%20pale%20and%20dry%2C%20her%20extremities%20cold%2C%20her%20body%20shaking%2C%20her%20fingers%20in%20her%20ears%2C%20screaming%20and%20crying%20with%20every%20hit%E2%80%A6%20and%20there%20was%20a%20hit%20every%20minute.%20Since%20that%20day%2C%20she%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20able%20to%20sleep%20except%20in%20my%20lap%2C%20with%20her%20fingers%20in%20her%20ears.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20remained%20like%20this%20for%20around%205%20hours%20of%C2%A0%C2%A0death%20and%20destruction.%20You%20can%20imagine%20what%20that%20sunrise%20was%20like%20for%20us%20as%20we%20realized%20we%20were%20still%20alive%20and%20breathing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20such%20have%20become%20our%20daily%20routines%2C%20our%20nights%2C%20our%20memories%2C%20and%20such%20are%20our%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20but%20God%20and%20He%20is%20our%20protector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERoo7%20is%20a%20mental%20health%20professional%2C%20anonymous%20for%20fear%20of%20being%20targeted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20series%20first%2