for%20building%20and%20maintaining%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fjcmc%2Farticle%2F25%2F4%2F274%2F5866390%5C%22%3Erelationships%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20can%20be%20places%20of%20joy%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.sagepub.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1177%2F13548565231153505%5C%22%3Esolidarity%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheoutline.com%2Fpost%2F2315%2Flong-live-the-group-chat%5C%22%3Erefuge%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20they%20can%20also%20be%20burdensome%2C%20and%20create%20feelings%20of%20anxiety%20and%20worry.%20I%20researched%20group%20chat%20dynamics%20and%20these%20are%20the%20three%20biggest%20issues%20I%20encountered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20You%E2%80%99re%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20volume%20of%20messages%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20volume%20of%20messages%20and%20notifications%20group%20chats%20generate%20can%20be%20overwhelming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fjcmc%2Farticle%2F25%2F4%2F274%2F5866390%5C%22%3Emy%20own%20research%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20participant%20recalled%20accidentally%20leaving%20her%20phone%20at%20home%2C%20and%20returning%20to%20find%20she%E2%80%99d%20missed%20200%20messages%20in%20a%20group%20chat%20about%20buying%20a%20birthday%20gift.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20explained%20that%20their%20most%20active%20group%20chat%20kicked%20off%20at%208am%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20quiet%20down%20until%201am.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdl.acm.org%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1145%2F3427228.3427275%5C%22%3Esurvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20people%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20United%20Kingdom%20suggests%20this%20is%20a%20common%20problem%2C%20with%2040%25%20of%20the%20respondents%20indicating%20they%20were%20overwhelmed%20with%20group%20chat%20messages%20and%20notifications.%20And%20then%20there%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ic.unicamp.br%2F%257Eoliveira%2Fdoc%2FMHCI2014_An-in-situ-study-of-mobile-phone-notifications.pdf%5C%22%3Enotifications%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20email%2C%20social%20media%2C%20calendars%2C%20news%20apps%2C%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20often%20manage%20this%20by%20muting%20group%20chats.%20But%20this%20can%20mean%20missing%20important%20information%20or%20plans%20to%20catch%20up%2C%20or%20having%20to%20dip%20in%20and%20out%20of%20the%20group%20chat%20to%20check%20for%20relevant%20conversations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20can%20also%20find%20the%20chaos%20of%20group%20chat%20conversations%20overwhelming.%20In%20large%20groups%2C%20multiple%20conversations%20can%20be%20running%20at%20once%2C%20making%20it%20hard%20to%20keep%20track%20of%20what%20is%20being%20discussed%20or%20planned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20problems%20can%20make%20group%20chats%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fjoc%2Farticle-abstract%2F66%2F5%2F834%2F4082414%3Flogin%3Dfalse%5C%22%3Eineffective%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20tasks%20they%20were%20set%20up%20to%20complete.%20Especially%20in%20large%20groups%20of%20acquaintances%2C%20planning%20can%20devolve%20into%20a%20mess%20of%20opinions%2C%20alternatives%20and%20side%20conversations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20participant%20in%20my%20research%20described%20a%20group%20chat%20about%20a%20birthday%20gift%20getting%20sidetracked%20by%20two%20people%20having%20their%20own%20catch%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20recounted%20a%20disastrous%20group%20chat%20involving%2020%20people%20trying%20to%20organise%20a%20potluck%20dinner.%20Rather%20than%20reaching%20a%20consensus%20about%20who%20would%20bring%20what%2C%20the%20conversation%20devolved%20into%20a%20debate%20about%20whether%20potlucks%20were%20a%20bad%20idea%2C%20with%20one%20person%20insisting%20professional%20catering%20would%20better%20account%20for%20dietary%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20there%20%E2%80%93%20but%20can%E2%80%99t%20leave%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%2C%20possibly%20more%20significant%2C%20challenges%20are%20the%20difficult%20or%20awkward%20social%20dynamics%20that%20can%20arise.%20The%20ease%20of%20creating%20groups%20and%20adding%20members%20means%20people%20can%20be%20included%20in%20groups%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20chosen%20to%20join.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fjoc%2Farticle-abstract%2F66%2F5%2F834%2F4082414%3Flogin%3Dfalse%5C%22%3Eone%20instance%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20this%2C%20a%20woman%20was%20added%20to%20a%20group%20for%20organising%20a%20shared%20gift%20for%20a%20colleague.%20She%20would%20have%20preferred%20not%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20gift%20but%20found%20it%20too%20awkward%20to%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChallenging%20dynamics%20can%20also%20arise%20when%20relationships%20change%20after%20a%20group%20chat%20has%20been%20established.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20participant%20told%20me%20about%20a%20group%20chat%20started%20by%20four%20close%20friends%20when%20they%20began%20university.%20A%20year%20later%2C%20one%20person%20had%20grown%20distant%20and%20become%20largely%20silent%20in%20the%20group%20chat%2C%20although%20the%20other%20three%20still%20used%20it%20to%20chat%20and%20organise%20catch%20ups.%20My%20participant%20found%20this%20dynamic%20incredibly%20awkward%20and%20had%20become%20cautious%20about%20starting%20group%20chats%20as%20a%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20participants%20described%20feeling%20trapped%20in%20group%20chats%20they%20would%20prefer%20to%20leave.%20The%20blunt%20%E2%80%9Cx%20has%20left%20the%20group%E2%80%9D%20notification%20made%20them%20reluctant%20to%20formally%20quit%20but%20ignoring%20the%20group%20was%20also%20uncomfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20these%20challenges%20stem%20from%20the%20rigid%20membership%20of%20group%20chats%20(you%E2%80%99re%20either%20in%20or%20you%E2%80%99re%20out)%20which%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20always%20gel%20with%20the%20complexity%20of%20our%20relationships.%20These%20challenges%20may%20also%20be%20exacerbated%20by%20unclear%20or%20contested%20social%20etiquette%20around%20group%20messaging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20You%20feel%20excluded%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20difficult%20issues%20arise%20when%20processes%20of%20social%20exclusion%20play%20out%20in%20group%20chats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fjcmc%2Farticle%2F25%2F4%2F274%2F5866390%5C%22%3EBack%20channel%20groups%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20emerge%2C%20where%20some%20group%20members%20create%20a%20new%20group%20to%20privately%20communicate%20about%20what%E2%80%99s%20happening%20in%20the%20main%20chat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20most%20dramatic%20cases%2C%20participants%20described%20people%20getting%20kicked%20out%20of%20groups%20because%20of%20disagreements%20or%20because%20someone%20felt%20the%20group%20chat%20had%20become%20too%20large.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdl.acm.org%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1145%2F3427228.3427275%5C%22%3EResearch%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggests%20that%20being%20removed%20from%20a%20group%20is%20rare%20and%20mostly%20occurs%20when%20a%20relationship%20has%20ended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20guessing%20whether%20you%E2%80%99ve%20been%20excluded%20from%20a%20group%20chat%20can%20be%20cause%20for%20anxiety%2C%20especially%20because%20you%20might%20not%20just%20be%20missing%20out%20on%20gossip%20and%20cat%20videos%20but%20also%20plans%20to%20catch%20up%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20what%20can%20you%20do%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20relationships%20with%20each%20other%20can%20be%20weird%2C%20awkward%20and%20messy%20%E2%80%93%20group%20chats%20reflect%20this%20social%20reality%20but%20with%20an%20added%20layer%20of%20technological%20complexity%20thrown%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGenerally%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fjoc%2Farticle-abstract%2F66%2F5%2F834%2F4082414%3Flogin%3Dfalse%5C%22%3Eresearch%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggests%20that%20the%20group%20chats%20people%20enjoy%20most%20are%20smaller%20groups%20with%20closer%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20until%20app%20design%20improves%20and%20we%20collectively%20figure%20out%20etiquette%20for%20awkward%20group%20chat%20moments%2C%20your%20best%20bets%20are%20to%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Euse%20group%20chats%20with%20a%20handful%20of%20people%20who%20know%20each%20other%2C%20or%20who%20you%E2%80%99re%20confident%20will%20get%20along%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Efind%20another%20way%20of%20organising%20that%20potluck.%20Use%20other%20forms%20of%20organisation%20for%20more%20complex%20events%20or%20with%20larger%20groups%20(invitations%2C%20Facebook%20events%20or%20one-on-one%20texts)%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Emute%20those%20crazy%20chats%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20struggling%20with%20distraction%20or%20aren%E2%80%99t%20that%20interested.%20Muting%20is%20common%20and%20increasingly%20expected.%20If%20the%20chat%20is%20often%20used%20for%20organising%20things%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20miss%2C%20let%20someone%20in%20the%20group%20know%20so%20they%20can%20keep%20you%20posted%20or%20make%20a%20routine%20of%20checking%20in%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3Eif%20you%E2%80%99re%20feeling%20weird%20about%20some%20group%20chat%20social%20dynamics%2C%20raise%20it%20with%20the%20person%20in%20the%20group%20you%20know%20best.%20We%20can%20make%20lots%20of%20assumptions%20about%20what%20other%20people%E2%80%99s%20messaging%20behaviours%20mean%20but%20the%20lack%20of%20extra%20social%20cues%20mean%20our%20assumptions%20can%20be%20off.%20That%20person%20might%20not%20be%20avoiding%20you%20%E2%80%93%20they%20might%20just%20have%20the%20chat%20muted!%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fprofiles%2Fkate-mannell-1375883%5C%22%3EKate%20Mannell%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Research%20Fellow%20in%20Digital%20Childhoods%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Finstitutions%2Fde