rred%20to%20by%20percentages%20in%20the%20survey%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EToday%20we%20look%20at%20Jutt%20(52%2C730%20people)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20previous%20parts%20of%20this%20series%2C%20we%20have%20discussed%20those%20caste%20groups%20of%20Bihar%20which%20are%20comprised%20of%20members%20who%20belong%20to%20either%20agrarian%20or%20artisan%20communities.%20Today%2C%20let%20us%20talk%20about%20a%20caste%20group%20members%20of%20which%20are%20neither%20farmers%20nor%20craftsmen%20but%20are%20artistes%20and%20performers.%20It%20is%20a%20caste%20whose%20existence%20itself%20is%20steeped%20in%20art%2C%20especially%20dancing%20and%20singing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20are%20talking%20about%20the%20Jutt%20community.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20316px)%2085vw%2C%20316px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22316%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%20838w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-210x300.jpg%20210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%20715w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22453%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHave%20you%20ever%20seen%20culture%20in%20corporeal%20form%3F%20I%20do%20not%20mean%20idols%20which%20are%20installed%20during%20Hindu%20festivals.%20In%20the%20villages%20of%20Bihar%2C%20gods%20and%20goddesses%20do%20not%20quite%20immediately%20mean%20idols.%20For%20them%2C%20every%20god%20and%20goddess%20resides%20in%20each%20body%20and%20place.%20But%20Jutts%20are%20not%20gods%20and%20goddesses.%20They%20are%20living%20people%2C%20who%20are%20culture%20incarnate.%20And%20the%20sweetness%20of%20their%20culture%20makes%20Bihar%20stand%20out.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Jutts%20must%20not%20be%20confused%20with%20the%20Jatt%20community%20of%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%20and%20western%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Jatts%20are%20a%20farming%20community%20and%20although%20the%20Jutts%20of%20Bihar%20do%20work%20as%20agricultural%20labourers%2C%20their%20main%20occupation%20is%20not%20farming.%20They%20are%20people%20who%20dance%20and%20sing%2C%20especially%20during%20festivals.%20The%20women%20of%20this%20community%2C%20or%20Juttin%2C%20support%20the%20men%20in%20their%20performances.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20written%20record%20as%20to%20when%20and%20why%20their%20ancestors%20became%20performers.%20Perhaps%20they%20lived%20in%20the%20forests%20and%20brought%20the%20tribal%20culture%20from%20the%20forests%20to%20the%20plains.%20It%20is%20assumed%20because%20their%20style%20of%20dance%20is%20seen%20only%20in%20the%20tribal%20society%20where%20people%20dance%2C%20sing%20and%20play%20drums%20in%20the%20evening%20or%20during%20festivals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20might%20ask%20why%20culture%20was%20not%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20key%20professional%20criteria%20in%20history.%20If%20it%20had%20been%20so%2C%20one%20would%20at%20least%20find%20mention%20of%20how%20their%20style%20of%20singing%20and%20dancing%20changed%20when%20their%20ancestors%20shifted%20from%20the%20forests%20to%20the%20plains.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%2C%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Jutt%20caste%20group%20reside%20only%20in%20a%20few%20districts%20of%20Bihar.%20According%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98Caste%20Based%20Census%20Report%202022%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20Bihar%20government%2C%20they%20live%20in%20Saharsa%2C%20Supaul%2C%20Madhepura%2C%20Araria%2C%20Darbhanga%2C%20Madhubani%2C%20Sitamarhi%20and%20Khagaria%20districts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInterestingly%2C%20Jutts%20are%20both%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Nutt%20caste%20in%20the%20state%20who%20belong%20to%20both%20the%20communities.%20There%20are%20many%20similarities%20between%20the%20people%20of%20Nutt%20and%20Jutt%20castes.%20One%20major%20similarity%20is%20that%20both%20of%20them%20are%20entertainers%20involved%20in%20performing%20arts%20%E2%80%93%20dancing%20and%20singing.%20But%20the%20Nutts%20mainly%20live%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20Ganges.%20It%20is%20possible%20that%20the%20Nutts%20from%20the%20areas%20of%20Magadha%2C%20Bhojpur%2C%20etc.%20are%20members%20of%20Jutt%20community.%20But%20there%20is%20no%20way%20one%20can%20establish%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20similarity%20is%20that%20most%20of%20the%20people%20of%20both%20these%20castes%20are%20either%20landless%20or%20possess%20land%20only%20in%20name.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20total%20population%20of%20Hindu%20members%20of%20the%20Jutt%20caste%20is%207781%20and%20they%20live%20in%20Saharsa%2C%20Supaul%2C%20Madhepura%20and%20Araria%20districts%20whereas%20the%20Muslim%20population%20of%20this%20caste%20which%20is%20around%2044949%20lives%20in%20Madhubani%2C%20Sitamarhi%2C%20Darbhanga%2C%20Khagaria%20and%20Araria.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESongs%2C%20music%20and%20dance%20have%20been%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20lives%20of%20these%20people%2C%20whether%20they%20are%20Hindu%20or%20Muslim.%20They%20neither%20glorify%20any%20Hindu%20gods%20in%20their%20songs%20nor%20recite%20the%20Kalma%20in%20praise%20of%20a%20formless%20being%20like%20Sufis.%20These%20are%20worldly%20people%20and%20they%20dance%20and%20sing%20for%20the%20inhabitants%20of%20this%20earth.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20far%20as%20their%20political%20and%20social%20status%20is%20concerned%2C%20they%20are%20simply%20referred%20to%20as%20Jutt-Juttin.%20Even%20if%20the%20population%20of%20both%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim%20Jutts%20is%20added%2C%20it%20amounts%20only%20to%2052%2C730.%20However%2C%20if%20the%20population%20of%20Nutt%20caste%20%E2%80%93%201%2C05%2C358%20Hindus%20and%2061%2C629%20Muslims%20%E2%80%93%20is%20added%20to%20the%20Jutt%20population%20it%20comes%20to%202%2C19%2C717.%20But%20this%20number%20is%20still%20not%20significant%20for%20their%20voice%20to%20be%20heard%20on%20the%20political%20front.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20some%20more%20people%20have%20adopted%20their%20art%20in%20Bihar.%20They%20perform%20the%20traditional%20Jutt-Juttin%20dance%20on%20stage%20though%20they%20are%20not%20people%20of%20the%20Jutt%20community.%20This%20brings%20us%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Jutt%20people%20are%20now%20migrating%20not%20only%20from%20their%20native%20areas%20but%20also%20from%20their%20culture%20in%20search%20of%20livelihood.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20pain%20of%20migration%20also%20appears%20in%20one%20of%20their%20songs%20in%20which%20a%20Jutt%20man%20asks%20his%20wife%20to%20let%20him%20go%20to%20foreign%20countries%20so%20that%20he%20can%20earn%20money.%20He%20also%20tempts%20her%20by%20saying%20that%20when%20he%20returns%20he%20will%20bring%20her%20a%20gold%20chain%20and%20sweets.%20But%20in%20response%20his%20wife%20says%20that%20the%20gold%20chain%20is%20like%20the%20dust%20on%20his%20feet%20and%20upon%20hearing%20that%20he%20is%20leaving%20his%20culture%2C%20she%20calls%20him%20%3Cem%3Ekulborna%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20destroyer%20%E2%80%93%20and%20asks%20him%20to%20always%20remain%20in%20front%20of%20her.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20question%20is%2C%20who%20will%20understand%20the%20pain%20of%20this%20exodus%20of%20the%20Jutt%20people%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehma