m%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20men%20were%20meant%20to%20use%20machinery%2C%20however%2C%20a%20motor%20failure%20prompted%20one%20of%20them%20to%20climb%20down%20a%2025-foot-deep%20sewage%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20respond%2C%20others%20followed%20in%20to%20rescue%20him%20but%20lost%20consciousness%2C%20according%20to%20H.L.%20Rathod%2C%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20Surat%20Rural.%20The%20bodies%20of%20all%20four%20victims%20were%20transported%20to%20Surat%20Government%20Hospital%20for%20a%20post-mortem%20examination%2C%20TOI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Fnov%2F16%2F4-migrant-workers-die-while-cleaning-septic-tank-in-surat-2633333.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmergency%20response%20teams%20from%20ERC%20fire%20stations%20at%20Kamrej%20and%20Bardoli%20swiftly%20responded%20to%20the%20distress%20call.%20Fire-fighters%20extracted%20the%20unconscious%20workers%20from%20the%20septic%20tank%2C%20but%20they%20were%20declared%20dead%20by%20the%20108-emergency%20team%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20said%20that%20though%20it%20appears%20to%20be%20an%20accident%2C%20if%20any%20carelessness%20is%20discovered%20during%20the%20inquiry%20then%20they%20would%20pursue%20a%20case%20of%20criminal%20negligence%20and%20investigate%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2F339-lives-lost-to-manual-scavenging-in-the-last-five-years-govt-data-reveals%5C%22%3E339%20people%20have%20died%20while%20cleaning%20sewers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20septic%20tanks%20in%20India%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20according%20to%20government%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManual%20scavenging%20is%20an%20outlawed%20practice%20under%20the%20Prohibition%20of%20Employment%20as%20Manual%20Scavengers%20and%20their%20Rehabilitation%20(PEMSR)%20Act%2C%202013.%20The%20Act%20bans%20t