intercontinental%20ballistic%20missile%20with%20the%20nuclear-capable%20%26quot%3BAvangard%26quot%3B%20hypersonic%20glide%20vehicle%20into%20a%20launch%20silo%20in%20southern%20Russia.%20The%20Avangard%20glide%20vehicle%20can%20maneuver%20at%20hypersonic%20speeds%20and%20was%20developed%20in%20response%20to%20the%20US's%20development%20of%20new%20weapons%20and%20missile%20defense%20systems.%20Both%20Russia%20and%20the%20US%20have%20expressed%20concern%20about%20the%20breakdown%20of%20arms-control%20treaties%2C%20while%20also%20developing%20new%20weapons%20systems.%20Russia%20claims%20that%20US%20dominance%20is%20crumbling%20and%20accuses%20it%20of%20causing%20global%20chaos.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-loads-missile-with-nuclear-capable-glide-vehicle-into-launch-silo%2Farticleshow%2F105256455.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-loads-missile-with-nuclear-capable-glide-vehicle-into-launch-silo%2Famp_articleshow%2F105256455.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-loads-missile-with-nuclear-capable-glide-vehicle-into-launch-silo%2Famp_articleshow%2F105256455.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22British%20Govt%20and%20Opposition%E2%80%99s%20Full-On%20Support%20for%20Israel%20is%20Causing%20Islamophobia%20in%20Great%20Britain%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16125741%2FF9yf7uwXwAAldA3.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBritish%20Prime%20Minster%20Rishi%20Sunak%20has%20finally%20had%20to%20sack%20his%20home%20secretary%2C%20Suella%20Braverman%20for%20her%20open%20defiance%20of%20his%20authority.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20offence%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20was%20an%20incendiary%20article%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20which%20she%20attacked%20pro-Palestinian%20demonstrations%20as%20%E2%80%98hate%20marches%E2%80%99%20and%20a%20%E2%80%98mob%E2%80%99%20and%20accused%20the%20police%20of%20playing%20favourites%20and%20bowing%20to%20left-wing%20causes%20%E2%80%93%20a%20direct%20challenge%20to%20the%20police%E2%80%99s%20operational%20independence.%20She%20had%20apparently%20been%20asked%20to%20modify%20the%20article%20when%20she%20sent%20it%20for%20clearing%20to%20No.%2010%2C%20but%20had%20published%20it%20unchanged.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Her%20career%20as%20Rishi%20Sunak%E2%80%99s%20home%20secretary%20has%20now%20ended%2C%20but%20that%20of%20being%20a%20right-wing%20provocateur%20may%20only%20just%20be%20getting%20started.%20As%20right-wing%20conservatives%20gather%20to%20consider%20their%20next%20moves%2C%20Braverman%20promised%20that%20she%20would%20%E2%80%98have%20more%20to%20say%20in%20due%20course.%E2%80%99%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20she%20leaves%20behind%20a%20government%20and%20a%20country%20more%20polarised%20than%20ever%20over%20a%20conflict%20miles%20away%20in%20a%20land%20that%20the%20British%20government%20left%20in%20flames%20in%201948.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDays%20after%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20October%207%20attacks%20on%20Israel%2C%20British%20PM%20Sunak%20flew%20to%20Israel%20to%20stand%20with%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20and%20pledge%20his%20support%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%98We%20also%20want%20you%20to%20win%2C%E2%80%99%20as%20if%20this%20were%20some%20sort%20of%20grotesque%20game.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20tally%20in%20this%20case%20is%20in%20lives%2C%20and%20long%20after%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20health%20authorities%20have%20put%20the%20number%20of%20dead%20from%20the%20Israeli%20Defence%20Force%E2%80%99s%20attacks%20on%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20at%20over%2011%2C000%2C%20the%20British%20government%20and%20its%20opposition%20continue%20to%20pick%20sides%20in%20a%20war%20that%20can%20only%20have%20losers.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20one%20of%20the%20first%20losers%20in%20this%20case%20is%20community%20cohesion%20in%20Britain.%20Nowhere%20is%20this%20more%20apparent%20than%20in%20the%20bitter%20domestic%20arguments%20that%20are%20raging%20in%20Britain%20over%20the%20refusal%20by%20Rishi%20Sunak%2C%20as%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20and%20Keir%20Starmer%2C%20as%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20(and%20on%20current%20trends%2C%20possibly%20the%20next%20prime%20minister%20of%20the%20country)%20to%20join%20in%20calls%20made%20by%20the%20United%20Nations%20and%20most%20of%20its%20members%20for%20a%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%20in%20the%20region.%20It%20is%20difficult%20to%20counter%20the%20impression%20that%20one%20group%E2%80%99s%20pain%20counts%20for%20less.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20should%20of%20course%20not%20need%20clarifying%20that%20support%20for%20Israel%20does%20not%20equate%20to%20support%20for%20the%20Netanyahu%20government.%20Equally%2C%20people%20demonstrating%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Palestinians%20are%20not%20backing%20Hamas.%20Yet%2C%20it%20is%20exactly%20this%20position%20that%20the%20government%2C%20especially%20the%20recently%20sacked%20home%20secretary%2C%20Suella%20Braverman%2C%20has%20taken%2C%20with%20her%20consistent%20branding%20of%20pro-Palestinian%20demonstrations%20as%20%E2%80%98hate%20marches%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Manichean%20view%20of%20the%20conflict%20adopted%20by%20the%20British%20government%20and%20echoed%20by%20the%20opposition%20has%20left%20large%20swathes%20of%20the%20British%20public%20disconnected%20from%20the%20official%20view.%C2%A0%20Parliament%20has%20spoken%20as%20one%20to%20condemn%20Hamas%E2%80%99%207%20October%20violence%2C%20but%20has%20refused%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20suffering%20caused%20by%20the%20Israeli%20bombardment%20of%20Gaza.%C2%A0%20There%20was%20mourning%20for%20British%20Israeli%20lives%20lost%20and%20blighted%20by%20the%20attacks%2C%20but%20no%20acknowledgement%20of%20the%20distress%20and%20suffering%20of%20British%20Palestinians%20in%20the%20subsequent%20siege%20of%20Gaza%20by%20the%20IDF.%C2%A0%20It%20is%20difficult%20not%20to%20conclude%20from%20this%2C%20as%20Baroness%20Warsi%2C%20a%20Conservative%20peer%20and%20former%20cabinet%20minister%20and%20Chair%20of%20the%20Conservative%20Party%20did%2C%20that%20%E2%80%98Muslims%20don%E2%80%99t%20matter%E2%80%99%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20Britain.%C2%A0%20The%20war%20in%20Gaza%20has%20allowed%20politicians%20in%20Britain%20to%20unleash%20the%20most%20cynical%20culture%20war%20of%20pitting%20one%20group%20against%20another%20%E2%80%93%20in%20this%20case%2C%20Muslims%20against%20the%20rest.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20results%20are%20already%20in.%C2%A0%20In%20the%20month%20following%20the%20attacks%20in%20Israel%2C%20the%20Metropolitan%20Police%20recorded%20657%20antisemitic%20incidents%2C%20compared%20to%2049%20from%20the%20same%20period%20last%20year.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20there%20were%20230%20Islamophobic%20incidents%2C%20up%20from%2071%20in%20the%20same%20period%20last%20year.%20And%20to%20this%20tinderbox%20of%20hate%20and%20insecurity%2C%20Braverman%20took%20a%20lit%20match%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20(unrevised)%20opinion%20piece%20published%20on%20November%209.%20Choosing%20as%20her%20target%20the%20third%20in%20a%20series%20of%20rolling%20Saturday%20protest%20marches%20expressing%20solidarity%20with%20Palestinians%20and%20which%20have%20been%20calling%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20response%20to%20the%20humanitarian%20crisis%20in%20Gaza%2C%20Braverman%20has%20accused%20the%20%E2%80%98pro-Palestinian%20mobs%E2%80%99%2C%20(as%20she%20has%20termed%20the%20mostly%20British%20citizens%2C%20including%20British%20Jewish%20activists%20who%20oppose%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20policy%20on%20Palestine)%20of%20%E2%80%98an%20assertion%20of%20primacy%20by%20certain%20groups%20%E2%80%93%20particularly%20Islamists.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Frishi-sunak-suella-braverman-david-cameron%5C%22%3ERishi%20Sunak%20Faces%20Conservative%20Party%20Unrest%20After%20Sacking%20Suella%20Braverman%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBaroness%20Warsi%20had%20warned%20that%20this%20breathtakingly%20cynical%20pitting%20of%20Muslims%20against%20the%20rest%20would%20only%20embolden%20the%20far%20right%2C%20and%20events%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20march%20proved%20her%20correct%20as%20far-right%20English%20Defence%20League%20members%20(who%20had%20already%20threatened%20to%20congregate%20at%20the%20Cenotaph%20to%20defend%20it%20from%20those%20they%20considered%20unpatriotic)%20clashed%20with%20the%20police.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20march%20in%20question%20happened%20to%20coincide%20with%20Armistice%20Day%2C%20the%20day%20the%20guns%20finally%20fell%20silent%20on%20the%20blood-soaked%20battlefields%20of%20Europe%20after%20the%20Great%20War.%20The%20demonstrators%20wanted%20to%20use%20the%20backdrop%20of%20remembrance%20of%20the%20many%20lives%20lost%20to%20call%20for%20a%20halt%20to%20the%20bloodshed%20in%20Gaza%20%E2%80%93%20but%20with%20a%20demonstration%20that%20would%20not%20go%20anywhere%20near%20the%20Cenotaph%2C%20the%20focal%20point%20of%20Remembrance%20events.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20they%20got%2C%20instead%2C%20was%20a%20questioning%20of%20their%20loyalties%20by%20the%20then%20home%20secretary%20and%20her%20PM.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Sunak%2C%20who%20tried%20and%20failed%20to%20pressure%20the%20Metropolitan%20police%20into%20banning%20the%2011%20November%20march%20issued%20a%20statement%2C%20that%20while%20conceding%20the%20right%20of%20the%20protests%20to%20go%20ahead%2C%20nevertheless%20termed%20them%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20just%20disrespectful%20but%20offen%5Bsive%20to%5D%20our%20heartfelt%20gratitude%E2%80%9D%20to%20those%20who%20fought%20for%20freedom.%20For%20those%20marching%2C%20the%20really%20offensive%20part%20of%20this%20statement%20is%20the%20assumption%20that%20none%20of%20them%20have%20any%20links%20to%20those%20who%20fought%20for%20the%20freedom%20of%20Britain%2C%20its%20allies%20and%20its%20colonies.%20Muslim%20blood%20was%20shed%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20as%20the%20Turkish%20empire%20was%20dismantled%20and%20in%20Europe.%20Of%20the%201.5%20million%20Indian%20troops%20who%20fought%20in%20WWI%2C%20at%20least%20400%2C000%20were%20Muslim.%20Many%20more%20Muslims%20served%20as%20sailors%20and%20labourers.%20The%20first%20Victoria%20Cross%20awarded%20to%20a%20South%20Asian%20went%20to%20Sepoy%20Khudadad%20Khan%20on%20October%2031%2C%201914.%20Khan%20was%20the%20sole%20survivor%20of%20a%20group%20from%20the%20129%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Baluchis%20who%20faced%20down%20advancing%20Germans%20in%20the%20Belgian%20village%20of%20Hollebeke%2C%20buying%20the%20allies%20enough%20time%20for%20reinforcements%20to%20stop%20a%20German%20advance%20on%20vital%20ports.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20stories%20of%20sacrifice%20and%20valour%20should%20not%20need%20repeating.%20Yet%20each%20time%20there%20is%20tension%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20Muslims%20in%20Britain%20have%20to%20prove%20their%20loyalties%20where%20others%20might%20just%20wave%20their%20passports.%C2%A0%20And%20sadly%20for%20community%20cohesion%2C%20there%20is%20hardly%20any%20dissent%20to%20this%20approach%20expressed%20by%20the%20Labour%20Party%2C%20the%20official%20opposition.%20Islamophobia%20is%20becoming%20institutionalised%20in%20British%20politics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20middle%20of%20these%20controversies%2C%20communities%20secretary%20Michael%20Gove%20has%20asked%20for%20%C2%A350%20million%20to%20counter%20extremism.%20This%20money%20will%20be%20used%20to%20identify%20and%20counter%20radical%20ideologies%20and%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Fc8b798a8-b4c7-4200-af95-c71ace680416%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ETimes%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%98supporting%20moderate%20Muslim%20voices%20and%20improving%20English%20language%20training.%E2%80%99%20In%20other%20words%2C%20divide%20Muslims%20into%20the%20right%20sort%20and%20the%20ones%20whose%20loyalties%20are%20always%20suspect%2C%20with%20those%20not%20speaking%20English%20presumably%20falling%20into%20the%20latter%20category.%20Instead%20of%20tackling%20the%20attitudes%20and%20policies%20that%20alienate%20Muslims%2C%20money%20will%20now%20be%20spent%20on%20further%20classifying%20them%20as%20a%20problem%20to%20be%20fixed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGovernments%20worldwide%20should%20be%20under%20no%20illusions%20that%20this%20taking%20of%20sides%20will%20tear%20at%20the%20fabric%20of%20communal%20living.%C2%A0%20In%20America%2C%20a%20number%20of%20South%20Asians%20reportedly%20refused%20an%20invitation%20from%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20to%20celebrate%20Diwali%20in%20protest%20of%20the%20administration%E2%80%99s%20support%20for%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98collective%20punishment%E2%80%99%20of%20Gazans.%20Support%20for%20Palestine%20has%20been%20an%20article%20of%20faith%20in%20India%2C%20and%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20back%20a%20proposal%20at%20the%20UN%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza%20has%20caused%20very%20real%20hurt.%20The%20suffering%20in%20the%20Levant%20should%20not%20be%20exploited%20for%20narrow%20domestic%20political%20gains.%C2%A0%20Because%20the%20fires%20that%20start%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20rarely%20remain%20confined%20to%20that%20region.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700119905000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16125741%2FF9yf7uwXwAAldA3.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fislamophobia-great-britain-israel-palestine-sunak%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sacked%20home%20secretary%20Suella%20Braverman%20will%20now%20emerge%20as%20a%20leading%20voice%20of%20the%20hard%20right-wing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fislamophobia-great-britain-israel-palestine-sunak%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Due%20to%20Record%20High%20Oil%20Purchases%2C%20Russia%20Emerges%20as%20India's%20Second%20Largest%20Source%20of%20Imports%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04193929%2Fimage-966.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ERussia%20has%20been%20India%E2%80%99s%20second%20largest%20source%20of%20imports%20for%20the%20last%20seven%20months%20in%20the%20current%20financial%20year%20due%20to%20increased%20oil%20purchases%20from%20Moscow%2C%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Fforeign-trade%2Fimports-from-russia-up-64-pc-to-usd-36-27-bn-in-apr-oct%2Farticleshow%2F105237342.cms%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20citing%20government%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20marked%20difference%20from%20the%20situation%20that%20had%20existed%20during%20the%20same%20period%20last%20year.%20Before%20Russia%2C%20it%20was%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20which%20was%20in%20second%20place.%20The%20UAE%20is%20now%20India%E2%80%99s%20third%20largest%20source%20of%20imports.%20Meanwhile%2C%20China%20continues%20to%20be%20in%20the%20top%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20five%20largest%20exporters%20to%20India%20currently%20are%20China%2C%20Russia%2C%20the%20United%20Emirates%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%E2%80%99s%20exports%20to%20India%20shot%20up%20from%20%24%2022.13%20billion%20during%20April-October%20in%20fiscal%202023%20to%20%2436.27%20during%20the%20same%20period%20in%20the%20current%20financial%20year.%20India%E2%80%99s%20imports%20from%20Russia%20had%20risen%20by%20about%2067%25%20to%20%24%2030.42%20billion%20during%20the%20April-September%20period%20this%20fiscal%20on%20higher%20shipments%20of%20crude%20oil%20and%20fertiliser%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fimports-from-russia-up-67-in-apr-sep-on-higher-shipments-of-oil-govt-data-123101301366_1.html%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20commerce%20ministry%20data%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20China%E2%80%99s%20exports%20to%20India%20remained%20almost%20the%20same%20during%20the%20same%20period%20(April-October%202023)%2C%20with%20a%20marginal%20decrease%2C%20from%20%24%2060.26%20billion%20to%20%24%2060.02%20billion.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20UAE%E2%80%99s%20exports%20to%20India%20fell%20from%20%24%2031.67%20billion%20to%20%24%2024.91%20billion%20in%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Findias-trade-deficit-at-record-high-of-31-46-billion-imports-shoot-up-by-12-3%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20trade%20deficit%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20at%20a%20record%20high%20of%20%2431.46%20billion%20as%20imports%20have%20shot%20up%20by%2012.3%25.%20The%20trade%20deficit%20widened%20to%20%2431.46%20billion%20last%20month%2C%20much%20higher%20than%20economists%E2%80%99%20expectation%20of%20%2420.50%20billion.%20The%20expectation%20was%20as%20measured%20earlier%20by%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Findias-merchandise-trade-deficit-3146-bln-october-2023-11-15%2F%5C%22%3EReuters%20poll%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20five%20India%20export%20destinations%20are%20the%20US%2C%20UAE%2C%20Netherlands%