ter%20an%20aesthetic%20appeal%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20Priced%20at%20Rs%20500%2C%20Gowatham%20was%20able%20to%20sell%20nearly%20300%20planters%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20team%20at%20IIM%20Ahmedabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FGowtham-Reddy-1700051764.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gowtham%20was%20awarded%20with%20Lexus%20Design%20Awards%20for%20his%20self%20watering%20system.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FGowtham-Reddy-1700051764.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FGowtham-Reddy-1700051764-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FGowtham-Reddy-1700051764-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FGowtham-Reddy-1700051764-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FGowtham-Reddy-1700051764-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334173%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGowtham%20was%20awarded%20with%20Lexus%20Design%20Awards%20for%20his%20self%20watering%20system.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Gowtham%E2%80%99s%20innovative%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F270170%2Fwater-plants-on-vacation-expert-gardening-tips-diy-youtube%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eself-watering%20system%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereceived%20recognition%20at%20the%20Lexus%20Design%20Awards%20under%20the%20category%20of%20Best%20Student%20Project.%20The%20international%20design%20competition%20calls%20upon%20young%20creative%20talent%20around%20the%20wo