%2C%20crashed.%20This%20came%20as%20a%20defeat%20for%20the%20Indian%20National%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fasha-san-5-1699625115.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Asha%20has%20jotted%20down%20her%20experiences%20from%20scraps%20of%20papers%20that%20have%20become%20a%20significant%20personal%20account%20of%20the%20Indian%20freedom%20movement.%C2%A0%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fasha-san-5-1699625115.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fasha-san-5-1699625115-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fasha-san-5-1699625115-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fasha-san-5-1699625115-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fasha-san-5-1699625115-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334048%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAsha%20has%20jotted%20down%20her%20experiences%20from%20scraps%20of%20paper%20that%20have%20become%20a%20significant%20personal%20account%20of%20the%20Indian%20freedom%20movement.%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20year%20later%2C%20Asha%20and%20her%20father%20were%20given%20a%20safe%20passage%20to%20India%20and%20they%20were%20reunited%20with%20Sati%20in%201947%20when%20India%20was%20freed%20from%20British%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20can%20never%20forget%20the%20moment%20our%20country%20was%20freed%20from%20the%20British%20Raj.%20I%20would%20like%20younger%20generations%20to%20understand%20the%20hardships%20behind%20the%20freedom%20movement.%20Be%20a%20real%20Indian%20who%20never%20surrenders%20to%20the%20forces%20of%20any%20other%20country.%20If%20anyone%20says%20anything%20against%20your%20country%2C%20be%20brave%20enough%20to%20stand%20for%20it%20and%20correct%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Asha%20%3Cem%3Esan%20%3C%2Fem%3Etells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20in%20her%20frail%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20Asha%20restarted%20her%20education%20and%20got%20married%20in%201949.%20While%20she%20engaged%20herself%20in%20volunteer%20works%2C%20her%20contribution%2C%20like%20many%20other%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F190053%2Fgulab-kaur-woman-freedom-fighter-punjab-independence-day-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewomen%20freedom%20fighters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Tanvi%20believes%2C%20remained%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F129013%2Fnetaji-subas-chandra-bose-death-conspiracies%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENetaji%E2%80%99s%20death%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20most%20of%20the%20records%20were%20destroyed.%20So%2C%20not%20many%20know%20the%20contribution%20of%20the%20INA%20and%20this%20young%20girl%20in%20the%20Indian%20freedom%20movement%20in%20East%20Asia.%20It%20was%20only%20after%20INA%20members%20came%20to%20India%20that%20Indian%20citizens%20got%20to%20know%20about%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20regiment%20in%20Japan%20and%20how%20these%20women%20fought%20for%20freedom.%20We%20only%20know%20about%20a%20handful%20of%20female%20freedom%20fighters%20despite%20them%20being%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20freedom%20struggle%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20read%20such%20personal%20stories%20of%20war%2C%20it%20makes%20you%20understand%20what%20people%20went%20through%20and%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20take%20a%20country%2C%20that%20was%20nurtured%20by%20the%20sacrifices%20of%20people%2C%20for%20granted.%20Her%20story%20is%20inspirational%20for%20young%20women.%20For%20%3Cem%3Edadi%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eit%20was%20only%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%20that%20people%20started%20giving%20her%20recognition.%20This%20book%20has%20gotten%20some%20attention%20to%20her%20story%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tanvi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20even%20went%20the%20extra%20mile%20to%20collate%20various%20photographs%20and%20letters%20written%20in%20classic%20Japanese%20language%20and%20the%20INA%20archives%20to%20put%20together%20the%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Tanvi%E2%80%99s%20home%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20bedtime%20stories%20are%20centered%20around%20Asha%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20the%20freedom%20movement.%20Her%20children%20take%20pride%20in%20singing%20%3Cem%3EKadam%20Kadam%20Badhaye%20Ja.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20Tanvi%20Srivastava.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699626225000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334021%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Inspired%20by%20Netaji%20Bose%2C%20Asha%20Sahay%20was%2017%20when%20she%20joined%20INA's%20Rani%20of%20Jhansi%20regiment%20and%20fought%20for%20Indian%20independence.%20Her%20great-granddaughter-in-law%2C%20Tanvi%20Srivastava%2C%20has%20documented%20her%20incredible%20story%20in%20the%20book%20'The%20War%20Diary%20of%20Asha-san'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Is%20How%20Americans%20Really%20Feel%20About%20Tipping%20%E2%80%94%20And%20Who%20They're%20Likely%20To%20Tip%20Most%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22A%20new%20survey%20shows%20U.S.%20adults%20are%20far%20more%20likely%20to%20tip%20certain%20service%20workers%20than%20others.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699542004000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F654bf02